var book = {
	"name": "Isaia",
	"numChapters": 66,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Amozaa fapa Isaian Juda-ho lal Uzia te, Jothama te, Ahazaa te, Hezekia te lal laia, Juda-ho leh Jerusalem chungchang thua inlarna a hmuh chu.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Aw vante u, ngaithla u la, aw leilung, beng chhi rawh, LALPA chuan thu a sawi e: \"Fanaute ka chawmin ka tiseilian a, ka chungah an hel ta si a.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bawngpain a neitu a hria a, sabengtung pawhin a pu chaw pekna a hre bawk a: Israelho erawh chuan an hre si lo a, ka mite chuan an ngaihtuah lo e,\" tiin.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> A! hnam sual, khawlohnaa khat, thi th alo tih ching, hnam nikhua lo an ni. LALPA chu an kalsan a, Israel-ho Mi Thianghlim chu hmusit a, intihrangin an hnung tawlh ta.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Engati nge in hel zual deuh deuh a, vuaka in la awm cheu ni le? Lu chu a pumin a na a, thinlung pawh chu a pumin a chau ta.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Kephah hnuai atanga lu thleng zakin dam lai reng reng a awm lo; pem te, vuak duk chur te, pan hnai late hlir a ni: chung chu an hmet ping lo a, an tuam hek lo a, sahriak an hnawih hek lo.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> In ram chu a tiau zo a; in khuate chu meiin a kang zo va: in ram chu ram dang miten in mithmuhah an ei zo a, ram dang mite tihchhiat angin a chhe zo ta.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Zion fanu chu grep huana venbuk ang leh, fanghma huana thlam ang leh, khawpui hual vel anga hnutchhiahin a awm ta.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Sipaihote LALPA chuan tihboral bang tlemte min lo zuahsak suh se la chuan, Sodom ang khan kan awm daih tawh ang a, Gomorra ang mai khan kan awm tawh ang.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Sodom roreltute u, LALPA thu hi hre rawh u; Gomorra mite u, kan Pathian dan thu-ah hian beng chhi rawh u.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> LALPA chuan, \"In inthawina zozai hi ka tan eng nge a tangkaina awm? Berampa halrala hlante leh ran chawm thaute thau chu ka hne ta; bawngpate leh bram note leh kalpate thisenah pawh ka lawm lo e.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ka hmaa inlan tura in lo kal hian, ka biak in hung chhung kawtlai rah hi tuin nge phut che u ni?",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Thilpek mai maite chu rawn keng tawh suh u; englo rimtui chu ka tan thil tenawm tak a ni; thla thar te, chawlhni te, khawmpuia insawm khawm te mai mai chu ka ngaithei tawp lo mai.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> In thla tharte leh in hun bi nei kutte chu ka rilru chuan a hua a ni: ka tan thil hnawksak tak a ni; tuar ka ning tawh e.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Tichuan in kut in phar hunah pawh in lakah ka mit ka hup tawh ang a: a ni, vawi tam tak in tanwgtai hunah pawh ka ngaithla tawh lo ang: in kutte chu thisenin a khat si a.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Insil u la, intifai rawh u; ka mithmuh phak loah in thiltihte hi a sualna chu dah bo rawh u; sual tih hi bang tawh u la:",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> thil tha tih zir tawh rawh u; rorelna fel zawng u la, hnehchhiana tuarte chu tanpui u la, pa nei lote chu rorelsak u la, hmeithaite chu sawipui rawh u,\" a tih ni.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> LALPA chuan, \"Hawh teh u, i ngaihtuah tlang teh ang u! In sualte chu sen lar angin awm tawh mah se la, vur angin a var ang; sen duk angin sen tawh mah se la, beram hmul angin a awm ang.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Tihnuam tak leh thu awih taka in awm chuan, in rama thil thate hi in ei ang:",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> nimahsela in duh loa in hel chuan, khandaihin a ei zo ang che u: LALPA ka chuan chu chu a sawi tawh a ni,\" a ti a.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Engtizia nge khawpui rinawm tak chu nawhchizuarah a lo chan tak le aw! Rorel felnaa khatnu a nih thin vei nen! Amahah chuan felna a wm thin a, tunah erawh chuan tualthattute an awm tak zawk hi.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> I tangka chu a ekchhiaah a lo chang ta a, i uain chu tui nen pawlh a lo ni ta.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> I mi liante chu mi helhmang, rukrute thian an ni a; mi tinin tham an duh a, lawmman an um thin: pa nei lo te ro an relsak thin lo a, hmeithaite thute lah an hnenah a thleng ngai hek lo.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Chuvangin, Lalpa, Sipaihote LALPA, Israel-ho Mi Chaka chuan heti hian a sawi a: \"A! mi dotute hi ka tifikiang mai ang a, ka hmelmate chungah phuba ka la ang:",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> tin, i chungah ka kut ka thlak leh ang a, i ekchhia chu fai takin ka tibo ang a, i suan zawng zawng chu ka la bo vek ang:",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> tin, i chunga roreltute chu a tira an awm ang khan ka awmtir leh ang a, i chhunga remruattute chu a hmasa bera an awm ang khan ka awmtir leh bawk ang: chu mi hnuah chuan, 'Felna khawpui, khawpui rinawm tak,' an la ti ang che.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Zion chu rorelna fela chhan chauh a ni tawh ang a, a chhunga mi hawikir lehte pawh felnaa chhan chhuah an ni ang.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Nimahsela, bawhchhetute leh mi sualte tihchhiatna chu a awm rual ang a, LALPA kalsantute pawh tihboralin an awm ang.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> In sasaw duh takte chu in zahpui tawhin, in huan thlante avang chuan zak takin in awm dawn a ni.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Sasua a hnah uai tawh leh huan tui hmu lo ang mai hi in ni dan si a.Tin, mi chak tak chu ziza tawm ang a ni tawh ang a, a hnathawh chu meisi ang a ni ang; tichuan an kang dun ang a, tuma'n an timit lo ang,\" tiin.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Tin, mi chak tak chu ziza tawm ang a ni tawh ang a, a hnathawh chu meisi ang a ni ang; tichuan an kang dun ang a, tuma'n an timit lo ang,\" tiin."
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Amozaa fapa Isaian Juda-ho leh Jerusalem chungchang thu a hmuh chu.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Ni hnuhnungahte chuan heti hi a ni ang a, LALPA in amwna tlang chu tlang lian chungahte chuan tihnghehin a awm ang a, tlang te te chungah chuan chawisanin a awm bawk ang; chutah chuan hnam tinrengte chu an kal nguah nguah ang.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Tin, chi tam takte chu an kal ang a, \"Lo haw u la, LALPA tlangah, Jakoba Pathian inah chuan i chho ang u; tichuan ani'n a kawng chanchinte chu min zirtir ang a, a kalkawngahte chuan kan kal ang,\" an ti ang: Zion atang chuan dan thu chu a lo chhuak dawn si a, lalpa thu chu Jerusalem atnagin a lo chhuak dawn a ni.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Tin, ani chuan hnam tin karah ro a rel ang a, chi tam tak pawh a zilhhau vang: tin, a khandaihte chu leilehna hmawr zumahte an chher ang a, an feite chu theikung ahchhumna chem kawmahte an chher ang: hnam dangin hnam dang chungah khandaih an lek tawh lo ang a, indo dan pawh an zir tawh hek lo ang.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Aw Jakoba chhungte u, lo haw u la, LALPA engah i leng ang u.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Khawchhak lam tih dan te, Philistia dawite an ching a, ram dang mite tihdante an zawm tak avangin i mi Jakoba chhungte chu i kalsan ta a.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> An ram chu tangka leh rangkachakin a khat a, an sumte chu chhiar sen rual a ni hek lo; an ram chu sakawrin a khat a, an tawlailirte chu chhiar sen rual a ni hek lo.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> An ram chu milemin a khat a: anmahni kuta thawh chhuah, anmahni zungtangtea siam chu, an be thin.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Mi tete chu tihhniamin an awm a, mi liante chu tihlawmin an awm bawk a: chuvangin anni chu ngaidam suh ang che.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> LALPA hlauhawmna lak atang leh a mawina ropuina lak atang chuan lungpuiah chuan lut u la, vaivutah biru rawh u.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Mihring induhnate chu tihlawmin a awm ang a, mite chapona chu tihhniamin a awm ang, chu mi niah chuan LALPA chauh chu chawisanin a awm ang.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Sipaihote LALPA ni chu inngaisang leh chapo zawng zawng chungah leh chawisana awm zawng zawng chungah chuan a la awm dawn si a; tichuan tihtlawmin an awm ang:",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Lebanon tlanga sidar thing sang tak leh chawisana awmte zawng zawng chungah te,",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> tlang lian sang tak chungah te, tlang te chawisana awm zawng zawng chungah te,",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> in sang, sang tak zawng zawng chungah te, kulh tlangpui bang nei zawng zawng chungah te,",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Tarsish lawng lian zawng zawng chungah te, thil lem duhawm zawng zawng chungah te pawh a la awm ang.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Mihring induhnate chu tihhniamin a awm ang a, mite chapona chu tihlawmin a awm ang: chu mi niah chuan LALPA chauh chu chawisanin a awm ang.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Tin, milemte chu an boral daih ang.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Tin, lei hi nasa tak taka tinghing tura a thawh hunah, LALPA hlauhawmna lak atang leh mawina ropuina lak atang chuan mite chu lungpui pukahte leh lei kuaahte chuan an lut ang.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Chu mi niah chuan miten an tangkaraw milemte leh an rangkachak milem te, biak tura an siamsakte chu, buikelek hnenahte leh bak hnenahte chuan an paih ang a;",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> lei hi nasa tak taka tinghing tura a thawh hunah, LALPA hlauhawmna lak atang leh a mawina ropuina lak atang chuan, lungpui pukahte leh kham lungpui khu-ahte chuan an lut ang.An hnar chauha thaw awm mihring rin hi bansan tawh rawh uL eng kawngah nge rin tlak an nih tehlul ni?",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> An hnar chauha thaw awm mihring rin hi bansan tawh rawh uL eng kawngah nge rin tlak an nih tehlul ni?"
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ngai teh u, Lalpa, sipaihote LALPA chuan, Jerusalem hnen ata leh Juda-ho hnen ata chu an rinpui leh an rin ber, an rinpui chaw zawng zawng leh an rin ber tui zawng zawng chu, an laksak mek anih hi;",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> mi chak leh indo thiamte nen; roreltu leh, zawlnei leh, aienthiam leh, upate nen;",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> sawmnga hotu leh, mi zahawm leh, remruattu leh, themthiam leh, aikaihthiamte nen.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Tichuan, an mi laintea awm turin naupangte ka pe ang a, nausenten an chungah ro an rel ang.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Tichuan, mite chu hnehchhiahin an awm ang, tin, mahni thenawmte nen inhnehchhiahin an awm ang: naupang chu upa chungah chapo takin an awm ang a, mi chhe te pawh mi zahawm chungah chapo takin an awm bawk ang.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Miin a unau a pa inah chelhin, \"Nang chuan silhfen i nei a, kan roreltuah awm la, he chhiatna hi i kutah awm rawh se,\" a tih hunah;",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> chu mi hunah chuan ani chuan a aw a chhuah ang a, \"Kei zawng siathatuah ka awm dawn lo e; ka inah ei tur a awm si lo a, silhfen a awm hek lo: mite roreltuah min siak lo ang,\" tiin.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> A ropuina an hmusit avangin an tawng leh thiltihte chu LALPA do zawng a ni a, Jerusalem chu a chhe zo a, Juda-ho chu an tlu zo ta a ni.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> An hmel lan danin anmahni a hek chawp a; an sualna chu Sodom ang maiin an lantir a, an zep lo. An nunna chung chu a pik e! thil tha loin an inthungrul chawp si a.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Mi fel thu-ah chuan, \"An la tha dawn,\" ti rawh u: an thiltih rahte chu an ei dawn si a.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Mi sual chung chu a pik e! An la chhe dawn a ni: an kuta thiltih thungrulhna chu an hnenah pek a la ni dawn si a.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ka mite zawng anmahni hnehchhiahtute hi naupangte an ni ta a, hmeichhiaten an chungah ro an rel ta. Aw ka mite u, in hruaitute chuan an hruai sual che u a, in kalna kawngte chu an tichhe thin.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> LALPA chu sawipui turin a lo ding chhuak a, mite ro rel turin a lo ding ta a.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> LALPA chuan a mite upaho chungah leh an mi lianho chungah ro a rel ang: Lalpa, Sipaihote LALPA chuan, \"Nangmahniho hi in ni, grep huan ei zotute chu; mi retheite laka sum lak chu in inahte a ni a awm ni:",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> engtizia nge ka mite chu in nem sawr a, retheite hmai chu in rawt samw ni?\" a ti a.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Chu lo pawh chu LALPA chuan, \"Zion fanute chu chapo aka an awm a, dak awr awr leh mi melh hraw hrawa an kal a, an kal chu ti awh awhin an kal a, an kete an pen rik chhawng chhawng avangin,",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> LALPA chuan Zion fanute chhipah chuan pan khir a awmtir ang a, Lalpa chuan an zahmawhte pawh a tilang ang,\" a ti a.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Chumi niah chuan Lalpa'n an incheimawinate chu a laksak ang, kebun te, len lukhum te, nghawngkawl te chu;",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> bengbeh uai diah diah te, banbun te, inkhuhna puante chu;",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> lu cherna te, ke bun khaidiat te, kawnghren te, rimtui bawm te, invenna te chu;",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> hming nemna zungbun te, hnar vuahte chu;",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> kut ni thuamhnaw te, kawrfual te, puan sin te, ipte te chu;",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> darthlalang te, puan zai sin te, diar te, intuam mawina puante chu.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Tin, heti hi a ni ang a, mawisawla rimtui tak aiah thil tawih a awm ang; tin, kawnghren aiah hruizen a awm ang; tin, sam hniar siau aiah lu kawlhna a awm ang ; tin, puan mawi tak aiah saiip puan ven a awm ang: hmel that aiah thir linga deh chhiatna a awm ang.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> I mite chu khandaiha tihtlukin an awm ang a, i mi chak takte chu indonaah an tlu ang.A kulh kawngkharte chu an awm inchumin an tap ang a; ani chu a ruak ang a, leiah a thu ang.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> A kulh kawngkharte chu an awm inchumin an tap ang a; ani chu a ruak ang a, leiah a thu ang."
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Tin, chu mi niah chuan hmeichhe pasarihin mipa pakhat an chelh ang a, \"Keimahni chaw kan ei ang a, keimahni silhfente kan inbel ang e: i hming chauh min puttir rawh; ka hming chhia hi min chhilhsak rawh,\" tiin, an sawi ang.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Chu mi niah chuan LALPA peng chu mawi tak leh ropui takin a awm ang a, Israel-ho la damte tan chuan leia rahte chu tha tak leh mawi takin a awm ang.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Tin, heti hi a ni ang a, LALPA'n, rorelna thlarau leh kanna thlarau a, Zion fanute bawlhlawhna chu a silfai hnu leh,",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Jerusalem thisen chu a chhung ata a tlenfai hnu chuan, Zion-a la awm leh Jerusalem-a la awmte chu thianghlim an ti ang, Jerusalem-a la damte zinga hming ziak zawng zawng te chu.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Tin, LALPA'n Zion tlanga awmna zawng zawng chungah leh a inkhawmpuite chungah chuan chhunah chhum leh keikhu, zanah meialh eng a siamsak ang: ropuina zawng zawng chungah chuan englo zar a awm dawn si a.Chhunah ni sa hliahtu atan leh thlipui leh ruahpui lakah inhumhimna leh bihrukna hmun atan bawkte a ni ang.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Chhunah ni sa hliahtu atan leh thlipui leh ruahpui lakah inhumhimna leh bihrukna hmun atan bawkte a ni ang."
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ka tuh taka thu, a grep huan chungchang thu chu, ka duh taka tan lain ka sa teh ang. Ka duh taka chuan tlang lei tha tak maiah grep huan a nei a:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> a velin lei a lai khuar a, a lungte chu a chhar fai a, grep hrui tha ber mi a phun a, a laiah chuan in sang a sa a, chutah chuan grep sawrna khur pawh a lai a: tin, grep raha rah turin a beisei a, nimahsela grep suak maiin a lo rah ta zawk a.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Tunah hian, aw Jerusalem-a awmte leh Juda mite u, khawngaih takin kei leh ka grep huan kara thu hi min ngaihtuahsak teh u khai.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ka grep huanah hian ka tih tawh ang lo liam kha chuan a chungah eng nge tih leh chuan tur lo la awm ta ni le? Eng vangin nge, grep raha rah tura ka besei nen khan, grep suaka a lo rah mai kha ni le?",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Tunah hian gai teh u, ka grep huan chunga ka tih tur chu ka hrilh ang che u: a hling pal chu ka la bo ang a, ei zawhin a awm ang: a lung pal chu ka tichim ang a, rah behin a awm ang:",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> tin, ka tiram vek ang a; sah noin a awm lo ang a, laih phutin a awm hek lo vang; buar leh hnimhlingneite a to zakw ang: chhumte pawh a chunga ruah reng reng surtir lo turin thu ka pe bawk ang.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Sipaihote LALPA grep huan chu Israel chhungte hi a ni a, Juda mite hi a kung duhawm tak chu an ni si a; rorelna fel a beisei a, nimahsela, ngai teh, hnehchhiahna a lo awm ta zawk a; felna a beisei a, nimahsela, ngai teh, au thawm alo awm ta zawk a ni.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ram lailiah anmahni chauh an awm theihna tura mi tel vena hmun rang rang awm lo khawp hiala in leh in inzamwtir zel leh, lo leh lo inzawmtir zel thintute chung chu a pik e!",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Sipaihote LALPA chuan ka bengah heti hian a ti, \"Tihtakzetin in tam tak, lian tak tak, mawi pui puite chu, urtu awm loin a la ram ang.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Grep huan tin, sawm hmunah bath khat chauh a la haw dawn a, buh chi homer khat tuhin ephah khat chauh a la haw dawn si a,\" tiin.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Zu um tura zing tak taka tho a, uainin a tihruih bung hma loha zan rei tak tak thlenga awm thinte chu an chung a pik e!",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> tingtang leh perhkhuang te, khuangte leh phenglawngte, uain ne an ruaithehnaahte chuan a awm thin a, nimahsela LALPA hnathawh chu an ngaisang thin lo a, a kut thiltih chu an ngaihtuah ngai hek lo.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Chuvangin ka mite chu, hriatna an neih loh avangin, sala hruaiin an awm ta a: an mi zahawmte chu an ril a tam a, an mipuite chu tuihalin an dangro zo ta a.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Chuvangin Seol chuan a duhna chu a lo tizau a, a ka chu teh rual loh khawpin a ang ta a: tichuan an ropuina te, an mipui te, an ropui hbung bungna te, an zinga lawm taka awmte nen chuan an lut thla ta duah duah a.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Mi tete chu tihkunin an awm, a, mi liante chu tihtlawmin an awm a, chapo mitte chu tihhniamin a awm ta a;",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> sipaihote LALPA erawh chu rorelnaa chawisanin a awm ta zawk a, Pathian, Mi Thianghlim chu, felnaa tihthianghlimin a awm ta a.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Tin, beram note chu an tlatna hmuna an tla angin an tla dial dial ang a, mi thau pui pui hmun rama thilte chu vakvaihoten an ei ang.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bumna hruihruala khawlohna hnuk a, tawlailir hruizena sualna hnuk chu an chung a pik e!",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> \"Kan hmuhna turin ti thuai se la, a thiltih tur chu ti rang thuai rawh se: kan hriat theihna turin Israelho Mi Thianghlim remruat chu lo hnaiin lo thleng rawh se,\" ti thintute chu.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Thil tha lo chu thil tha tia, thi tha chu thil tha lo ti thina, eng chu thima ngaia, thim chu enga ngai thina, thil thlum chu thil khaa ngaia, thil kha chu thil thluma ngai thintute chu an chung a pik e!",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Mahni ngaiha fingte leh mahni mithmuha bengvarte chu an chung a pik e!",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Uain in kawnga mi chak ta, zu chawhpawlh kanwga thahrui nei apiangte chu an chung a pik e!",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> tham ei avanga mi sual thiam chantir thina, mi fel felna laksak thintute chu.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Chuvangin meialhin buh pal a liak ral duak duak thin ang leh, hnim ro chu meialha a tlu zawih zawih thin angin an zung chu tawihna angin a awm ang a, an par chu vaivut angin a chho chuai chuai ang: sipaihote LALPA dan chu an duh loh a, Israel-ho Mi Thianghlim thu chu an ngaihnep avangin.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Chuvangin LALPA thin chu a mite chungah a thawk a, a kut chu an chungah a lek a, a vua a, tichuan tlangte chu a khur dur dur a, an ruangte chu kawtthler laiahte chuan balhhlawh ang maiin a awm rem rum a. Chuti kauva a tih pawh chuan a thinur chu a la reh si lo a, a kut chu a la l ek ta cheu a.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> hnam tin hla taka mite tan chhinchhiahna a tar chhuak ang a, kawlkil ata ko turin a faifuk ang: tichuan, ngai teh, anniho chu rang takin an lo kal t huai ang:",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> an zingah tumah an hah lo ang a, an inchhuih hek lo ang; tumah an muthlu lo vang a, an muhil hek lo ang; an kawnghren chu phelh dulin a awm hek lo ang a, an pheikhawk c hilhna chu a cht hek lo ang:",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> an thalte chu zum tak a ni a, an thal ngul zawng zawngte chu khawih sain a awm thup a; an sakawr tinte chu meilung ang maia ngaih a ni ang a, an tawlalilir kete chu thawngaleivir ang maia ngaih a ni bawk ang:",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> an thawm ri hum hum chu sakeibaknei hahum ang mai a ni ang a, sakeibaknei vanglaite hahum ang maiin an ri hum hum ang; a ni, an ri hum hum ang a, an saseh tur chu a she ang a, him takin an kal bopui ang a, chhanchhuaktu tur tumah an awm lo ang.Chu mi nbiah chuan tuifinriat ri hum hum angin an chungah an ri hum hum ang: tichuan miin ram chu an han thlir chuan, ngai teh, thim leh manganna hlir a ni a, eng lah chu, chu mia chhumahte chuan tihthimin a awm a.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Chu mi nbiah chuan tuifinriat ri hum hum angin an chungah an ri hum hum ang: tichuan miin ram chu an han thlir chuan, ngai teh, thim leh manganna hlir a ni a, eng lah chu, chu mia chhumahte chuan tihthimin a awm a."
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Lal Uzia a thih ikum khan LALPA chu lalthuphah sang ak chawisana t hu ka hmu a, a silhfen hmawr fual chuan biak in chu a tikhat a vek a.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> A kiangah chuan serafte an ding a: thla paruk an nei theuh a, an thla pahnihin an hmai an khuh a, pahnihin an kephahte an khuh a, pahnihin an thlawk a.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Tin, \"Sipaihote LALPA chu a thianghlim e, a thianghlim e, a thianghlim e, lei pum pui chu a ropuinain a khat,\" tiin, an inau tawn an inau tawn thin a.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Tichuan a autu au thawmah chuan a kawngka bul lungphum lamin a nghing ta dur dur a, in chu meikhuin a khat ta a.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Chu veleh, kei chuan, \"Hmui bawlhhlawh pu mi ka nih a, hmui bawlhhlawh pu mite zinga awm ka nih avangin ka chung a va pik em! Ka boral ta a nih a hmu ta si a,\" ka ti a.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Chutichuan seraf pakhat, maicham ata chaicheha a cheh, mieling kengin ka hnenah a thlawk a,",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> ka ka a han dep a, \"Ngai rawh, hei hian i hmui a tawk a; tichuan i khawlohna lak bo a ni ta a, i sual pawh tlenfai a ni ta,\" a ti a.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Tin, \"Tunge ka tirh ang a, tu nge ka tan lal ang?\" tiin, LALPA aw chu ka hria a,",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Tichuan keiin, \"Kei heta hi ka awm, mi tir ta che,\" ka ti a. Tin, ani chuan, \"Kal la, he chite hi hrilh rawh. 'Bengin a hriat zawng hria u la, a ngaihna erawh chu hre suh u; a hmuh chu hmu u la, hriat erawh chu hre suh u,\" tiin.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> He chite thinlung hi tithau la, an bengte tingawng la, an mitte maimitchhintir rawh; chutilochuan an mitin an hmu ang a, an bengin an hria ang a, an thinlungin an hre bawk ang a, an hawikir leh ang a, tihdamin an awm dah ang e,\" a ti a.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Tin, kei chuan, \"LALPA, eng chen nge ni ang?\" ka ti a. Tin, ani chuan, a chhang a, \"Khawpuite mihring awm, awm loa a ram a, inte urtu awm loa rma chu a tiau vek a,",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> LALPA'n mite chu hla taka a sawn a, ram chhungah hmun kalsan hnu tam tak a awm hma loh chuan.Tin, a chhungah chuan samw zingah pakhat pawh la awm se la ei zawhin an awm lehnghal ang: nimahsela thil leh sasual kih hnua a bul a la awm reng thin angin chi thianghlim chu abul a awm reng chu a ni,\" tiin.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Tin, a chhungah chuan samw zingah pakhat pawh la awm se la ei zawhin an awm lehnghal ang: nimahsela thil leh sasual kih hnua a bul a la awm reng thin angin chi thianghlim chu abul a awm reng chu a ni,\" tiin."
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Tin, Uzia fa Jothama fapa Ahaza lal lai chuan heti hi a ni a, Suria lal Rezina leh Israel lal Remalia fapa peka chu Jerusalem run turin an chho a; nimahselah, an hneh thei lo.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Tin, Davida chhungte chu, \"Suria chu Ephraim nen an tang dun ta,\" tiin, an hrilh a. Tichuan a thinlung leh a khua leh tuite thinlung chu, ramhnuai thingte thliin a tinghing susu susu ang hian, tihnghinin a lo awm ta a.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Chutichuan LALPA chuan Isaia hnenah, \"Nang leh i fapa Searjasuba chu, dil chakta zawk tuilakna tawpah, puansutu phul lamlianah chuan, Ahazaa hmuak turin kal chhuak tawh u la;",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> a hnenah, 'Fimkhur la, awm hle hle rawh; meichher bung khu mai mai pahnih, Suria lal Rezina leh Remalia fapaa thinurna nasa tak chu, hlau suh la, i thinglung chu zam suh se.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Juda chu han beiin han tibuai i la, chutah chuan kan tan luhna tur siamin, a lai takah Tabeela fapa chu lalah i thuttir ang u, tiin.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Suria leh Ephraim leh Remalia fapa chuan an phiar che avangin.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Lalpa PATHIAN chuan heti hian a ti a. An thu phiar chu a puitling lo ang a, a hlawhtling hek lo ang.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Suria lu chu Damaska a ni a, Damaska lu chu Rezina lek a ni si a: kum sawmruk leh kum nga ral hmain Ephraim chu chi tih tlak loah aawm turin tihchhiat vekin a awm ang:",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> tin, Ephraim lu chu Samari a ni a, Samri lu chu Remalia fapa lek a ni si a. In rin duh loh chuan, tihnghehin in awm thuai lo ang, tiin,' ti rawh,\" a ti a.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Tin, LALPA chuan Ahazaa a be leh a,",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> \"LALPA i Pathian hnenah chhinchhiahna dil rawh; Seol thuk tak ata emaw van sang tak ata emaw,\" a ti a.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ahazaa erawh chuan, \"Kal dil lo ang, LALPA pawh ka fiah hek lo ang,\" a ti a.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Tin, ani chuan, \"Aw Davida chhungte u, tunah ngaithla teh u; mihring tihhah hi thil te tak teah in ruat a ni maw, ka Pathian lam pawh tihhah in duh zel ni?",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> chuvangin LALPA ngei chuan chhinchhiahna a pe ang che u; ngai teh u, nula thianghlim pakhat a rai ang a, fapa a hring ang a, a hmingah Immanuela a sa ang.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ani chuan thil tha lo lam duh loh nachang a hriat hunah leh, thil tha lam duh nachang a hriat hunah chuan bawnghnute khal leh khawizu a ei thin ang.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Naupang chu t hil tha lo lam duh loh nachang leh thil tha lam duh nachang a hriat hma pawhin lal pahnih i huatate ram chu a tiau dawn a ni,\" a ti a.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ephraim chuan Juda a then ni ata la thleng ngai lo nite chu LALPA chuan i chungah leh, i khua leh tuite chungah leh, i pa chhungte chungah chuan a thlentir ang, Assuria lal ngei chu.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Chu mi niah chuan heti hi a ni ang a, LALPA chu Aigupta lui tawp rettea tho awm leh, Assuria rama ikhuai awm chu, ko turin a faifuk ang.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Tichuan an lo kal ang a, an zain kawr chhe rek rukah te, lungpui pukah te, hnimhlingnei zawng zawngah te, ran tlatna hmun zawng zawngahte an fu ang.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Chu mi niah chuan Lalpa'n bakmehchem hawh, Luipui piah rama Assuria lal awm chu hmangin, lu leh ke hmul chu a ziat fai ang a; khabe hmul pawh a ziat bo vek ang.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Tichuan chu mi niah chan heti hi a ni ang a, mi pakhatin bawngla pakhat leh beram pahnih chauh a vul ang;",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> nimahsela heti hi a ni ang a, hnutetui tam tak an la pek dawn avangin hnutetui khal a ei thin ang: ram chhunga la awm apiangin hnutetui khal leh khawizu an ei theuh dawn si a.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Tin, chu mi niah chuan heti hi a ni ang a, hmun tin, grep hrui sang, tangka sang man awmna apiangte chu, buar leh hnimhlingnei hmun mai a ni tawh ang.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Ram zawng zawng chu buar leh hnimhlingnei hlir a lo nih tak avangin chutah chuan thal leh thal ngul kengin an kal ang.Tin, tlang, bawngtuthlawha laih tawh zawng zawngah chuan, buar leh hnimhlingnei hlauh avangin i lo kal lo ang a, bawngchalte tlattirna leh beram chil mai atan a ni zawk tawh ang,\" a ti a.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Tin, tlang, bawngtuthlawha laih tawh zawng zawngah chuan, buar leh hnimhlingnei hlauh avangin i lo kal lo ang a, bawngchalte tlattirna leh beram chil mai atan a ni zawk tawh ang,\" a ti a."
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Tin, LALPA chuan ka hnenah, \"Lehkha ziakna phek hlai tak la a, mihring kawlawmin a chungah ;Maher-salal-has-baza atan,' tiin, ziak rawh;",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> tichuan hretu rinawm, puithiam Uria leh Jaberekia fapa Zekaria chu hriatpuitu atan ka siam ang,\" a ti a.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Tin, zawlneinu hennah chuan ka kal a, tichuan ani chuan nau a pai a, fapa a hring ta a. Chutichuan LALPA'n ka hnenah,\"A hmingah Maher-salal-has-baza sa rawh.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Naupang chuan, 'Ka nu,''Ka pa, tih nachang a hriat hma pawhin Damaska hausaknate a hriat hma pawhin Damaska hausaknate leh Samari laka ral lak sumte chu Assuria lal hmaah an kal bopui dawn si a,\" a ti a.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Tin, LALPA chuan ka hnenah a sawi leh a,",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Heng chite hian Silova tui dam taka luang del delte chu an duh loh avang leh, Rezina leh Remalia fapa chunga an lawm avangin,",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> ngai teh, LALPA chuan luipui tui, khauh takte leh tam takte (Assuria lal leh a ropuina zawng zawng chu), an chungah a luantir ang : tichuan a kuang zawng zawng chu a lo liam dul dulin, a kam zawng zawngah pawh a liam dul dul ang :",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> tin, Juda-ho ram thlengin a tuam lut dul dul ang a; a liamin a luang tlang dul dul ang a; nghawng pawh a chim phak hial ang; tin, a thla zar chuan, aw Immanuel, i ram vang lam zawng zawng hi a awh vek ang.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> \"Chi tinte u, buai ta nuai nuai che u, kehsawmin in awm dawn nia; ram hla taka mi zawng zawngte u, beng chhi rawh u: inralthuam rawh u, kehsawmin in awm dawn nia; in ralthuam rawh u, kehsawmin in awm dawn nia.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Inrawn khawm rawh u, engmah a ni hlei lo ang e; thu sawi rawh u, a puitling thei lo ang e: Pathian kan hnenah a awm si a,\" tiin.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> LALPA chuan kut chak takin heti hian ka hnenah a saiw a, he chita kawngah hian ka kal ve lohna turin mi thunun a nih hi:",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> \"He chite hian 'Phiar an nei e,' an tih thin nazawng chu 'Phiar an nei e,' ti ve suh u; an tih pawh chu tih ve loin, hlau ve hek suh u.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Sipaihote LALPA, amah ngei chu in tithianghlim tur a ni; amah chu in tiha ni sela, amah chu in hlauha ni rawh se.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Tin, ani chu hmun thianghlim ani ang a; Israela chhung hnihte tan erawh chuan tlukna lung leh dalna lungpui a ni zawk ang a, Jerusalem-a awmte tan thang leh fal ani bawk ang.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Tichuan mi tam takin chu chu an chhuihin an tlu ang a, tihkehin an awm ang a, an awk ang a, manin an awm ang,\" tiin.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Hriattirna thu zial hi phuar la, dan thu hi ka zirtirte zingah nemin chhinchhiarh raw.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Tin, kei chuan Jakona chhungte laka a hmai thuptu LALPA chu ka nghak ang a, amah chu ka thlir reng ang.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> ngai teh, kei leh LALPA mi pek naupangte hi, Israel-ho zingah hhian sipaihote LALPA Zion tlanga awm laka chhinchhiahna atante leh thilmak atante kan ni a.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Tin, miin, \"Ramhuai aienthiam zawl leh dawithiam hram chuap chuap leh phun nuah nuahte chu rawn rawh u,\" an tih hunah che u chuan heti hian chhang rawh u, \"Miten an Pathian chu anr awn zawk tur a ni lo'm ni? Mi nungte tan chuan mitthi an rawn tur em ni?",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Dan Thu leh Hriattirna Thu chu rawn tur a ni,\" tiin. Chu mi thu ang zela an sawi loh chuan an tan khua reng reng reng a var thuai dawn lo a ni.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Mangang tak leh riltam chungin ram chu an fang ang a; tin, heti hi a ni ang a, an ril a tam hun chuan an thin chu a ur em em ang a, an lal leh an Pathian chu anchhia an lawh bawrh bawrh ang a, an vanvadak vak vak ang:tin, lei lam an en ang a, ngai teh, manganna leh thimna, thlaphan nguina chu a ni ang: tichuan thim chhah mupah hnawh boin an awm ang.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> tin, lei lam an en ang a, ngai teh, manganna leh thimna, thlaphan nguina chu a ni ang: tichuan thim chhah mupah hnawh boin an awm ang."
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Nimahsela thlaphanga awm tawhi tan chuan nguina reng reng a awm tawh lo ang. Hman lai chuan Zebulun ram Nephtali ram chu hmustawmin a awmtir a, nimahsela hun hnuhnungah chuan ropui takin a awmtir ta, dil kamah, Jordan ralah, hnam tin Galili chu.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Mi thim hnuaia kalte chuan eng nasa tak an hmu ta: thihna hlim rama awmte chungah ngei chuan eng chu a lo eng ta.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Hnam chu i titam ta a, an hlimna pawh i tipung ta a: buh seng laia hlim angin i hmaah an hlim ta a, miin rallak sum an sema an hlim ang maiin.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> A ritphurhna nghawngkawl leh a kovia zawn fung, a hnechiahtu talhtum chu, Midian-ho hneh ni ang khan i tihtliaksak ta si a.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Indona hmuna mi ralthuama an inthuamna zawng zawngte leh an silhfen thisen kai hniang hnuangte chu hala tuah ral a la ni ang.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Kan tan naupang a lo piang a, fapa pekin kan awm ta a: rorelna chu a kokiah a chuang ang a: a hmingah chuan, Maka, Remruattua, Pathian Chaka, Chatuan Pa, Remna Lal an ti dawn si a.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> A ram a zu zel ang a, a ramah remnain tawpintai a nei lo ang; Davida lalthutthlengah a thu ang a, dik tak leh fal takin rorelin a rawn tinghet ang, tun atanga kumkhuain, thahnemngaihna chuan chung chu a ti ang.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Lalpa chuan Jakob-ho ramah thu a thawn a, Israel-ho chungah a tla ta a.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Tichuan mi zawng zawng, Ephraim-ho leh Samaria awm, chapo tak leh rilrua uangthuang taka,",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> \"Lei rawh chante chu chim mah se la lung chang chherin kan rem mai ang: theipui thingte chu sah chhumin awm mah se la, sidar thingten kan thlak mai ang,\" titute chuan an la hria ang.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Chuvangin LALPA chuan Rezina dotute chu amah do turin a chawisang ang a;",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> a hmelma, a hma lama Suria-hote, a hnung lama Philistia-hote chu, a chawk tho vang; tichuan ka angin Israel-ho chu an ei zo ang. Chuti kauva a tih pawh chuan a thinur chu a la reh si lo a, a kut chu a la lek ta cheu a.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Nimahsela mite chuan anmahni vawtu lam chu an hawi chuang si lo a, sipaihote LALPA chu an zawng chuang hek lo.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Chuvangin LALPA chuan Israel-ho alian atein, tum kau leh phungladin ang maiin ni khat thilah a chhawk vek ang.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Upa leh mi zahawmte chu, a lu chu an ni a; dawt zirtir thin zawlneite chu, a mei chu an ni.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Heng mite hruaitute hian an hruai sual thin a ni; an hruaiate chu tihboralin an awm tihn.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Chuvangin Lalpa chu an tlangvalhote chungah a lawm lo ang a, an fahrahte leh hmeithaite chu a khawngaih hek lo ang: an zain Pathian zha lo mi leh thil tha lo titute an ni theuh a, ka zawng zawng chuan thu lawilo a sawi theuh si a. Chuti kauva a tih pawh chuan a thinur chu a la reh si lo a, a kut chu a la lek ta cheu a.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Suahsualna chu mei angin a alh hluah hluah si thin a, buar leh hnimhlingneite chu a kang ral thin: a ni, ramhnuai thing bit zingahte chuan a kang hluah hluah a, a khu chho ngut ngut thin.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Sipaihote Lalpa thinur avangin ram chu a kang chhia a, mite pawh chu meia tuah tur thing ang an ni a; tumah mahni unau pawh an zuah lo.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Tichuan miiin an ding lama mi an chuh ang a, nimahsela a ril a la tam cheu vang; an vei lama mi an ei ang a, nimahsela an tlai chuang lo ang: mi tinin mahni ban ti an ei theuh ang.Manase-hoin Ephraim-ho an ei ang a, Ephraim-hoin Manase-ho an ei ang: tin, an pahnih chuan Juda-ho an do dun ang. Chuti kauva a tih pawh chuan a thinur chu a la reh si lo a, a kut chu a la lek ta cheu a.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Manase-hoin Ephraim-ho an ei ang a, Ephraim-hoin Manase-ho an ei ang: tin, an pahnih chuan Juda-ho an do dun ang. Chuti kauva a tih pawh chuan a thinur chu a la reh si lo a, a kut chu a la lek ta cheu a."
		},
		"10": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Dan chimawm tak siam a, thupek khirh tak ngaihtuah chhuaktute u, in chung a pik e!",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Hetiang hian mi khawngaihthlakte dik takin in relsak duh lo a, retheite that vena tur in dang tlat a, hmeithaite in ei a, fahrahte in rawk a.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Tichuan, an kan niah che u leh hla tak atanga tiauna lo thleng turah chuan eng nge in tih tak ang le? tanpui dilin tu hnenah nge in tlan tak ang le? In ropuina chu khawiah nge in hnutchhiah tak ang le?",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Salho hnuaiahte an kun ang a, thahho hnuaiahte an tlu ang, chu chauh chu an chan a ni tawh ang. Chuti kauva a tih pawh chuan a thinur chu a la reh si lo a, a kut chu a la lek ta cheu a.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Hawh Assuria mi, ka thinurna talhtum, ka lungnih lohna kengtu tiang!",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Rallak la tur leh, thil laksak la tur leh, kawtthler chirhdiak anga rap turin ani chu Pathian zah lo hnam do turin ka tir ang a, ka thinurna mite beit urin thu ka pe ang.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Nimahsela ani chuan chutiang chu a tum ani lo a, chutiang chu arilru pawhin a ngaihtuah hek lo; hnam tam namena tam lo tihchhiat leh tihboral a ni a rilruk zawk ni.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> \"Ka mi lian zawng zawngte hi lal vek an ni lo'm ni?",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Kalno khua chu Karchemis khua ang mai ani tawh lo'm ni? Hamath khua chu Arpad khua ang mai ani tawh lo'm ni? Samari khua chu Damaska khu ang mai a ni tawh lo'm ni?",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> ka kut hian milemho ram, Jerusalem khua leh Samari khuaa mi aia milem siam chawp tha zawk neitu pawh, a zang chhuak ta si a,",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Samari khua leh a milemte chunga ka tih ang khan Jerusalem khua leh a milemte chungah pawh hian ka ti ve lo ang ang em ni?\" a ti si a.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Chumi avang chuan heti hi a ni ang a, Lalpa chuan Zion tlang leh Jerusalem khaw chunga a hnathawh tur zawng zawng a thawh zawh hunah chuan, Assuria lal rilru uangthuang rah leh a mit chapo ropina chu ka la hrem ang.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ani chuan, \"Ka kut chaknain ka ti a ni, ka finna nen hian; ka bengvar si a: chi tin, ramrite lah chu ka sawn a, an rote lah chu chhushak a, lalthutphaha thute lah chu mi huai tak tih angin ka hnuk thla ta a:",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> ka kut hian chi tin, hausaknate lah chu sava bu angin a zawng chhuak a; miin sava tui a pui rauhsan hnute an la angin leulung luah zawng zawng hi ka la vek a a ni: thla zap emaw, ka ang emaw, hram emaw reng reng pawh an awm lo,\" a ti vei si a.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Hreipui hian thl chehna'na a hmangtu chu a uankhum dawn em ni? Thingzaina hian a hruttu chu a hnuaichhiah danw em ni? Talhtumin alektute chu a lek vel zawk ang emaw, tiangin thing ni si lo a lek zawk ang emaw mai hi a ni.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Chuvangin Lalpa, sipaihote LALPA chuan, a mi thaute zingah chuan cherna a tir ang a; a ropuina hnuaiah chuan mei alh lai mek ang hian mei chhemin a awm ang.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Tin, Israel-ho entu chu mei atan a ni ang a, an Mi Thianghlim chu mei alh atan ani bawk ang: chu chuan ni khat thilah a hnimhlingneite leh a buarte chu a tikangin a tiboral ang,",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> A ram ngaw leh a lei tha hmun ropuina pawh chu, thlarau leh taksa lamin, a tioboral ang: tichuan, chhinchhiahna kengtu a chauh hun lai ang a ni ang.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> A ram ngawa thing la awm chhunte chu naupang ziak tham leka tlem a ni tawh ang.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Tin, chumi niah chuan heti hi a ni ang a, Israel-ho la awm chhunte leh Jakoba chhungte zinga a la damte chuan anmahni thattu chu an ring leh tawh lo ang a; LALPA Israel-ho Mi Thianghlim chu, tihtakzetin an ring tawh zakw ang.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> A la awm chhun, Jakob-ho la awm chhunte chu, Pathian chak tak hnenah chuan an la kir leh ang.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> I mi Israel-ho chu tuifinriat tiau vaivut zatin awm mah se la, a la awm chhunte chauh chu an kir leh dawn si a:",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> rorelna dik tak chuan a tihchhiat vek tur an ni.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Lalpa, Sipaihote LALPA chuan, tawpna, tawpna thleng ngei tura ruat tlat chu, lei chung zawng lailiah chuan a la siam dawn si a.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Chuvangin Lalpa, sipaihote LALPA chuan, heti hian a ti, \"Aw ka mi, Zion-a awmte u, Aigupta rama an tih ang khan talhtuma vua che uin a tiang chu in chungah lek mah se la Assuria m chu hlau suh u.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> rei lo te achinah chuan lungnih lohna chu hrikthlakin a awm tawh ang a, ka thinurna pawh anmahni tihborlnain hrikthlakin a awm tawh ang.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Oreb lungpuia Midian-ho an thah lai ang khan sipaihote LALPA chuan amah bei turin vuakna chu a chawk tho ang a: a tiang chu tuifinriat chung lamah a awm ang a, Aigupta rama a lek ang khan a lek ang.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Chumi niah chuan heti hi a ni ang a, aritphurh chu i koki ata lak boin a awm ang a, a nghawngkawl chu i nghawng ata lak boin a awm bawk ang: hriak thih avang chuan nghawngkawl chu tihchiatin a awm tawh ang,\" tiin.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Aiath khua a thleng ta, Migron khua a kal tlang ta; Mimkas khuaah a bungrua a dah ta;",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> kawnah an liam ta; Geba khuaah an riak ta: Ramah khawho chu an khur an khur ta; Saula Gibeah khawho chu an tlan bo ta.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Aw Galim khaw fanu! I awin ring takin au rawh; aw Laisah khua! Ngaithla rawh; aw Anathoth, i va khawngaihthlak em!",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Madmenah khawho tlan boin an awm ta; gebim khuaa awmte chu tlan bo tumin an inhawrkhawm luai luai e.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> vawiin ngei hian Nob khuaah a cham dawn: Zion fanu tlang, Jerusalem mual pawng chu, a kut a thin khum e.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Ngai teh, Lalpa, sipaihote LALPA chuan, thil rapthlak takin a zarte chu sat thla ang a: sang tak takte chu kihin a awm ang a, a lawr bikte pawh chu rawt hniamin a awm ang.Thirin ramhnuai thing bik takte chu a kit ang a, Lebanin sidar thingte chu mi ropi kihin a tlu dur dur ang."
		},
		"11": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Jesaia bul atangin chawrno a lo chhuak ang a, a zung atangtea puak chhuak chu a rah ang:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> tin, LALPA thlarau-finna leh hriat theihna thlarau, remruatna leh chakna thlarau, hriantna leh LALPA tihna thlarau chu - a chungah a fu ang:",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> tichuan a lawmna chu LALPA tihnaah a ni ang: a mita a hmuh angin ro a rel lo vang a, a benga a hriat angin a zilhau hek lo ang:",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> retheite chu fel takin ro a reslak zawk ang a, leia mi thuhnuairawlhte atan chuan thlei bik nei loin a zilhhausak bawk ang: a ka talhtumin lei hi a vua ang a, ahmuia thawin mi suaksualte chu a that ang.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Tin, felna hi a taihren a ni ang a, rinawmna hi a kawnghren a ni ang.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Tin, chinghnia chu beram no nen an awm dun tawh ang a, keite chu kel no nen an bawk dun tawh ang; bawng no leh sakeibaknei vanglai leh ran chawmthaute chu an awmho tawh ang a; naupang tein a hruai duah duah ang.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Tin, sebawng leh savawm an tla ang a; an nott chu an bawk za dial dial tawh ang: tin, sakeibaknei chuan bawngpa angin buhpawl a ei tawh ang.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Tin, nau hnute hne lai chu rulrial kaw kotlangah a tualchai ang a, nau hnute hnek bang tawh chuan rulmuk tawmkuk kotlangah a kut a nghat ang.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> ka tlang thianghlimah reng reng chuan intihnat a awm tawh lo ang a, intihchhiat a awm tawh hek lo ang: tuite hian tuifinriat a khuh reng angin, leilung hi LALPA hriatnain a khat zo vek dawn a ni.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Tin, chu mi niah chuan heti hi a ni ang a, Jesaia zung, mi tin chhinchhiahna atan ding chu, amah ngei chu hnam tinn an rawn ang a; a chawlhna hmun chu a ropui ang.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Tichuan Ephraim-ho itsikna ch a bo tawh ang a, Juda-ho tibuaitute chu tihboralin an awm tawh ang: Ephraim-hoin Juda-ho a itsik tawh lo ang a, Juda-ho pawhin Ephraim-ho chu an tibuai tawh l ang.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Tichuan anniho chu thlang lamah Philistia-ho kikiah chuan zuk thlawkin an zuk fu ang a; khawchhak fate chu an rawk za ang: Edom leh Mab-ho chungah chuan an kut an thlak ang a: Amona thlahte chuan an thu an awih tawh ang.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Tin, LALPA chuan Ephraim ho itsikna chu a bo tawh ang a, Juda-ho tibuaitute chu tihboralin an awm tawh ang: Ephraim-hoin Juda ho an itsik tawh lo ang a, Juda -ho pawhin Ephraim-ho chu an tibuai tawh lo ang.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Tichuan anniho chu thlang lamah Philistia-ho kokiah chuan zuk thlawkin an zuk fu ang a; khawchhak fate chu an rawk za ang: Edom leh Mab-ho chungah chuan an kut an thlak ang a: Amona thlahte chuan an thu an awih tawh ang.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Tin, LALPA chuan Aigupta tuifinriat tengsawl chu a tichhe vek ang a; Luipui pawh chu a thli lum huam huam chuan a kut a thin khum ang a, luite pasariha siam khawpin a vua ang a, mite chu kephah pawh huh loin a kal kaitir ang.Tichuan, Aigupta ram ata an chhoh nia Israel-ho tana lamlian a lo awm ang kha, a miteho thi bang la awm chhunte tan chuan Assuria ram atangin lamlian a lo awm ang.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Tichuan, Aigupta ram ata an chhoh nia Israel-ho tana lamlian a lo awm ang kha, a miteho thi bang la awm chhunte tan chuan Assuria ram atangin lamlian a lo awm ang."
		},
		"12": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Chu mi niah chuan heti hian i la sawi ang, \"Aw LALPA, lawm thu ka hrilh ang che; ka chungah lo thinur ta mah la, i thinur chu a reh ta a, nangin mi thlamuan ta a nih hi.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Ngai teh, Pathian chu mi chhandamtu a ni a; ka ring ang a, hlauin ka awm lo vang: LALPA JEHOVA chu ka chakna leh ka hla a ni si a; mi chhandamtu a lo ni ta bawk a,\" tiin.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Chuvangin chhandamna tuikhur atate chu hlim takin tui in la chawi ang.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Tin, chu mi niah chuan heti hian in la sawi ang, \"LALPA hnenah chuan lawmthu hril u la, a hming lam u la, a thiltihte chu mi tin zingah hriattir u la, a hming chu chawiawiin a awm tih sawi rawh u.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> LALPA chawimawiin hla sa rawh u; ani chuan thil tha berte chu a lo ti tawh si a; chu chu leilung luah zawng zawngah hian hriatin awm rawh se.Zion-a awmte u , ring takin au u la, au tuar tuar rawh u, Israel-ho Mi thianghlim in zinga rawm chu a ropui si a,\" tiin.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Zion-a awmte u , ring takin au u la, au tuar tuar rawh u, Israel-ho Mi thianghlim in zinga rawm chu a ropui si a,\" tiin."
		},
		"13": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Babulon khaw phur rik Amozaa fdapa Isaian a hmuh chu.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Mi liahnbo kawngkaahte chuan an luh theihna turin tlang kawlh vulah chuan chhinchhiahna tar chhuak u la, ring takin anni chu au u la, kutin zaizir rawh u.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Keimah ngeiin ka mi ruatho chu thu ka pe ta, a ni, ka mi chak tak, ka mi induh taka hlimte chu, ka thinur hrithlatu atan ka ko ta.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Chu! Tlanga mipui au thawm, mipui tam tak thawm ang mai chu! Chu! hnam tin rama mi awm khawmho sa mur mur thawm chu! Sipaihote LALPA chuan ral bei turin Sipaiho a pun hlawm anih chu.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Anniho, LALPA leh a lungnih lohna hriamhreite chu, ram hla tak ata, kawl kil tawp ret atangin ram zawng zawng hi tichhe turin an lo kal a ni.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Chiau vak vak rawh u; LALPA ni chu a hnai tawh si a; Engkimtitheia atanga tihchhiatna a lo thleng angin a lo thleng dawn e.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Chuvangin kut zawng zawng a chak lo ang a; mirhing thinlung tinreng pawh a tuiral ang:",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> tin, an hlau vang a; natna leh lungnih lohnate chuan a man hlawm ang a; hmeichhe nau vei ang maiin an na ang: mak intitawnin an awm hlawm ang; an hmelte chu meiahlh hmel ang mai a ni ang.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ngai teh, ram titiau tur leh chuta mi sualte chu a chhung ata tiboral turin LALPA ni chu nasa takin thinrimna leh thinurna nasa tak nen, a lo thleng dawn e.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> van arsite leh a chhohreivungte chu an eng an chhuah lo ang a; ni chu a chhuah laia tihthimin a awm ang a, thla pawhin a eng chu a entir dawn tawh lo a ni.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Tin, khawvel hi an sualna avangin ka hrem ang a, mi suaksualte chu an khawlohna avangin ka hrem bawk ang; tin, mi chapo tawng chaltlai chu ka tireh ang a, mi hlauhawm chapona chu ka tihniam bawk ang.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Mi hi rangkachak thianghlim ai pawha vang zawkin ka siam ang a, mihring ngei hi Ophir rangkachak thianghlim ai pawha vang zakwin ka siam ang.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Chutichuan, van khi ka tikhur ang a, sipaihote LALPA thinrim avangin, a thinurna nasa tak niah chuan, lei pawh hi a awmna hmun sawn dawrh khawpa tihnghinin a awm ang.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Tin, heti hi a ni ang a, sakhi um nek ang leh beram tuma khalh khawm loh angin mi tinin mahni chipuite lam theuh an hawi ang a, mi tin mahni ram lamah theuh an tlan bo ang.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Tupawh an hmh apiang chhunt langin an awm ang a, tupawh an man apiang khandaiha tihtlukin an awm ang.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> An nausente pawh an mithmuhah sawm dep khawpa lei vuakna'na hmanin an awm ang a; an inte chu rawkin a awm ang a, an nupuite chu pawnsual tawkin an awm bawk ang.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ngai teh, Media-ho anmahni bei turin ka chawk tho ang a, chungho chuan tangka an ngaihsak lo ang a, rangkachak ah pawh an lawm lo ang.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> An thla ngulte chuan tlangvalte chu a tisawm ang a; mi rila rah khawngaihna reng reng an nei lo ang a; an mit chuan naupangte a zuah lo ang.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Tin, Babulon, ram tin, ropuina, Kaldai-ho chhuan thil mawi tak chu, Pathianin Sodom leh Gomorra a tihboral lai ang khan a la awm ang.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Engtikahmah chutah chuan mi an awm tawh lo ang a, chhuan awm chhung zawng zawng chuan a chhungah awm an awm hek lo ang: Arab miten chutah chuan an puan in chu an zar hek lo ang a; beram vengtuten chutah chuan an beram rualte chu an bawhtir hek lo ang.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Thlalera ram sate chutah chuan an bawk ang a; an inte chu thil nung ngui taktein a khat ang a; sava ngahwngseite chutah chuan an cheng ang a, satharte chutah chan an tualchai tawh zawk ang.Tin, chinghniate chu an kulh bingah chuan an hram ang a, sihalte pawh an lal in nuam takahte chuan an hram bawk ang: tin, a hrem hun tur chu a thleng dawn tawh a, a nite pawh tihseiin a awm lo ang.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Tin, chinghniate chu an kulh bingah chuan an hram ang a, sihalte pawh an lal in nuam takahte chuan an hram bawk ang: tin, a hrem hun tur chu a thleng dawn tawh a, a nite pawh tihseiin a awm lo ang."
		},
		"14": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> LALPA chuan Jakob-ho a khawngaih ang a, a khawngaih ang a, Israel-ho chu thlangin anmahni ram ngeiah a la awmtir dawn si a: tin, ram dang mite chuan anmahni an zaw ang a, Jakoba chhungte chu an vuan ang a, Jakoba chhungte chu an vuan tlat ang.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Tin, mi tin chuan anmahni an hruai ang a, an hmun tur chu an thlen ang: tichuan Israela chhuungte chuan LALPA ramah chuan ani chu bawipaahte leh bawihnuahte an la nei ang a; anmahni sala neite chu salah an la man ang a; anmahni tiduhdahtute chungah chuan ro an la rel ang.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Tin, i lungngaihna ata te, i buaina ata te, hnathawh hautak ze an thawhtirna che atate LALPA'n a chawlhtir che niah chuan heti hi a ni ang a,",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> he tihelna thu h Babulon lal au khumin i la saiw ang, \"Eng tizia nge hnehchhiahtu chu a va reh ta em! Eng tizia nge rangkachak khawpui ch a va reh ta em!",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> LALPA chuan mi suaksual tiang a titliak ta, roreltute lal tiang chu;",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> mi dang chunga rawngra taka inlek a, an tlawm tawhte tiduhdah bang ngai lote,",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Leilung pum pui hi a chawl a, a reh rawih rawih a: hla an sa chhuak phut a.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> A ni, i chung thu avangin farte chu an hlim a, Lebanon tlanga didar thingte nen, \"Tihtlawma i awm achin chu kit thlutu tur reng reng kan hnenah an lo chho ngai ta lo,' tiin.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Hnuai lam ata Seol chu i lo thleng hmuak tur chein, nangmah avangin a buai mur mur a ni: mitthi, leia puipa zawng zawngte chu, nangmah avangin achawk tho a; hnam tin lal zawng zawng chu an lalthutphah ata a kai thi ta.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Chung zawng zawng chuan nangmah biain, i hnenah heti chuan nangmah biain, i hnenah heti hian an sawi ang, 'Nang pawh keimahni angin i chak lo e ta elo? Keimahni awm angin i awm ta elo?",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> I ropui bung bungna chu Seol-a hruai thlak a ni ta, i perhkhuang ri bur burte nen: changpat chu i hnuaiah an phah a, englo lungte chuan an khuh ta che a nih hi,' tiin.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Aw 'varparh,' 'zing lam fapa,' engtizia nge van ata i tlak tak chu le! Hnam tin titlawmtu, engtizia nge lai sah thlaka i awm tak chu le!",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> I rulruah chuan, 'Vanah ka chho ang a, Pathian arsite chung lamah khian ka lalthuphah ka chawi sang ang; tin, inkhawmna tlang, hmar tawp reta awmah chuan, ka thu ang a:",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> chhum aia sang zawkahte khain ka chho ang a; Chungnungbera ang maiin ka awm ang, i tih thin vei nen khan.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Nimahsela Seol-ah, klhuarkhurum tawp retahte chuan, hruai thlakin i awm dawn si.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> A hmu che apiangin an en ngun ang chia, 'He mi hi maw lei tikhura, ram tin tinghing a,",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> khawvel thlaler anga siama, a khaw awmte tiboral a, a salte an in lama kal tura chhuah ngai loa chu?' tiin, i chanchin an la chhut ang.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> hnam tin lal zawng zawng, an zainm mahni in theuhvah ropui takin an muhil a.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> nang erawh chu a zung puak chhuak tenawm tak leh, ral thah, khandaiha chhun tlang, khuarkhuruma lungte zinga chhukho silhfen angin i thlan in atanga hla takah paih chhuahin i awm tak zawk hi; ruang rah beh ang maiin.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> I ram i tihchhiat a, i khua leh i tuite i thah avangin an zingah phumin i awm ve lo ang; thil tha lo titute thlahte hming chu kumkhuain an lam lo ang.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> An thawh a, leilung an neih a, lei chung hi khuaa na tihkhah lohna'n, an pute sualna avangin a fate thah zai rel rawh u,\" tiin.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Tin, anmahni bei turin ka tho ang, sipaihote LALPA'n a ti, Babulon atanga hming leh, a la awm chhunte leh, fapa leh fapaa fapa chu ka tiboral ang, LALPA'n a ti.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Sakuh tan rovah ka siam bawk ang a, dilahte pawh ka siam ang: tihboralna hmunphiahin ka phiat bawk ang, sipaihote LALPA'n a ti.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Sipaihote LALPA chuan hetianga sawiin chhia a chham ta, \"Matheilova ka ngaihtuah ang tak hian a lo thleng ang a; ka ruat ang tak hian a awm bawk ang:",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> ka ramah chuan Assuria mi chu ka tichhia ang a, ka tlangahte chuan ka chil nek ang, tih ang hian: chu mi hunah chuan a nghawngkawl bahtir chu anmahni atang chuan a bo tawh ang a, an rit phurhtir chu anmahni koki atang chuan a bo tawh bawk ang.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Chu chu a ni, lei chung zawng zawnga thu ruat chu ni, chu bawk chu a ni, hnam tinreng chunga kut phar chu ni.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Sipaihote LALPA chuan aruat tawh si a, tuin nge suhsak ang? A kut chu pharin a awm tawh a, tuin nge lak kirtir ang?\" tiin.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Lal Ahazaa thih kumah khan ka phur rit hi a lo awm ta.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Aw Philistia ram pum pui, nangmah vuakna tiang at hlaih tak avangin lawm suh: rul zung atang chuan rulmuk a chhuak dawn si a, a rah chu rul alh thlawk thei a la ni ang.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Mi rethei fa tirte chu an tla dial dial tawh ang a, mi pachhiate chu him takin an bawk tawh ang: tin, nanga zung erawh chu tamin ka tithi ang a, i ta la awm chhunte chu thahin an awm ang.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Aw kawngkhar, chiau vak vak rawh; aw khawpui, au rawh; aw Philistia, i pumin, i tuiral zo ta; hmar lam atangin meikhu a lo chhuak si a, an hun ruatahte chuan hnufual reng an awm ngai lo a ni.Philistia hnam palaite chu engtin nge kan chhan ang le? \"LALPA'n Zion chu a din a, a mite zinga retheite chu amahah din a, a mite zinga retheite ch amahah an tlu lut ang,\" tiin a ni ang chu.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Philistia hnam palaite chu engtin nge kan chhan ang le? \"LALPA'n Zion chu a din a, a mite zinga retheite chu amahah din a, a mite zinga retheite ch amahah an tlu lut ang,\" tiin a ni ang chu."
		},
		"15": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Moab ram phur tir chu, Zan khatah Moab rama Ar khua chu tihchhiatin a awm a, engmah loa siamin a awm ta si a; zan khatah Moab ram Kir khua chu tihchhiatin a awm a, engmah loa siamin a awm ta si a.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bajith-ah leh Dobon-ah, hmun sangahte chuan, tap turin a chho ta a: Moab-ho chuan Nebo leh Medeba chu an tah khum vak vak a, an lu zawng zawng a kawlh vek a, khabe hmul tinreng pawh mehin a awm ta vek a.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> An kawtthlerahte chuan saiip puan an veng a: an in chungahte leh an mual zau laiahte chuan mi tin chu nasa taka tapin an chiau vak vak a.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Tin, Hesbon-ho pawh an au a. Elealeh-ho nen; an aw chu Jahaz in Moab-ho ralthuama inthuamte chu ring takin an au a; an nuna chu an kaw chhungah chuan a khur a.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Moab-ho avangin ka thinlung chu a au a; an m thate chu Zoar khuaah leh Eglath-selisi-jah-ah an tlan a: Luhith chhovah chuan tap chungin an kal chho a ni; Horonaim kawngah chuan chhiatna auin an au chhuak a ni.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Nimrim tuite chu tihchhiatin a awm dawn si a: hlobet chu a vuai zo a, hlobet chawrno chu a rawp a, thil hring reng reng ch a awm ta si lo.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Chuvangin an sum la neih chhunte leh an dah thatte chu tuipuisuthlah Lui ralah chuan an kal bopui ang.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Au thawm chu Moab ramri velahte chuan a thang si a; a chiau vak vak thawm chu Eglaim khaw lamah a thang a, a chiau vak vak thawm chu Beer-elim khaw lamah a thang a ni.Dimon tuite chu thisenin a bual zo vek si a: Dimon chungah chuan thil nasalehzual ka thlentir dawn si a, Moab-ho zinga tlan chhuakte chungah leh, chu ram ala awm chhunte chungah chuan sakeibaknei ka thlentir ang.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Dimon tuite chu thisenin a bual zo vek si a: Dimon chungah chuan thil nasalehzual ka thlentir dawn si a, Moab-ho zinga tlan chhuakte chungah leh, chu ram ala awm chhunte chungah chuan sakeibaknei ka thlentir ang."
		},
		"16": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ram roreltu tan beram note chu Sela khua thlaler lama awm atang chuan Zion fanu tlangah chuan thawn rawh u.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Tichuan, Moab fanute chu sava, a bu ata rau darha thlawk thlawkte angin Arnon lui kaiah an awm dawn nia.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> rem min ruatsak la, ro min relsak rawh; i hlim chu chhun laiah zan angin siam la: hnawh chhuahte chu bihruktir rawh; tlan bo chu mantir suh.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Moab zinga mi hnawh chhuaha awmte chu i hnenah awm rawh se; an tan tichetu hmel lakah chuan bihrukna hmun ni rawh: hleprutu chu engmah loa siamin a awm ta si a,tihchhiatna a reh ta a, hnehchiahtute chu ram atang hian tihboralin an awm ta.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Tichuan lalthutphah khawngaihnaa tihnghehin a awm ang a, chumi chungah, Davida puan inah chuan, mi pakhat, rorelin, rorelna fel zawngin, thil fel rang taka ti nghalin, tihtakzetin a thu ang.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Moab-ho chapona thu, an chapo em em ani tih kan lo hria a; an tawng chaltlaizia leh, an chapoizia leh, an thinurzia thu chu; an uannate chu engmah a ni lo.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Chuvangin Moab-ho chu Moab ho chungah an chiau vak vak ang: Kir-ha-reseth grep rep hlawm chu lungchhe vankaiin in la tah chhan ang.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Hesbon lote chu a chau zo ta si a, Sibmah grep hrui nen: hnam tin lalte chuan a kung tha mite chu an titliang pheng phung a; Jazer khaw thleng thlengin a zam hlawm a, thlalerah a za lut a; a pengte chu a zma darh sung a, tuipui chu a zam kai ta a.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Chuvangin Sibmah grep hrui chu Jazer tahin ka tah ang a: aw Hesbon leh Elealeh, ka mittuin ka leih ang che: i nipui rahte chungah leh i buh seng chungah chuan inbei au thawm chu a tla ta si a.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Lawmna chu laksakin a awm ta, lo tha tak atangte chuan hlimna chu laksakin a awm ta bawk a; grep huanahte chuan hla sak reng reng a awm tawh lo ang a, thawm hlimawn reng reng a awm tawh hek lo ang; grep sawrna khurahte chuan rap sawrtu reng rengin uain an rap chhuak tawh lo ang; grep seng au chu ka tireh ta.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> chuvangin ka rilte hi Moab khawngaih avangin tingtang angin a ri a, ka kawchhung chu Kir-heres khawngaih avangin tingtang angin a ribawk a.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Tin, heti hi a ni ang a, Moab chu a inlan hunah, hmun sangah intihaha, tanwgtai tura a hmun thianghlim a alo kal hunah chuan a hlawhtling lo ang.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Chung chu Moab chungchang thu LALPA'n tun hma lama a sawi kha a ni.Tunah erawh chuan LALPA'n, \"Inhlawhfa kum chhiar kum thum chhungin Moab ropuina chu, a mipui tam takte chawpin, hmuhsitawma awmtirin a awm ang a; a la awm chhunte chu tlemte tak meuh sawi tham loh an ni ang,\" tiin, a sawi ta.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Tunah erawh chuan LALPA'n, \"Inhlawhfa kum chhiar kum thum chhungin Moab ropuina chu, a mipui tam takte chawpin, hmuhsitawma awmtirin a awm ang a; a la awm chhunte chu tlemte tak meuh sawi tham loh an ni ang,\" tiin, a sawi ta."
		},
		"17": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Damaska khaw phur tir chu. Ngai teh, Damaska chu khawpui ni tawh lo turin lak bo a ni ta, tichuan in chim khawm mai a ni tawh ang.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Aroer khuate chu tlansanin a awm ta; beram rualte awmna tur a ni mai ang, chung chu an bawk ang aa, tuma'n an tihlau lo ang.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ephraim lakah kulhpui chu a bo ang a, Damaska lakah ram chu a bo ang, Suria rama la awm chhunte pawh an bo ang, Israela thlahte ropuina ang lekin an awm ang, sipaihote LALPA'n a ti a.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Nimahsela, oliv thing vuak hnua ziding sang ber chhipah rah pahnih thum emaw, thing rah tak zar sei berah te pali panga ema a awm thin ang hian chutah chuan hmaih chhar tur a la awm ang, LALPA, Israel-ho Mi Thianghlim chu a thlir tawh ang.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Tichuan buh sengtupan buh a laka, a vuite chu kuta a help ang mai hi a ang a; a ni, Rephaim ruamah miin buh vui hmaihte chu an char ang mai hi a ni ang.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Nimahsela, oliv thing vuak hnua a ziding sang ber chhipah rah pahnih pathum emaw, thing rah tak zar sei berah te pali panga emaw a awm thin ang hian chutah chuan hmaih chhar tur a la awm ang, LALPA, Israel-ho Pathian chuan a ti a.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Chu mi niah chuan miin an siamtu lam an en tawh ang a, an mitte chu Israel-ho Mi Thianghlim chuan a thlir tawh ang.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> maicham, anmahni kut chhuak lamte chu, an en tawh lo ang a, anmahni kuta siam, Aserte emaw, ni lemte emaw an zah tawh hek lo ang.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Chu mi niah chuan an khaw nghet takte chu ngawbing leh tlang chipa hmun tlansan hnu, Israela thlahte hmaa an tlansan hnu ang kha, a ni ang: tichuan hmun tihtiau ani tah ang.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Pathian i chhandamtu i theihnghilh a, i chakna lungpui chu i hre reng si lo; chuvangin kung mawi tak takte i phun thin a, a chhungah chuan tang danglamte i vut bur fur thin a:",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> i phun niin i ping vel thin a, zingah chuan i thil chi chu i tipar thin: nimahsela rah lawh chu lungngaihna leh natna nasa tak niah chuan a bo thin.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> A, mipui tam tak ri dur dur, tuifinriatte ri dur dur anga ri dur durte leh, hna tin, ri hum hum, tui nasa takte ri hum hu anga ri hum humte chu aw!",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> hnam tin chu tui tam tak ri hum hum angin an ri hum hum ang: nimahwsela ani chuan a zilhhau vang a, tichuan hla takah an tlan bo ang a, tlanga buhsi thli len ang leh vaivut thlipui len vir mup mup anga umin an awm ang.Tlai lamah chuan, ngai teh, thil rapthlek tak a awm a; tin, khawvar hmain an awm ta lo. Chu chu rallaka min laksaktute chan ani a, mi ruksaktute pual a ni bawk a.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Tlai lamah chuan, ngai teh, thil rapthlek tak a awm a; tin, khawvar hmain an awm ta lo. Chu chu rallaka min laksaktute chan ani a, mi ruksaktute pual a ni bawk a."
		},
		"18": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> A, thla zap ri hum hum ram, Ethiopia rama luite rala awm,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> tuipuia, tui chunga luang lawngahte palaiho tirtu chu! Zualko chak takte u, hnam sang thler thlawrh mam tak hnenah, an chhuah tan achin tun thleng mi hlauhawm takte hnenah chuan, kal rawh u; chu hnam chuan ram an sem thin a, an rapthlu bawk thin, an ram chu luite chuan a sem darh a ni.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Khawvela awm zawng zawng leh leilung luahte u; tlangahte chhinchhiahna an tar chhuah hunah en rawh u: tawtawrawt an ham hunah ngaithla rawh u.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> LALPA'n ka hnenah heti hian a saiw a ni, \"Ka awm hle hle ang a, ka awmnaah hian ka thlir reng ang; ni sat laia khaw lum thiang vel vul ang leh buh seng khaw lum laia daifim chhum ang hian, tiin.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Grep lawh hun hmaa, a par a rem a, a par chu grep puama a lo cha hunah chuan, a peng te te chu theikung ahchhumna chemtein a ait chhum dawn si a, a peng zam darhte chu a lo boin a sat chhum bawk ang.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Chung chu tlanga sava kohamte tan leh, leia sate tan chuan hnutchhiahin an awm hlawm ang: tichuan sava kohamte chuan anni chu nipui chhungin an ei ang a, leia sa zawng zawng chuan thlasik chhungin an ei ang.Chu mi hunah chuan, sipaihote LALPA hming awmna hmun, Zion tlangah chuan, sipaihote LALPA hnena pek atan mi sang thlerh thlawrh mam takte hnen ata, an chhuah tan achin tun thlenga mi hlauhawm takte hnen ata chu, lawmman an rawn sin ang; chu hnam chuan ram an sem thin a, an rapthlu bawk thin, an ram chu luite chuan a sem darh a ni.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Chu mi hunah chuan, sipaihote LALPA hming awmna hmun, Zion tlangah chuan, sipaihote LALPA hnena pek atan mi sang thlerh thlawrh mam takte hnen ata, an chhuah tan achin tun thlenga mi hlauhawm takte hnen ata chu, lawmman an rawn sin ang; chu hnam chuan ram an sem thin a, an rapthlu bawk thin, an ram chu luite chuan a sem darh a ni."
		},
		"19": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Aigupta ram phur rit chu.Ngai teh, LALPA chu chhum chak tak chunga chuangin Aigupta ram a lo thleng ta e: Aigupta ram milemte chu a hmaah chuan an khur zawih zawih ang a, Aigupta-ho thinlung chu an kawchhungah a tuiral mai ang.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Tin, Aigupta mite chu Aigupta mite vek bei turin ka chawk tho ang: tichuan, mi tinin mahni unau beiin, mi tinin mahni thenawm beiin, an inkap ang; khua leh khua an inbei ang a, ram leh ram an inbei ang.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Tichuan, Aigupta-ho thlarau chu an kawchhungah chuan engmah loa siamin a awm ang a; an remruat chu ka tichhia ang: tichuan, milemte leh, aikaihthiamte leh, ramhuai aienthiam zalwte leh, dawithiamte chu an rawn ang.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Tin, Aigupta mite chu hotu nunchhe tak kutah chuan ka hlan ang a; tichuan lal kawlh takin an chungah ro a rel tawh ang. Lalpa, sipaihote LALPA chuan a ti.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Tin, tuipui tuite chu a kang ang a, lui chu a luang boin a lo kangchat tawh ang.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Luite ch a rimchia ang a; Aigupta ram tuiluangte chu a kam telh telh ang a, a kangchat mai ang: phairuangte leh tui hnimte chu a vuai zo ang.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Nile lui kianga, Nile lui kam ngeia, ran tlatna phulte leh, Nile lui kianga thil chin zawng zawngte chu a lo ro ang a, len boin a awm ang a, a awm tawh lo ang.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> sangha mantute pawh chu an tap ang a, Nile luia nghakawi khai thinte zawng zawngte chu an awm an inchum chau tawh ang.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Chu lo pawh chu ziza zai sin dke mite leh puan ngo tah mite chu an mualpho ang.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Tin, a lung bante chu tihsawmin a awm ang a, inhlawhfa thin zawng zawngte chu an rilrui an lungngai ang.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Zoan khuaa mi liante chu an a ngawt mai: Pharaoa remruattu fing berte remruat chu sa remruat ang mai a lo ni ta; Pharaoa hnenah, \"Mi fing fapa, hmasang lalho fapa ka ni,\" engtiziaa ti thin nge in nih?",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Khawiah nge i mi fingte chu le? Anni chuan hrilh nghal che rawh se; Aigupta ram chung thil thleng tur sipaihote LALPA ruatte chu, hre rawh se.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Zoan khua ami liante chu mi a an lo ni ta a, Noph khuaa mi liante chu bumin an awm ta; Aigupta hnamho kila lungte chuan Aigupta-ho chu an vah botir ta.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> LALPA chuan Aigupta-ho zingah luhlulna thlarau a awmtir ta: tichuan zu rui mi chu a luakah a pai thlawk thlawk ang hian Aigupta-ho chu an hnathawh tinrengah a kal kawitir ta.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Aigupta-ho tan luin emaw, meiin emaw, tum kauin emaw, phungladinin emaw thawhsak theih a awm tawh hek lo ang.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Chu mi niah chuan Aigupta-ho chu hmeichheho ang an ni ang a: sipaihote LALPA kut thin chu an chunga a thin avangin an khurin an hlau ang.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Juda rama awmho chu Aigupta-ho tan chuan rapthlak tak an lo ni tawh ang a, an hming an lamna apiangte chuan an hlau vang, an chunga thleng tur sipaihote LALPA thu ruat avang chuan.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Chu mi niah chuan Kanaan-ho tawnga tawng leh,sipaihote LALPA hnenah chhechhama thu tiam thinte chu, Aigupta ram chhungah khaw panga a awm ang a; pakhat chu Boralna Khua an ti ang.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Chu mi niah chuan Aigupta ram laiah chuan LALPA tan maicham a awm ang a, a ramriah chuan LALPA tan lungphun a awm ang.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Chu chu Aigupta ram a sipaihote LALPA tan chuan chhinchhiahna leh hriatna a ni ang: hnehchhiahtute avangin LALPA an la au dawn si a, tichuan anin chhandamtu leh humhimtu a tir ang a, ani chuan anniho chu a chhan chhuak ang.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Tichuan LALPA chu Aigupta mite chuan chu mi niah chuan LALPA chu an hre tawh ang;a ni, inthawina leh thil pekin chibai an buk ang a, LALPA hnenah chuan thu an tiam ang a, an hlen bawk ang.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Tin, LALPA chuan Aigupta-ho chu a vua ang; a vua ang a, a tidam bawk ang; tichuan LALPA hnenah an kir leh ang a, ani chu anmahni ngen thlukin a awm ang a, anmahni a tidam ang.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Chumi niah chuan Aigupta ram atangin Assuria ram thlengin lamlian a awm ang a; tichuan Assuria mite chu Aigupta ramah an kal ang a, Aigupta mite chu Assuria ramah an kal bawk ang; Aigupta mite chuan Assuria mite nen Pathian chibai an buk tlang tawh ang.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Chumi niah chuan Israel-ho chu Aigupta-ho leh Assuria-ho pathumtu an n ni ang a, lei lailiah hian malsawmna an ni ang:sipaihote LALPA chuan, \"Ka mi Aigupta-hpte leh ka kut chhuak Assuria-hote leh ka rochan Israel-hote chu malsawmin awm rawh se,\" tiin, mal a sawm si a.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> sipaihote LALPA chuan, \"Ka mi Aigupta-hpte leh ka kut chhuak Assuria-hote leh ka rochan Israel-hote chu malsawmin awm rawh se,\" tiin, mal a sawm si a."
		},
		"20": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Assuria lal Sargona tithin Tartana Asdod khuaa a lo kal a, Asdod khua a bei a, a lak kum khan;",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> chumi lai chuan LALPA'n Amozaa fapa Isaia ka chuan, \"Kal la, i kawnga saiip puan kha phel la, i kea i pheikhawk kha dah rawh,\" tin, a sawi a. Tichuan chutiang chuan a ti a, saruak leh pheikhawk bun loin a kal a kal ta a.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Tin, LALPA chuan, \"Ka chhiahhlawh Isaia hi Aigupta-ho chungah leh Thiopia-ho chungah chhinchhiahna leh thilmak atan kum thum chhunga saruak leh pheikhawk bun loa a kal ang hian,",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Assuria lal chuan Aigupta-ho mante leh Ethiopia-ho salte chu, apui apangin, saruak leh pheikhawk bun lo leh mawng langin Aigupta-ho mualphona turin a hruai bo ang.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Tichuan an beisei ber Ethiopia-ho leh an ropuina ber Aigupta-ho avang chuan mangang tak leh mualpho takin an awm tawh ang.Tichuan, chu mi niah chuan he tuifinriat kama mi hian, 'Ngai teh, kan beisei ber, Assuria lal laka min chhanhim tura min puitu atana kan tlanna chu, heti a ni ta si a: keini hi engtin nge ka tlan chauh ang?' an la ti ang,\" a ti.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Tichuan, chu mi niah chuan he tuifinriat kama mi hian, 'Ngai teh, kan beisei ber, Assuria lal laka min chhanhim tura min puitu atana kan tlanna chu, heti a ni ta si a: keini hi engtin nge ka tlan chauh ang?' an la ti ang,\" a ti."
		},
		"21": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Tuipui thlaler phur rit chu. Chhim rama thawngaleivir a kal tlang angin thlaler atangin, ram hlauhawm tak atang chuan, a lo kal e.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> inlarna khirhkhan tak ka hnenah hriattir a ni tawh; vervek taka titu chuan vervek takin a ti a, rawktu chuan a rawk a. Aw Elam-ho, kal chho rawh u; aw Media-ho hual rawh u; an rumna zawng zawng chu ka tireh vek tawh e.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Chuvangin ka kawngte hi natna nasa takin a khat a, hmeichhe nau vei natna anga natnain mi man ta: benga hre thei anga natnain mi man ta: benga hre thei lo khawpin na ka tuar a, khaw hmu thei lo khawpin ka mangang a.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> ka thinlung hi a thaw hlawp hlawp a, thil rapthlak takin mi tihlau va: tlai nem ka nghahhlelh thin kha ka tan khurhnaah a chang ta.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Dawhkan chu an buatsaih a, ralvengtu chu an ventir a, an ei a, an in a: mi lainate u, tho u la, phaw kha hriak hnawih rawh u.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Lalpa chuan ka hnenah heti hian a sawi a ni, \"kal la, ralvengtu ventir rawh; ani chuan a thil hmuh chu sawi rawh se:",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> tin, sipai pawl te, sakawr chung chuan, a kawp zela kal te, sabengtung pawl te, sanghawngsei pawlte a hmuh hunah chuan ngun takin a ngaithla kiau vang,\" tiin.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Tin, ani chu sakeibaknei angina au a; \"Aw LALPA, chhunah chuan ralven buk chungah hian ka ding fo a, zankhua khuain ka vennaah hian mi awmtir fo a:",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> ngai teh, hetah hian mihring paw, sakawr chung chuang, a kawp zela kal an lo kal e,\" tiin. Tin, amah vek chuan, \"Babulon khua chu a tlawm ta, a tlawm ta; an pathianho milem siam chawpte zawng zawng chu leiah tihkeh sawmin a awm ta,\" tiin, a chhang a.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Aw ka buh vuaksa, ka hruiha buh: sipaihote LALPA, Israel-ho Pathian laka ka hriat chu ka hrih che u a nih hi.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Dumah phur tir chu. Miin Seir tlang atangin mi au a, \"Ramvengtu, zan hi engti nge ni tawh? Ralvengtu zan hi engti nge ni tawh?\" tiin.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ralvengtu chuan, \"Zing a lo ni dawn ta e, zan pawh; in zawh duh chuan zawt rawh u: hawi leh u la, lo kal rawh u,\" a ti a.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Arabia ram chunga phur rit chu. Aw Dedan-ho khualzin pawl tinte u, Arabia rama ramhnuaiah in riak ang.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Tuihal hnenah chuan tui an rawn la a, tema rama awmte chuan an chawin tlan bote chu an hmuak a.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Khandaihte lakah, khandaih phawi sa lakah leh, thal ngun khawih sa lakah leh indona nasa tak lak ata tlan bo an ni si a.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> LALPA chuan heti hian ka hnenah a sawi si a, \"Inhlawhfa kum chhiar kum khat chhungin Kedar-ho ropuina zawng zawng chu a bo zo ang a,thal kap mi, Kedara thlahte zinga mi chak tak la awm chhun chu, tlem te an ni ang: LALPA, Israel-ho Pathian chuan, chu chu a sawi tawh si a,\" tiin.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> thal kap mi, Kedara thlahte zinga mi chak tak la awm chhun chu, tlem te an ni ang: LALPA, Israel-ho Pathian chuan, chu chu a sawi tawh si a,\" tiin."
		},
		"22": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Inlarna ruam phur rit chu. Eng in ti nge ni le, in chungahte in lawn vek ni?",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Aw au thawma khat, khawpui sa mur mur, khaw hlim tak, i chhunga an thahte chu khandaiha thah chhunga an thahte chu khandaiah thah an ni lo a, inkahnaa thi an ni hek lo.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> I roreltu zawng zawng chu an tlan bo za a, thal kap mite phuarin an awm a: i ta an hmuh zawng zawng chu phuar khawmin an awm a, hla tak atanga lo tlan bote chu. Chuvangin kei chuan, \"Min en loin lehlam en rawh u, ka tap vak vak dawn e; ka miteho fanu rallaka an lak thu-ah chuan mi hnem duh harsa suh u\" ka ti a.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> inlarna ruamah hian buaina te, manganna te, rah behna te, Lalpa sipai-hote LALPA hnen ata a lo thleng a. Kulh bang tihchim a ni a, tlangahte mangangin an au a.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Tichuan, Elam-ho chuan thal bawm an keng a, mihring huanna talailirte leh sakawr chung chuang mite nen: Kir-ho chuan phaw tuamna chu an phelh a.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Tin, heti hi a ni a, i ruam tha berte chu tawlailirtein a khat a a, sakawr chung chuang mite chu kulh kawngkhar bulah an tlim hmui a.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Tin, Juda-ho khuhna chu a la bo a; tichuan chu mi niah chuan ngawpu ina ralthuamna chu in en ta a.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Davida khaw kulhpui chhe laite in en bawk a, a tam tih in hria a: tin, dil thlangta zawk tuite chu in luan khawmtir a.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Tin Jerusalem inte in chhiar a, kulhpui bang siam thatna'n inte chu in thiat a.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Dil hlui tui awmna turin kulhpui pahnih karah chuan ti tlinkhawmna in siam a; nimahsela chung titu lam chu in en si lo a, hmasanga lo siamtu chu in ngaihsak hek lo.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Chumi niah chuan Lalpa, sipaihote LALPA chuan, tap tur leh awm inchum tur leh lu tikawlh tur leh saiip puan veng turin a ko va:",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> nimahsela, ngai the, hlimna leh lawmna te, bawng talhna leh beram talhna te, sa eina leh uain inna te a am ta zawk a, \"I eiin i in ang u, naktukah chuan kan thi dawn si a,\" an ti a.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Tichuan sipaihote LALPA chu ka bengah a inhriattir a, \"Mathei loin he sualna hi in thih hma loh zawng in lakah tlenfai ani tawh lo ang, Lalpa, sipaihote LALPA chuan a ti,\" tiin.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Lalpa, sipaihote LALPA chuan, heti hian a ti, \"Kal la, he sum enkawltu tehchai hnenah hian, Sebnaa, lal in chunga hotua awm hnen ngeiah chuan, kal rah.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Tin, a hnenah heti hian sawi rawh, 'Hetah hian eng nge i tih? Hetah hian tute nge i neih a, thlan hetah i ker kuak tehchai ni? Ama tan sang taka thlan a ker kuak a, ama tan lungpuia awmna a siam tehchai hi!",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ngai teh, LALPA chuan mi chakin a paih angin a paihin apaih vak ang che; a ni, a funin a fun tlat ang che.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ani chuan matheiloin bawl hlum angin a tivir ang chia, ram zau takah a vawrh lut ang che; chutah chuan i thi ang a, chutah bawk chuan, nang, mahni lal in chhung timualphotupa, i ropuina tawlailirte chu a awm ang.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> I hnathawhna ata a hnawt chhuak ang chia, ani chuan i hotu nihna ata chu a hnuk thla ang che.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Tin, chu mi niah chuan heti hi a ni ang a, ka chhiahhlawh Eliakima,Hilkia fapa chu, ka ko ang a:",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> ani chu i kawrfual hi ka haktir ang a, i kawnghren hian ka tichak ang a, i rorelna hi a kutah ka kawltir ang: tichan ani chu Jerusalema awmte tan leh Juda chhungte tan pi a ni ang.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Tin, Davida chhungte chabi chu a kokiah ka dah ang a; ani chuan a hawng ang a, tuma'n an khar lo ang; a khar ang a, tuma'n an hawng lo ang.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Tin, ani chu, klhna hi hmun nghet taka an kilh tlat ngin, ka tinghet tlat ang a; tichuan ani chu a pa chhungte tan lalthutphah ropi tak atan a ni ang.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Tin, amahah chuan a pa chhungte ropuina zawng zawng chu an la bang vek ang, a fate leh a thlahte bungbelte tinreng, berhbu bungbel atanga tui dahna bungbel zawng zawng thlengin.Chu mi niah chuan, kilhna, hmun nghet taka kilh tlata awm chuan a la dawl lo vang: sah thlaka awmin, a tla tawh ang a, a chunga thil rit awm chu tihboralin a awm tawh ang; LALPA'n chu chu a sawi tawh si, sipaihote LALPA chuan a ti,\" tiin.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Chu mi niah chuan, kilhna, hmun nghet taka kilh tlata awm chuan a la dawl lo vang: sah thlaka awmin, a tla tawh ang a, a chunga thil rit awm chu tihboralin a awm tawh ang; LALPA'n chu chu a sawi tawh si, sipaihote LALPA chuan a ti,\" tiin."
		},
		"23": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Tura khaw phur rit chu. Tarsis lawng liante u, chiau vak vak rawh u; in reng reng awm lo khawpa tura chu tihchhiata a awm tak hi; chu chu Kupra ram atangin in lo hira a.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Tuipui kama chengte u, ngawi rawh u, Sidon khaw sumdawngte u,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> tuipui chunga kalin Aigupta ram Nile lui buh in chaw a, ram tinah in hralh a, in help chu in sum hnar ber a ni.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Aw Zidon, zak rawhL tuifinriat, tuifinriat kulhpui chuan, thu a sawi ta si a, \"Nau ka vei ngai lo a, ka hring ngai hek lo a, nula pawh ka tiseilian ngai hek lo,\" tiin.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Thuthang chu Aigupta ram a thlen hun chuan tura thuthang chu nasa takin an vei ang.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Tarsis-ah va kai u la; thliarkara awmte u, chiau vak vak rawh u.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Hei hi maw in khaw hlim tak, a hlunzia murakeka mi tawh, a kein hla taka awm tura a hruai thina chu?",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Lallukhum khumtirtu khua tura chungah hian tuin nge hei hi thleng turin ruat? Chuta sumdawngtute chu mi liante an ni a, chuta sumdawng mite chu leia mi zahawmte an ni si a.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Sipaihote LALPA chuan chapote ropuina tih tlawm leh khawvel mi zahawmte tihmualpho a tum tlat a ni.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Aw Tarsis fanu, Nile lui angin i ramah chuan luang liam rawh; i kawnghrenna reng reng a tawm tawh loh hi.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Tuifinriat chungah a kut a phar a, ramte chu a tinghing a: LALPA chuan Kanaan ram chungchang thu-ah thu a pe a, a kulhbingte tichhe turin.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Tin, anni chuan, \"Aw Zidon fanu nula, mi hnehchhiah, i hlim leh tawh lo ang: tho la, Kitim ramah kai rawh; chutah pawh chuan chawlhna reng reng i hmu chuang lo ang,\" a ti a.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> En teh, Kaldai-ho ram hi; he'ng mite hi an awm tawh lo: Assuria mi chuan thlalera ram sate tan a ruat tawh a ni: an in sangte chu an sa a, chuta lal inte chu an tiboral a, inchhiaah a siam ta.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Tarsis lawng liante u, chiau vak vak rawh u: in kulhbing chu tihchhiatin a awm tak hi.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Tin, chu mi niah chuan heti hi a ni ang a, tura khua chu, lal pakhat kum chhiara, kum sawmsarih chhung chu theihnghilhin a awm ang: kum sawmsarih ral hnuah chuan nawhchizuar hlaa an sawi angin tura khaw chungah chuan a la thlang ang.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> nang nawhchizuar, mite theihnghilh tawh hnu, tingang la la, tual fang rawh; tingrang kai la, hla tam tak sa rawh, hriata i awm leh theihna turin.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Tin, kum sawmsarih a ral hnu chuan LALPA chuan tura khua chu a tlawh ang a, a sumdawnna a chhunzawm leh ang; khawvel ram tinah a inzuar leh ang.Tin, a sum deh chhuah leh a hlawh chu LALPA hmaa awmte tan a ni dawn si a, hnianghnara an eiah leh, silhfen ropui tak an neih theihna'n.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Tin, a sum deh chhuah leh a hlawh chu LALPA hmaa awmte tan a ni dawn si a, hnianghnara an eiah leh, silhfen ropui tak an neih theihna'n."
		},
		"24": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ngai teh, LALPA chuan lei hi a tiruakin, a tiram dawn a, a khaikhup ang a, a awmate chu a tidarh dawn.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Tin, vantlang chunga tih angin, puithiam chungah pawh tih a ni ang; bawihpa chunga a awm angin, a pu chungah pawh a aw ang; bawihnu chunga awm angin, a pi chungah pawh a awm ang; leitu chunga a awm angin, hralhtu chungah pawh a awm ang; puktirtu chunga a awm angin, puktu chungah pawh a awm ang; a pung uma puktirtu chunga a awm angin, a hnena a pung petu chungah pawh a awm ang.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Lei hi tihruah fai kelh leh tihchhiat fai kelhin a awm ang; chu thu chu LALPA'n a sawi tawh si a.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> lei hi a tapin a chuai e, khawvel hi a chauin a chuai e, leia mi chungnungte hnuaiah chuan a chau ve.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Lei hi a awmnate hnuaiah chuan a bawlhhlawh zo ta; dante chu an bawhchhiat a, thuruat chu an tihdanglam a, kumkhaw thuthlung chu an bawhchhiat avangin.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> chuvangin anchhe lawhnain lei hi a ei zo a, a awmate chu thiam loh chantirin an awm ta: chuvangin leia awmte chu an kang hlum a, mi tlem te chauh an la awm.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Uain thar chu a tap e, grep hrui chu a chau ve, thinlunga hlim zawng zawngte chu an rum e.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Khuangtete hlimna chu a reh e, lawm taka awmte thawm chu a tawp e, tingtang hlim ri chu a reh e.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Hla sa chungin uain an in lo ang; zu chu a intute tan kha tak a ni ang.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Buaina khawpui chu tihchimin a awm ta: tumah reng reng an luh lohna'n in tin, kharin a awm ta.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Uain avangin kawtthlerahte chuan tap thawm a awm a; hlimna zawng zawng tihthimin a awm a, he ram hlimna hi a bo ta.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Khawpuiah chuan tiauna hnutchhiahin a awm a, a kulh kawngkhar chu vuak chhiatin a awm ta.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Lei lailia mi tin zingah hetiang hian a la awm dawn si a, oliv thing vuak hnua rah a la awm thin ang leh, grep lawh hnua grep hmaih lawh tur a la awm thin ang mai hian.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> chungte chuan an aw an chhuah ang a, an au vang; LALPA ropuina avangin tuifinriat atangin ring takin an au ve.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Chumi avang chuan LALPA chu khaw chhak lamah chawimawi rawh u, LALPA, Israel ho Pathian hing ngei chu, tuifinriatkam ruamahte chuan chawimawi rawh u.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Kawlkil tawpa hla sakte kan hria, \"Mi flte hnenah ropuina awm rawh se\" tih hla hi. Nimahsela, kei chuan, \"Ka cher tawlh tawlh a, ka cher tawlh talwh a, ka chung a pik e! vervek taka titute chuan vervek takin an ti a;a ni, vervek taka titute chuan vervek tak takin an ti,\" ka ti a.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Aw leia awm, hlauhawmna te, khuarkhurum te, thangte chu i chungah a awm e.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Tichuan heti hi a ni ang a, hlauhawm thawm atanga tlana chu, khuarkhurumah a tla ang a; khuarkhurum chhung ata chhuak chhova chu, thangah a awk ang: chung lama tukverhte chu hawnin a awm si a, leilung nghahchhante chu a nghing bawk a ni.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Lei hi a keh chhe vek a, lei hi tihralin a awm zo a, lei hi nasa takin a nghing a.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Lei hi zu rui mi angin a pai hlawk hlawk ang a, bawkte sawi angin a sawi luai luai ang; a bawhchhiatna chu a chungah rit takin a awm ang a, tichuan a tlu ang a, a tho leh tawh lo ang.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Tin, chumi niah chuan heti hi a ni ang a, LALPA chuan chung lama mi chungnunghopawl lian tak chu a hrem ang, leia lei lalte nen.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Tin, mi tangho khuarkhuruma hruai khawma an awm angin chungho chu hruai khawmin an awm ang a, tan inah khungin an awm ang a, ni rei tak hnuah chuan hremin an awm ang.Chumi hunah chuan thla khi zak takin a awm ang a, ni khi mualpho takin a awm ang; sipaihoi-te LALPA chu Zion tlang leh, Jerusalem khuaah leh, a upaho hmaah chuan, ropui takin lalah a awm dawn si a.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Chumi hunah chuan thla khi zak takin a awm ang a, ni khi mualpho takin a awm ang; sipaihoi-te LALPA chu Zion tlang leh, Jerusalem khuaah leh, a upaho hmaah chuan, ropui takin lalah a awm dawn si a."
		},
		"25": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Aw LALPA, nang chu ka Pathian i ni a; ka chawimawi ang chia, i hming ka fak ang; thil mak tak, hmasanga remruatte chu, rinawm tak thutakin i ti si a.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Khawpui pawh lei pawngah i chantir a; khua kulhpui nei pawh khaw chhiaah i chantir a; ramdang mite lal in pawh khua loah i chantir si a. Engtikah mah sakin a awm leh tawh lo ang.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Chuvangin mi chak takte chuan an chawimawi ang chia, hnam hlauhawm takte khawpui huan an hlau vang che.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Mi hlauhawmte thaw chu thlipuiin bang a nam sawk sawk anga a lo awm laite hian, nang chu mi rethei tan kulhbing, pachhe mangan lai atan kulhbing, thlipui laka inhumhimna, ni sa hliahna i ni si thin a.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Hmun rova khaw lum chu i tireh thin ang hian, ram dang mite thawm chu i tireh ang; khaw lum chu chhum hliaha tihrha a awm thin ang hian, mi hlauhawmho hla sa chu tihrehin a awm ang.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Tin, he tlangah hian sipaihote LALPA chuan mi tinreng tan thil thautein ruai a theh ang, uainte a fe nena inchiah reng, thil thau takte thlinga khat, uainte a fe nena inchiah reng tha taka thlir fai chu.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Tin, mi tinreng an vawm khuhna pawn lam leh, hnam tinreng an khuhna chu he tlangah hian a tichhia ang.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Thihna chu a lem hlen ta; Lalpa PATHIAN chuan mi zawng zawng hmai ata chu mittuite a hru fai ang a; a mite hmingchhiatna chu leilung luah zawng zawng ata a la bo ang: LALPA'n chu chu a sawi tawh si a.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Tin, chu mi niah chuan, \"Ngai teh u, hei hi kan Pathian a nih hi; ani hi kan nghak reng a, tichuan min chhandam ang: hei hi LALPA chu a nih hi; ani hi kan nghak reng a, a chhandamnaah chuan kan lawmin kan hlim ang,\" an ti ang.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> He tlangah hian LALPA kut chu a innghat ang a, Moab chu, buhpawl hi ekdur thlia rah beha a awm thin ang hian, ama hmunah rah behin a awm dawn si a.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Tichuan tuihleuhtun tui hleuh tura a vai ang hian, chu mi zingah chuan a kutte a vai ang: tin, a chapona chu akut vervekna chawpin LALPA'n a dah hniam ang.Tin, i kulh bangte in sang kulhpui chu a tichimin, a dah hniamin, leiah, vaivut thleng khawp rawkin a titlu ta.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Tin, i kulh bangte in sang kulhpui chu a tichimin, a dah hniamin, leiah, vaivut thleng khawp rawkin a titlu ta."
		},
		"26": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Chumi niah chuan Juda-ho ramah he hla hi an sa ang: \"Khawpui nghet tak ken nei a; ani chuan chhandamna chu kulh bangte leh kulhpuite tan a ruat ang.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Hnam fel thutak zawmtu chu a luh theihna turin kulh kawngkharte chu hawng rawh u.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> I chunga rilru nghattu chu, nangmah a rin che avangin, thlamuang tak maia awm turin i veng ang.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> LALPA chu kumkhuain ring rawh u: LALPA JEHOVA-ah chuan kumkhaw lungpui a awm si a.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ani chuan sang taka awmte chu a titlawm ta si a, khawpui sang ak chu chu chu dah hniam a, lei thleng rawkin a dah hniam a vaivut thleng zawkin a titlu a.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ke chuan a rap bet ang; retheite ke leh pachhiate pen ngei chuan.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Mi fel kawng chu dikna a ni a: nang thinlung dik tak pu chuan mi fel kawng chu i tirual thin.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> A ni aw LALPA, i rorelna kawngah chuan kan nghak reng chia; kan nunna duhzawng chu i hming lam leh nangmah hriat rengna lam hi a ni.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ka nunnain zanah ka duh chia; a ni, ka kawchhunga ka thlarau awm hian zing takah ka zawng ang che; i rorelnate chu leia a lo awm apiangin khawvela awmte chuan felna chu an zir thin si a.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Mi suaksual chu duhsakin awm mah se la, felna a zir chuang hlei lawng e: dikna ramah chuan dik lo takin a ti ang a, LALPA ropuina a hmu chuang lo ang.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> \"LALPA, i ban i phar a, an hmu si lo; mite tan i thahnemngaihna chu hmu se, an zak ang; a ni, nangmah dotute chu meiin a kang rla ang.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> LALPA, nangin remna min ruatsak ang: nangin kan hna zawng zawng pawh min thawhsak si a.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Aw LALPA kan Pathian, nangmah chang ni loin lal dangte pawhin kan chungah thu an nei tawh thin a, nimahsela nangma tanpui ngeiin i hming hi kan lam tawh ang.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Anni chu an thi ta a, an nung tawh lo ang; an ral thi ta a, an nung tawh lo vang; an ral ta a, an tho tah lo ang; chuvangin nangin anni chu i hremin i tichhia a, an hriat rengna zawng zawng pawh i tiboral ta.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> He hnam hi i tipung ta a, aw LALPA, he hnam hi i tupung ta; nang chu chawimawiin i awm ta: he ram hi a ramri zawng zawng i tizau ta.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> \"LALPA, an mangan laiin an zawng ruai thin chia, i hremna chu an chunga a tlak laiin an tawngtai mawlh mawlh a.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Hmeichhe nau pai, hrin hun hnai tawh chu, a na thin a, nau vei naa a chiau vawng vawng thin ang hian; aw LALPA, keini pawh i hmaah kan awm thin kha.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Nau kan pai a, kan na a, thli ang lek kan hrin kha: leiah hian chhan chhuahna lam reng kan tikaw lo a; khawvela awmho lah an tlu hek lo.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> I mitthite chu an nung leh ang a; ka mi ruangte chu an tho leh ang. Vaivuta awmte u, harh u la, hlim takin zai rawh u:I daifim chu thlaite daifim ang a ni a, lei hian mitthite chu a paih chhuak dawn si a,\" tih hi.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Hawh u, ka mite u, in pindan chhungahte lut u la, in kawngte chu inkhar khum rawh u: lungnih lohna hi a kian hma loh chu mitkhapkar lek biru rawh u.Ngai teh u, LALPA chu, an sualna avanga leia awmte hrem turin a awmna ata a lo chhuak dawn a ni: lei pawh hian a thisente chu a tilang ang a, mi an thahte chu a khuh tawh lo ang.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Ngai teh u, LALPA chu, an sualna avanga leia awmte hrem turin a awmna ata a lo chhuak dawn a ni: lei pawh hian a thisente chu a tilang ang a, mi an thahte chu a khuh tawh lo ang."
		},
		"27": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Chumi niah chuan LALPA chuan, a khandaih hriam tha tak, lian pui, rinawm tak chuan, liviathan rulpui chak tak leh liviathan rulpui chhawkawlh nghut chu a hrem ang a, tuipuia drakon awm chu a that bawk ang.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Chu mi niah chuan, grep huan mawi tak chawimawiin hla sa rawh u.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Kei LALPA hi a vengtu ka ni; mitkhapkar tinin tui ka leih ang a, tuma'n an khawih lohna'n achhun azanin ka veng ang.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> ka thin a rim tawh lo va: buar leh hnimhlingneite lo awm mah se ka thlo veng a, hmun khatah ka hal ral ang.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Kei min rem duh chuan ka angchhungah lo tlu lut se, mi rem rawh se.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Hun lo la thleng turah chuan Jakob-ho chuan zung an kai ang a; Israel-ho chu an kuhmumin an par ang: tichuan lei chung hi rahin a tikhat ang.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Amah vawtute a vuak ang takin amah chu a vaw ve em ni? A nih loh leh, ama thahte thahna ang takin amah chu thahin a awm em ni?",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Amah chu i kal botir laiin a tawk lekin amah chu i hnial a; khawchhak thli tleh niah chuan a thaw na tak chuan amah chu a len sawn ta.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> chuvangin hei hian Jakob-ho khawlohna chu tlenfai a ni ang a, hei hi an sual kal bopuina rah hlir a ni; Aserte leh ni lemte chu tho tawh lo tur khawpin maicham lung zawng zawng chu tlak lung den phel ram rum ang maia an siam hi.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Khua kulpui nei chu a khawhar a, awmna mi hnuchhawn leh kalsan hnu a ni ta si a, thlaler ang maiin: chutah chuan bawng no a tla ang a, chutah bawk chuan a bawk ang a, a tangte chu a ei ang.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> A zarte chu a vuai hun chuan thliahin a awm ang; hmeichheho an lo kal ang a, an hla mai ang: hriat theihna reng reng nei lo mite an ni si a; chuvangin an siamtu chuan anni chu a khawngaih lo ang a, anmahni dintu chuan anni chu a duh reng reng a duhsak lo ang.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Tin, chumi niah chuan heti hi a ni ang a, LALPA chuan, lui kuang khata luang dul dul atangin, Aigupta luite thlengin, a rah a vaw thla ang a, tichuan, aw Israela thlahte u, a mal mala chhiarin in am ang.Tin, chumi niah chuan heti hi a ni ang a, tawtawrawt lian pui an ham ang a; tichuan Assuria rama boral lek lekhote leh, Aigupta rama hnawh chhuahho awmte chu an lo kal ang a; Jerusalem khuaa tlang thianghlimah chuan LALPA chu chibai an buk ang.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Tin, chumi niah chuan heti hi a ni ang a, tawtawrawt lian pui an ham ang a; tichuan Assuria rama boral lek lekhote leh, Aigupta rama hnawh chhuahho awmte chu an lo kal ang a; Jerusalem khuaa tlang thianghlimah chuan LALPA chu chibai an buk ang."
		},
		"28": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ephraim-ho zu ruihmangte chapona lallukhum chung leh, an mawina ropui pangpar chuai mek, uain chiahhneha awmho ruam tha takin a khum chung chu a pik e!",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Ngai teh, LALPA chuan mi chak thiltithei tak a nei a; ani chuan, rial nasa tak tla dur dur, thlipui thil tichhe rem rum ang leh, tuilian nasa tak liam zur zur ang maiin, leiah a paih chawrh ang.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ephraim-ho zu ruihmangte chapona lallukhum chu rah behin a awm ang :",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> an mawina ropui pangpar chuai mek, ruam tha takin a khum chu, nipui hmaa theipui hmin hmasa ber, a entuin a hmuh a, a kuta a awm veleha a ei zawh mai htin ang chu a ni ang.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Chumi niah chuan sipaihote LALPA chu, a mi la awm chhungte tan ropuina lallukhum leh mawina lukum te,",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> rorel tura thua tan rorelna thlarau te, kulh kawngkhar bula rawn beiho dangkirtute tan chaknate a ni ang.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Nimahsela chungte pawh chu uain avangin an thle an thle a, zu avangin an pai an pai a; puithiamte leh zawlneite chu zu avangin an thle an thle a, uain lem zawhin an awm a, zu avangin an pai an pai a; inlarna thu-ah an thle an thle thin a, rorelna thu-ah an pai an pai thin.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Hmun fai reng reng awm lo khawpin dawhkan zawng zawng chu lauk leh thil bawlhhlawhin a khat a ni.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Hriatna lam chu tu hi nge a zirtir dawn tehchai: Thuchah chu tu hi nge a hriattir dawn tehchai: Hnute hnek bang hlimte leh hnute hnektir tawh lohte hi em ni?",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Thununna thu chunga thununna thu chherchuan a, thununna thu chunga thununna chherchhuan a; dan chunga dan chherchhuan a, dan chunga dan chherchhuan a; hetah tlem te, sawtah tlem te tih hlir a ni si a.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> A ni, nimahsela hmui danglam pu mi hmangin, tawng hrangin, he'ng mite hnenah hian thu a sawi tawh zawk ang:",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> \"Hei hi a ni, chawlhna chu ni, hahte chu chawlhtir rawh u! hei hi a ni, intihharhna chu ni,\" a tihate chu: nimahsela an ngaithla duh si lo.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Chuvangin, an kal a, zangthala an tluk a, an keh sawm a, thanga an awh a, mana an awm theihna turin, LALPA thu chu anniho tan chuan, thununna thu chunga thununna thu chherchhuan a, thununa thu chunga thununna thu chherchhuan a; dan chunga dan chherchhuan a, dan chunga dan chherchhuan a; hetah tlem te, sawtah tlem te tih hlir a ni mai ang.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Chumi avang chuan, mi hmusit hmang mite u, he mite, Jerusalem khuaa awmho, rorelsaktute u, LALPA thu hi hre rawh u:",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> \"Thihna lakah thu kan thlung ta, Seol nen thu kan intiam ta; vuakna tui lian liam chu a luan tlang hunah pawh keini thleng chuan a luang lo ang; dawt thute kan inhumhimna'n kan hmang a, dawt hnuaiah kan biru ta si a,\" in tih avangin,",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> chuvang chuan Lalpa PATHIAN chuan heti hian a sawi: \"Ngai teh, lung, lung riah hnu, a kila lung hlu tak phum nghet tak chu, Zion-ah chuan lungphum atan ka rem hi: a ringtu chu a hmanhmawh lo ang.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> rorelna fel chu a tihngilna hruiah ka hmang ang a, felna chu darmumkhaiah ka hmang ang: rial chu inhumhimna dawt thute chu a chhu bo vek ang a,t uite chuan bihrukna chu a chim pil ang.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Tin, thihna laka in thu thlun chu phelhin a awm ang a, Seol nena in thu intiam pawh chu a ding chuak lo ang; vuakna tui lian liam chu a luan tlang hunah, chu i hunah chuan a rah behin in awm ang.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> A luan tlang apiangin a la zel ang che u; atuk atuk tin, achhun achhunzanin, a luang tlang dawn si a: thuchah awmze hriat chu thil rapthlak hlir a ni ang,\" tiin.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Khum chu thluanna'n a tawi lutuk si a, puanthuah chu inkhuhna'n a te lutuk bawk si.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> A hna, a hna danglam chu, a thawh theihna'n leh, a thiltih, a thiltih danglam chu, a hlen theiana'n, LALPA chu, Perazim tlanga a tho ang khan, a tho dawn si a, Gibeon ruama a thinur ang khan a thinur dawn a ni.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Chutichuan mi hmusit hmangtute ni tawh suh u, chutilochuan in kawlbunte chu rinawm takin an siam dah ang e: tawpna, tawpna thleng ngei tura ruat tlat chu, lei pum pui chunga a thlen tur thu Lalpa, sipaihote LALPA hnen atang chuan ka hre si a.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Beng chhi u la, ka aw hi hre rawh u; ngaithla u la, ka thu sawi hi hre rawh u.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Leilettu chuan chi thehna'n lei a let reng ngai em ni? A lei tlangte chua tikehin a tisawm reng ngai em ni?",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> A chung chu a chawh rual zawhin mohuri-te chu a theh darh lo em ni? Zira te pawh a theh lo em ni? Buh te pawh a tlarin, barlite pawh a hmun ruatah, vai buhtunte pawh a vau hrulah a tuh thin lo em ni?",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> A Pathian chuan ani chu fel takin a thununin a zirtir thin si a.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Mohuri chu buh chilna khawl hriamin an chil ngai si lo a, zira chungah chuan tawlailir ke chu an lirhtir ngai hek lo; mohuri chu tiangin an vua a, zira chu talhtumin an vaw zawk thin a ni.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Chhang siamna buh chu rawtsawmin a awm thin a, kumkhuain a vaw reng dawn si lo: a tawlailir ke leh a sakawrte chuan tidarh mah se la, a rawt sawmtir ngai lo.Chung pawh chu sipaihote LALPA, inrawnna kawnga mi mak tak leh, finna kawnga mi tha tak lakah chuan a chhuak a ni.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Chung pawh chu sipaihote LALPA, inrawnna kawnga mi mak tak leh, finna kawnga mi tha tak lakah chuan a chhuak a ni."
		},
		"29": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> E Ariel , Ariel, Davida awm hmun khuarna khua! Kumah kum belh rawh u; kutte chu lo thleng leh rawh se:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> chumi hunah chuan Ariel hi ka timangang ang a, tichuan sunna leh tahna a awm ang:tin, a ni chu ka tan Ariel ang a ni ang.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Tin, nangmah bei tumin i velah ka ep ang chia, kulh siamin ka hual vel bawk ang chia, bei tur chein hual velna kulhbingte ka siam ang.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Tichuan tihtlukin i awm ang a, lei hnuai atangin thu i sawi ang a, i tawng chu vaivut zingah zawitein a ri chhuak ang; i aw chu ramhuai aienthiam zawl aw ang lekin lei hnuai atangin a chhuak ang a, i tawng chu vaivut zing atangin a lo chhuak se se ang.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Nimahsela nangmah dotu mipuite chu vaivut dip tak angin an awm ang a, mi hlauhawmho mipuite chu buhsi boral thinte ang hian an awm bawk ang: a ni, chu chu mitkhapkar loah a lo awm thut ang.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Khawpui ri te, lirnghing te, ri nasa tak te, thawngaleivir te, thlipui te, thil kanralhmang meialh tein anni chu sipaihote LALPA hremin an awm ang.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Tichuan Ariel dotu hnam zawng zawng mipuiho, amah leh a kulhbing beiotute zawng zawng leh amah timangangtu zawng zawngte chu, mumang ang lek an i ang, zana inlarna ang lek hi.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Mi riltamin mumang a neihin chaw a lo ei thin a, nimahsela a han harh a, a kua chu a lo la ruak ang hi a ni ang: a nih loh leh, mi tuihalin mumang a neihin tui a lo in thin a, nimahsela a han harh a, a lo la chavuin tui a la chak ang hi a ni ang: Zion tlang beitu, hnam zawng zawng mipuiho chu, chutiang chu an ni ang.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ding reng u la, mak ti rawh u, nuam leng u la, mitdelin awm rawh u: an rui a, nimahsela uain avang a ni lo; an pai an pai a, nimahzela zu avang a ni lo.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> LALPA chuan mut duhna thlarau chu in chungah a leih bua a, in mit, zawlneite chu, a maimitchhintir a; in lu, hmu theitute chu, a khuh ta si a.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Tichuan inlarna reng reng in tan lehkhabu char tlata thu ang a ni ta, chu chu miten lehkha thiam mi hnenah \"Khawngaih takin hei hi chhiar rawh,\" tiin an pe thin a: tin, ani chuan, \"Ka chhiar thei lo, char tlat a nih hi,\" a ti thin a:",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> tin, lehkhabu chu lehkha thiam lo mi hnenah, \"Khawngaih takin hei hi chhiar rawh,\" tiin a pe thin a: tin, ani chuan, \"Lehkha ka thiam lo,\" a ti thin.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Tin, Lalpa chuan, \"He mite hian mi rawn hnaih a, an ka leh an hmuiin mi chawimawi thin tak a, nimahsela an thinlung chu ka hlatah an sawn a, an mi tihna chu mihring thupek an inzirtir mai chu a ni:",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> chuvangin, ngai teh, he mite zingah hian thilmak tak mai chu: tichuan an mi fingte finna chu a boral tawh ang a, an mi bengvarte hriatna chu thupin a awm tawh ang,\" a ti a.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> An remruat chu LALPA laka thup tura thuk taka zawngtute chu an chung a pik e! an thiltihte chu thim hnuaiah a awm a, \"Tuin nge min hmu ang? Tuin nge hriat pawh min hria ang?\" an ti a.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Thilte hi in tiletling zo vek thin e a! Bel vawtu chu bellei ang leka ngaihin a awm dawn em ni, thil siam chuan a siamtu chu, \"Ani mi siam ka ni hlei nem,\" a tih ni? A nih loh leh, thil din chuan a dintu chu \"Hriatna reng a nei lo,\" a tih ni?",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Rei lo te chinah a ni lo'm ni? Lebanon chu lei tha tak hmuna chantirin a awm dawn a, lei tha tak hmun chu ram ngawa ngaihin a awm dawn?",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Chumi niah chuan bengngawngte chuan lehkhabu thute chu an bengin an hre tawh ang a, mitdel mitte chuan thim hnuai leh thim zing atangin a hmu tawh ang.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Thuhnuairawlhte pawh chuan LALPAah chuan an hlimna chu an tipung tawh ang a, mihring zinga retheite chu Israel-ho Mi Thianghlimah chuan an lawm tawh ang.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Mi hlauhawm chu engmah loa siamin a awm tawh a, hmusittu chu a reh tawh a, khawlohna nghakheltute zawng zawng chu tihboralin an awm tawh si a:",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> chungte chuan mi chu thupawi thu-ah thiltisualtuah an sia thin a, kulh kawngkaa ziltu awhna'n thang an kam thin a, mi fel chu thil engmah lo maiin an pumpelhtir thin.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Chuvangin LALPA, Abrahama tlantu chuan Jakoba chhungte chungchang thuah heti hian a ti: \"Jakob-ho chu tunah chuan an mualpho tawh lo ang a, an hmai chu a dang tawh hek lo ang.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> An fa, ka kut chhuakte chu, an zingah an hmuhin, ka hming chu an tithianghlim tawh zawk ang; a ni, Jakob-ho Mi Thianghlim chu an tithianghlim ang a, Israel-ho Pathian chu an tih tawh ang.Thlarauva vakbote pawh chuan an lo hre thiam tawh ang a, mi phunnawite chuan thu zirtir chu an zir tawh ang,\" tiin.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Thlarauva vakbote pawh chuan an lo hre thiam tawh ang a, mi phunnawite chuan thu zirtir chu an zir tawh ang,\" tiin."
		},
		"30": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> LALPA chuan, \"Fa helhmangho chu an chung a pik e! chungho chuan mi an rawn a, kei erawh chu mi rawn si lo a, an sual chunga sual an belhchhahna turin khuhnain an khuh a, ka thlarau thuin erawh chuan an khuh si lo a.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Pharaoa chaknaa intichak tur leh, Aigupta hlim ring turin, ka ka zawt si loin Aigupta rama chhuk tumin an kal a.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Chuvangin Pharaoa chakna chu in mualphona a ni tah ang a, Aigupta hlim in lo ring hi in zahna a ni tawh ang.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> A mi liante chu Zoan khuaah an awm a, a palaite chuan Janes khua an thleng ta si a.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> An tan hnemhnanna reng nei lo mi, tanpui ni lo a, hnemhnanna nei mi ni hek lo a, zah leh hmingchhiatna ni zawkte chu, an zain an la zahpui ang,\" a ti a.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Chhim rama sate phur rit chu. Manganna leh thlaphanna ram, sakeibakneinu leh sakeibakneipa, rulmuk leh rul alh thlawk thei chhuahna chu, an sum chu sabengtung no chungah te, an rote chu sanghawng sei zang pawngahte phurhtirin, an tana hnemhnanna nei lo mite hnenah pek turin, an kal tlang dual dual a.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Aigupta chuan sawt lo tak leh tangkai lo takin a tanpui thin si a: chuvangin a ni, ani chu, \"Rahab thu hle hle-i,\" ka vuah ni.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Tunah kal la, chung chu an hmaa lehkha ziakna phekah ziak la, lehkhabuah pawh ziak rawh, tun hnua kumkhaw tlaitluan atan a nih theihna'n.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Chungho chu mi helhmang te, fa dam theite, fa LALPA dan ngaithla duh lo te, an ni si a:",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> hmutheitute hnena, \"Hmutheitute hnena, \"Hmu suh u,\" zawlneite hnena, \"Thil dikte min hrilh lawk suh u, thilnuam lam kan hnenah sawi rawh u, bumna thu hrilh lawk rawh u:",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> kawng loah kal rawh u, kawng sirah peng rawh u, Israel-ho Mi Thainghlim chu kan hma ata hi tibo rawh u,\" ti thintute chu.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Chumi avang chuan Israel-ho Mi Thianghlim chuan heti hian a sawi a, \"He thu hi in hmusit avang leh hnechhiahna leh luhlulna in rin a, a chunga in innghah avangin,",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> he khawlohna hi nangni tan chuan lung bang sang tak chhe lai, chim lek lek, pawng pur, vwailehkhatah mitkhapkar loa chhe rup tur ang hi a ni ang.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Tichuan belvawtu bel an tikeh sawm ang hian, zuah awm hlek loa keh sawmin a them zingah lampei thuka mei lakna tur emaw, tuikhura tui thlana tur emaw pawh awm lo khawpin, a tikeh sawm ang,\" tiin.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Lalpa PATHIAN, Israel-ho Mi Thianghlim chuan, heti hian a sawi tawh si a, \"Kir leha chawla awmin, chhandamin in awm ang a, muang taka awmnaah leh ring taka awmnaah hian in chakna a awm ang,\" tiin: nimahsela in duh si lo.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> \"Ni lo, sakawr chung chuangin ka tlan dur dur ang,\" in ti zawk si a, chuvangin in tlan dur dur ngei ang: \"Thil cha tak chungah kan chuang ang,\" tin, ti a; chuvangin a umtu tur che u chu chak tak an ni ang.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Mi pakhat hrawkin mi sangkhat an tlan dur dur ang a: mi panga hrawkin in tlan dur dur ang: a tawpah chuan tlang chhipa pholeng tar ang leh, mual chunga chhinchhiahna awm anga hnutchhiahin in la awm mai ang.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Chuvangin LALPA chuan a khawngaih theihna tur che uin a nghak ang a, chuvangin a lainat theihna tur che uin chawimawiin a awm ang: LALPA chu rorel felna Pathian a ni si a; amah nghaktute zawng zawng chu an eng a thawl e.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Mite chu Jerusalem-a Ziona-ah chuan an awm dawn si a: in tap leh tawh lo ang; in au thawmah chuan ani chuan a khawngaih ngei ngei ang che u a; a hriat veleh a chhang ang che u.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> LALPA chuan manganna chaw leh hrehawmna tui pe che u mah se la, in zirtirtute chu biruin an awm tawh lo ang a, in mitin in zirtirtute chu a hmu zawk tawh ang:",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> tin, ding lama in pen veleh emaw, vie lama in pen veleh emaw, in bengin in hnung lama thu, \"Hei hi kawng a nih hi, tah hian kal rawh u,\" tiin a hre zel ang.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Tin, in tangka milem siam tangka tia cheina leh, in rangkachak milem chhun rangkachak tuia luanna chu in tibawrhbang ang a: thil bawlhhlawh angin in paih tawh ang a, a hnenah chuan, \"Kal bo daih rawh,\" ion ti ang.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Tichuan ani chuan i buh chi leia in tuh tur tan chuan ruah tui chu a pe ang a; leia thil tote pawh chu chawh a pe ang, chu chu tha tak, hlawk tak a ni ang: chumi niah chuan in rante chu ran tlatna hmun zau takahte chuan an tla ang,",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> bawngpa leh sabengtung no lei letutte chuan chaw leh sabengtung no lei lettute chuan chaw al, suahdur leh sisepa tihfai sa, an ei bawk ang.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Tin, inthahna nasa tak nia, ralven in sangte chu a chi ni chuan, tlang sang tinah leh mual pawng sang tinah chuan luipuite leh luite tui luangte a lo awm ang.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Chu lo pawh chu LALPA chuan a mite sil chu a tua a, an sahna pem chu a tihdam niah chuan, thla eng chu ni eng tlukin a awm tawh ang a, ni eng chu a lehsarihin, ni sarih chhung eng tlukin, a awm tawh ang.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Ngai teh, LALPA hming chu, a thinurnaa alh hluah hluain meikhu chhah mup chho ngut ngut zingah chuan, hla tak atangin a lo kal e: a hmuite chu lungnih lohnain a khat a, a lei chu thil kanralhmang mei ang a ni a:",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> a thaw chu, boralna thlangraa hnam tin thlei turin, lui nghawng thleng zeta a kuang liam dul dul ang a ni. Tin, mi tin kaah chuan hruai sualtirna hmuh dinna hrui a awm ang,",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Tin, zana kut thianghlima an kut laia hla an sa angin hla in sa ang a; LALPA tlanga Israel-ho Lungpui hnen thlang tura phenglawng nen an kal laia thinlung hlimna an nei angin thinlung hlimna pawh in nei ang.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Tin, LALPA chuan a aw ropui tak chu a hriattir tawh ang a, a thinurna nasa tak leh thil kanralhmang meialhin, thlipui leh ruahpui leh rialin, a kut thlak dan chu a entir tawh ang.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> LALPA aw avang chuan Assuria mi, talhtuma mi vaw thintu chu, tihkeh sawmin a awm dawn tawh si a.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Ani chu tiang ruat saa LALPA'n a vuak apiangin khuang tete leh tingtangte nen a vua ang a: a tiang leka inbeinaahte chuan anmahni a bei ang.Tophet khuar zau tak leh thuk tak thing chheh khah lal halna tur an buatsaih daih tawh a, a tikang turin LALPA chuan kat lui anga luang mei a thaw chhuak ang.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Tophet khuar zau tak leh thuk tak thing chheh khah lal halna tur an buatsaih daih tawh a, a tikang turin LALPA chuan kat lui anga luang mei a thaw chhuak ang."
		},
		"31": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Aigupta rama tanpuina zawng tura zuk kal a, sakawrte chunga rinna nghat a, a tam avanga tawlailirte leh an chak em avanga sakawr chung chuang mite ring a, Israel-ho Mi Thianghlim lam en si lo a, LALPA pawh rawn si lote chu an chung a pik e!",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Rawn lo mah se la ani pawh fing tak a sin, thil tha lo a rawnt hlentir ang a, a thute chu a lamlet lo ang: thil tha lo titute chhungte bei turin a thao zawk ang a, thil tisualtute tanpuina do turin a tho bawk ang.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Aigupta mite zawng Pathian an ni lo a, mihring mai an ni a; an sakawrte chu thlarau a ni lo a, tisa mai a ni a: tichuan LALPA'n a kut a phar hunah chuan a tanpuitu chu a pai thlawk thlawk ang a, atanpuia pawh chu a tlu ang a, an za chuan an boral tlang hlawm ang.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> LALPA chuan heti hian ka hnenah a sawi si a, \"Sakeibaknei leh sakeibaknei vanglaiin a sa hauh lai chuan beram vengtu tam tak a bei turin koh chhuahin awm mah se la, an aw chu ahlau dawn lo a, an bengchhen avangin a tiam chuang dawn hek lo ang hian, sipaihote lalpa chu Zion tlangah leh a mual pawngah bei turin a lo chhuk dawn a ni.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Savate an bu chunga an thlawk an thlawk ang hian sipahote LALPA chua Jerusalem khua chu a veng ang; a vengin a chhan chuak ang a, akal hleni a humhim ang.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> \"Aw Israela thlahte u, nasa taka in helsan taka lam chu hawi leh tawh rawh u.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Chumi niah chuan mi tinin mahni tangka milemte, mahni rangkachak milemte, sualna atana nangmahni kuta in insiam chawpte chu an la paih bo dawn si a.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> \"Chu mi hunah chuan Assuria mi chu, mihring khandaiha tihthluk ni loin, khandaih tihthlukin a awm ang a; khandaih, mihringte ta ni loin, amah chu a ei zo ang: tin, khandaih lak aa a tlan bo ang a, a tlangvalte chu chhiahchawitu an lo ni tawh ang.Tin, a lungpui chu thil rapthlak avangin a boral ang a, a mi liante chu chhinchhiahna avangin an mangang tawh ang,\" tiin, LALPA, a mei Zion-a awma leh, a rawh tuina mei Jerusalema awma chuan a ti a.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Tin, a lungpui chu thil rapthlak avangin a boral ang a, a mi liante chu chhinchhiahna avangin an mangang tawh ang,\" tiin, LALPA, a mei Zion-a awma leh, a rawh tuina mei Jerusalema awma chuan a ti a."
		},
		"32": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ngai teh, fel taka rorel tur lal a lo awm ang a, dik taka tithin hotute an lo chhuak bawk ang.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Thlipui laka bikna hmun ang leh thlihrang laka inhumhimna ang a ni ang; thlalera lui luang ang leh ramrova lungpui lian tak hlim ang mai chu.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> An mit chuan chiang takin a hmu ang a, an beng pawhin fiah takin a hre tawh ang.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Rilrua hmanhmawh chuan hriat thiam a zir ang a, dangawkte pawh nal takin an tawng thei ang.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Mi sual chu tuma zah a kai lo ang a, mi duham chuan ngaihsan a hlawh hek lo ang.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Mi sual chuan thu a a chhak chhuak a, suahsualna dang tur a suangtuah a, a thiltih leh a kam chhuakte chu LALPA elsen zawng hlir a ni; riltamte ei tur a laksak a, tuihalte in tur a tihbuaksak thin.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Mi duham chu khawlo tak a ni; retheite chu dawt tichhe turin thil sual a phiar chhuak a, pachhiate pawh an diknaah pawh a dang tlat thin.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Mi tha erawh chuan dik takin thil a ti a, thu dik a tan tlat thin.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Hmeichhe nuam tawlte u, tho u la ka thu hi ngaithla teh u; fanu ngaihsamte u, ka thu sawiah hian beng chhi rawh u.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Hmeichhe ngaihdamte u, kum khat leh ni eng zat emaw chinah chuan in mangang tah ang: grep lawh tur lah a awm dawn si lo a, lawh khawm turah chuan engmah a haw dawn hek lo.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Hmeichhe awm mai maite u, khur rawh u; mi ngaihsamte u, mangang takin awm rawh u; inhliup u la, saruakah insiam u la, in kawngahte chuan saiip puan veng rawh u.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Lo duhawmte avang leh grep hrui rah duh mi avang chuan an awm an chum an chum ang.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ka mite ramah hian hnimhlingneite leh buarte chu a tla ang: a ni, khawpui hlimawm taka hlimna in zawng zawng chungahte chuan,",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Lal in chu kalsanin a awm dawn si a; mi tamna khawpui chu chhuahsanin a awm ang a; a mual pawng leh a ralven buk chu kumkhaw pukah te, ram sabengtung lawmna te, ran rual tlatna hmunte a ni ang;",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> chunglam atangin a thlarau a rawn pe leh ang a, thlaler chu lei tha tak hmunah a chang ang a, lei tha tak hmun chu ram ngawa ngaiha a awm hun chuan.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> rorel felna chu thlalerah chuan a cheng ang a, felna chu lei tha tak hmunah chuan a awm ang.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Tin, felna hnathawh chu remna a ni ang a, felnaa thil chhuak chu kumkhuaa muang taka awmna leh ring tlata awmna a ni ang.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Tichuan ka mite chu ralmuanga awmnaah leh a nghet takahte leh chawlhna hmun muanawm takahte chuan an awm tawh ang.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Nimahsela ram ngaw chu tithlu turin rial a tla dur dur ang a; khawpui chu tihtlawm derin a awm ang.Tui luanna zawng zawng kama chi theh thin a, bawngpa leh sabengtung thlah thintute u, in eng a thawl e.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Tui luanna zawng zawng kama chi theh thin a, bawngpa leh sabengtung thlah thintute u, in eng a thawl e."
		},
		"33": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Nang rawk tawk ngai si lo a, rawktu, vervek taka tih tawk ngai si lov a, vervek taka titu, i chung a pik e! Mi rawk i ban hunah, rawk i la tawk ve ang ;a vervek taka i tih zawh hunah, i chungah vervek takin an ti ang.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Aw LALPA, min khawngaih ang che; kan nghah reng che hi: tuk tin kan ban lo ni la, mangan hunah chuan min chhandamtu lo ni bawk ang che. Sa mur mur thawmah chuan mi tin an tlan bo ta a; nang i thawh meuh chuan hnam tin tihdarhin an awm ta.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> In sum rallaka lak tur pangangin thil a thiar khawm sup sup ang hian thiar khawmin a awm ang a khaukhuapte an zuang sup sup ang hian anniho chu sum chungah an zuang sup sup ang.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> LALPA chu chawisanin a awm ta; chung lamah khian a awm si a: ani chuan Zion chu rorel felna leh felnain a tikhat ta.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> I dam chhung chuan awm nghehna a awm ang a, chhandamna te, finna te, hriatnate a awm reuh vang: LALPA tihna chu a ro a ni.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ngai teh, an pasalthate chu pawn lamah an au a; remna palaite chu an tap zawih zawih a.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> lamliante chu a thing thiap thuap a, mi zin veivak chu an awm ta lo va: ani chuan thuthlung chu a bawhchhia a, khuate chu a hmusit a, mihring a ngaihsak tak lo.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ram chu a rapin a chau a: Lebanon chu a zakin a vuai a: Saron chu thlaler ang a ni ta; Baan leh Karmel chuan an hnahte an thing thla a.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> LALPA chuan, \"Tunah chuan ka tho ang a, tunah chuan chawisanin ka awm tawh ang.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Hnim ro in pai ang a, buh pawl in hring ang: in thaw chu nangmahni kang ral tur mei a ni.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Mi tinrengte chu chinai lung rawh ang, hnim hlingnei sam hnu meia an paih ang chu an ni ang,\" a ti a.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Hla taka awmte u, ka thiltih hi bengin lo hre rawh u, hnaitea awmte u, ka thiltihtheihzia hi hre rawh u.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Zion-a mi sual awmte chuan an hlau a; Pathian zah lo mite chu khurhnain a man ta. \"Kanralhmang mei, kumkhuaa alh chu, kan zingah tu nge tuar thei awm ang?\" an ti a.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Fel taka awma dik taka sawi thintu; hnehchhiahnate hlawkpuina reng reng lungtena, tham la duh loa kut thinsana, thisen chhuah thu ngaithla duh loa beng hup a, sualna reng reng en duh loa maimitchhing thina chu;",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> chu mi chu chunglamah a awm ang aL a kulhbing sang chu lungpui kulhbingte chu a ni ang a; a chaw chu a hnenah pek a ni ang a, atuite chu a awm ngei ngei ang.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> I mite chuan lal chu a mawinaah chuan an la hmu ang a, ram parh zau tak an la thlir ang.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> \"A chhiartu kha khawiah nge a awm tak? Chhiah chawi buktu kha khawiah nge a awm tak? Ralven in sangte chhiartu kha, khawiah nge a awm tak?\" tiin, i thinlungin thil rapthlak tak kha i ngaihtuah ang.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Mi kawlh ta, rawng ril tak i hriat theih loha tawng mite, tawng hrang i hriat thiam loha tawngte chu i hmu tawh lo ang.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Kan kutna khawpui Zion chu en teh: i mitte chuan Jerusalem chu awmna muanawm tak, puan in engtik maha sawn lo tur, a kaih marna khen engtik maha phawi lo tur, a kaihna hrui reng reng chat lo tur ang chu, a hmu ang.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> chutah chuan LALPA, lui zau tak tak leh lui tete awm thliah thluahna hmun chu, ropui takin kan hnenah a awm zawk ang: chung tui chungah chuan indona lawng lianpui kar fung nei mi reng reng a kal lo ang a, lawng lian rpui tak pawhin a kal pel hek lo ang.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> LALPA chu kan roreltu a ni a, LALPA chu dan min petu a ni a, LALPA chu kan lal a ni; ani chuan min chhandam ang.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> I hruite chu tihdulin a awm a; an puan zar ngul bul chu an tinghet thei lo a, puan zar chu an zar thei lo: chu mi lai tak chuan rallak i tum tam tak chu semin a awm a; kebaite pawhin rallak sum an la ta a.chu mi khuaa awm chuan, \"Ka dam lo e,\" a ti lo ang a, a chhunga mi awmte chu sual ngaihdamin an awm ang.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> chu mi khuaa awm chuan, \"Ka dam lo e,\" a ti lo ang a, a chhunga mi awmte chu sual ngaihdamin an awm ang."
		},
		"34": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Hnam tinte u, benga hre turin lo hnai rawh u; mi tinte u, ngaithla rawh u: lei leh a chhunga awm zawng zawngte chuan bengin hre rawh se; khawvel lah a chhung ata chhuak zawng zawngte nen.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> LALPA chuan hnam tinreng chungah chuan lungnih lohna a neiin, an sipaiho zawng zawng chungah chuan thinrimna a nei si a: anni chu a tiboral vek a, thahah a pe ta a.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> An zinga thahate chu paih chhuahin an awm ang a, an ruang rimchhia chu a chho vut vut ang a, tlangte chu an thisena tihtuiin a awm ang.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Vana awmho zawng zawngte khi tihralin an awm ang a, van khi lehkhabu zial mi an zial angin zialin a awm ang a: a awmho zawng zawngte khi, grep hrui ata a hnah a vuai a tla thin ang leh, theipui kung ata a hna vuai a tla thin ang hian, an vuai zoin an tla vek ang.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ka khandaih chuan vanah tlai takin a in ta si a; ngai teh, chu chu, rorel turin, Edom-ho chungah leh ka anchhelawh mite chungah chuan a chhuk ang.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> LALPA khandaih chu thisenin a tlai a, thaunaa tihthauin a awm ta, brem note leh kelte thisenin, berampa kal thautein: LALPA chuan Bozrah khuaah chuan inthawina a nei a, Edom ramah chuan thahna nasa tak a nei bawk si a.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Selepate pawh chu an ruala sah thlukin an awm ang a, bawngpate, bawngchalte nen; an ram chuan thisen a tui ang a, an vaivut chu thaunaa tihthauin a am ang.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> LALPA phuba lak ni a ni tah si a, Zion avanga inbeihna thua thungrulhna kum chu.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> A lui tuite chu lawng hnaia chartirin a awm ang a, a vaivut chu kata chantirin a awm bawk ang a, a ram chu lawng hnai kang hluah hluahah a chang ang.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Achhun azanin tihmihin a awm lo ang a; ameikhu chu kumkhuain a chho ngut ngut ang a; chhuan zamw chhung zawng zawng chuan chiain a awm reng ang a; kumkhua pawhin tuma'n an pal lo ang.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Tuivalawng leh sakuhin chumi ram chu an nei zawk ang a; chingpirinu leh choak chutah chuan an awm ang a: LALPA'n a tichhe vek ang a, hmun ruakah chuan a sahal a khai ang.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> An mi thate chu ram awp turin an ko ang a, nimahsela chutah chuan koh tur tumah an awm lo ang a; an mi lian zawng zawng chu engmah lo an ni ang.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> An lal inahte chuan hnihlingneite a to ang a, an kulhpui chhungahte chuan taiten leh buarte a to ang: sihalte awmnaah leh sava nghawngseite tan tuallai a ni ang.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Tin, thlalera ram sate chu chinghniate nen an intawk ang a, sathar chuan a thian a ko ang a; a ni, zan thil hlauhawm pui chuan chutah chuan awm hmun a khuar ang a, ama tan chawlh hmun tur a hmu ang.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Chutah chuan rulthal chuan bu a chhep ang a, a tui ang a, a keu ang a, a awp khawm ang: a ni, chutah chuan mute chu kawppui nei theuhin an awm khawm ang.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> LALPA lehkhabuah zawng u la, chhiar rawh u: chung zingah chuan pakhat mah kim lo a awm lo ang a, pakhat mah kawppui nei lo a awm lo ang: ka ka ngeiin thu a pe a, ka thlarau ngeiin chung chu a hruai khawm ta hlawm si a.Ani chuan an tan thum a vawrsak a, a kutin hruia tehin ram chu a semsak hlawm a; kumkhuain an nei ang a, chhuan awm chhung zawng zawngin chutah chuan an awm ang.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ani chuan an tan thum a vawrsak a, a kutin hruia tehin ram chu a semsak hlawm a; kumkhuain an nei ang a, chhuan awm chhung zawng zawngin chutah chuan an awm ang."
		},
		"35": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Thlaler leh ram pilril chu a lawm ang a; ram ro chu a hlimin phul pangpar angin a par ang.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> A par vul chuk ang a, lawm tak leh hla sain a hlim ang; Lebanon ropuina chu a hnenah pek a ni ang, Karmel leh Saron mawina nen: LALPA ropuina an hmu ang, kan Pathian mawina nen.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Kut chak lote chu tichak u la, khup zawite chu tinghet rawh u.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Thinlung dawihte hnenah chuan, \"chak takin awm u la, hlau suh u: ngai teh u, in Pathian chu phuba lakna nen a lo kal ang, Pathian thungrulhna nen chuan; a lo kal ang a, a chhandam ang che u,\" ti rawh u.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Chumi hnuah chuan mitdelte mit chu tihmenin a awm ang a, bengngawngte beng chu tihvarin a awm ang.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Chumi hunah chuan ke baite chu sakhi angin an zuang ang a, tawngtheilote lei chu hlim takin a zai ang: thlalerah chuan tuite a lo chik chhuak luah luah dawn si a, ram rovah chuan luite tui a lo chik chhuak luah luah bawk ang.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Tichuan tiau dip sa tak hmun chu dilah a chang ang a, lei tuihal tak chu tuihnaahte a chang ang: sihalte chenna an mutnaah chuan, hlobet, phairuang leh phungladin nen a awm ang.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Tin, chutah chuan lamlian a awm ang, kawng nen, chu chu \"Thianghlimna Kawng\" an ti ang a; mi bawlhhlawh chu chutah chuan an kal lo ang; amaherwahchu chu mite an a ni zawk ang: mi zin veivakte, a ni, mi ate pawh, chutah chuan an bo lo ang.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Sakeibaknei reng reng chutah chuan a awm lo ang a, sa koham reng reng chutah chuan a chho hek lo ang, chutah chuan hmuh tur pawh a awm lo ang; tlante erawh chu chutah chuan an kal zawk ang:tin, LALPA tlante chu an kir leh ang a, hla sa chungin Zion chu an thleng ang a; chatuana lawmna an lu chungah a awm tawh ang: hlimna leh lawmna an hmu ang a, lungngaihna leh rumna chu a bo tawh ang.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> tin, LALPA tlante chu an kir leh ang a, hla sa chungin Zion chu an thleng ang a; chatuana lawmna an lu chungah a awm tawh ang: hlimna leh lawmna an hmu ang a, lungngaihna leh rumna chu a bo tawh ang."
		},
		"36": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Tin, Hezekia lal kum sawm leh kum lina kumah chuan heti hi a ni a, Assuria ram lal Senakeriba chu Juda rama khua kulhpui nei zawng zawng bei turin a han chho a, a la ta a.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Tin, Assuria lal chuan Rabsakeba chu sipaiho tam tak hruaiin Lakis khua atangin Jerusalem khuaa lal Hezekia hnenah chuan a ti ra. Tin, dil chhakta zawk tuilakna kianga puan sutu phul lamlianah chuan a din ga.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Chutichuan lal chhungte chunga hotua awm Hilkia fapa Eliakima te, lehkha ziaktu Sebnaa te, chanchin ziaktu Asaphaa fapa Joa-te chu a hnenah an lo chhuak a.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Tin, Rabsakehan an hnenah, \"Hezekia hnenah heti hian sawi rawh u, 'Lal ropui tak Assuria lal chuan heti hian a ti, I rinna i nghahna hi eng nge ni le?",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Indona atan chuan i remruat leh i chakna hi thu mai mai a ni, ka ti: tu nge i rin a, ka chunga i hel tak ni le?",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ngai teh, he luang sawp tiang, Aigupta-ho hi, i ring a nih hi; chumi chu miin a rinchhan chuan akutah a chhun lut nhgawt ang; Aigupta lal Pharaoa chu amah ringtu zawng zawng chungah chuan chutiang chu a ni thin.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> A nih loh leh, ka hnenah, LALPA kan Pathian chu a ni kan rin ni, i tih chuan, ani chu Hezekian Juda-ho hnenah leh Jerusalem-ho hnenah, He maicham hmaah chauh hian in be tur a ni, tiin, a hmun sangte leh a maichamte a lak bosak kha a ni lo'm ni?",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Chutichuan, khawngaih takin, ka pu Assuria lal hnenah chuan thu tiam rawh, tichuan keiin sakawr sanghnih ka pe ang che, nangin a chunga chuangtu turte i hmuh theih dawn phawt chuan.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Engtin nge, tawlailirte leh sakwar chung chuang mite la thu-ah Aiugupta-ho chunga i rinna nghatin, ka pu chhiahhlawh te berte zinga hotu pakhat pawh hi i dan zawh dawn le?",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Tin, he ram hi tichhe tura bei turin LALPA tel loa lo chho em ka nih? LALPA'n ka hnenah, Chu ram chu bei turin chho la, tichhe rawh, mi ti a ni,' tiin,\" a ti a.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Tin, Eliakima leh Sebnaa leh Joate chuan, Rabsakeha hnenah, \"Khawngaih takin i chhiahhlawhte hi Suria tawngin min be awh rawh; chu chu kan hre thei si a: kulh bang chunga mite beng hriatah Juda tawngin min be tawh suh,\" an ti a.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Nimahsela Rabsakeha chuan, \"Ka pu chuan i pu hnen chauhvah leh i hnen chauhvah he'ng thu hi sawi turin mi tir em ni? Kulh bang chhunga thuho, nangmahni nena mahni ek la ei tur leh mahni zun la in turte hnenah hian mi tir zawk ani lawm ni?\" a ti a.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ti Rabsakeha chu a ding a, Juda tawngin aw ring takin a au a, \"Lal ropui tak Assuria lal thute hi ngaithla rawh u.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Lal chuan heti hian a ti, 'Hezekia bumin awm duh suh u; ani chuan a chhanhim thei dawn si lo cheh u:",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Hezekian, LALPA chuan matheiloin min chhanhim ang; he khawpui hi Assuria lal kutah pekin a awm lo ang, tiin sawi mah se la, LALPA chu Hezekia sawi angin ringduh chuang hek suh u.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> ,17 Hezekia thu ngaithla suh u: Assuria lal chuan heti hian a sawi si a, Min rem ula, ka hnenah hian lo chhuak rawh u; tin, ka lo kal a, nangmahni ram anga bu leh uain awmna ram, chhang leh grep huante awmna rama ka kalpui hma loh che u chuan, mi tinin mahni grep huia mi leh mi tinin mahni theipui kunga mi ei theuh ula, i tinin mahni tuikhur tui in theuh rawh u.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> ,16 Hezekia thu ngaithla suh u: Assuria lal chuan heti hian a sawi si a, Min rem ula, ka hnenah hian lo chhuak rawh u; tin, ka lo kal a, nangmahni ram anga bu leh uain awmna ram, chhang leh grep huante awmna rama ka kalpui hma loh che u chuan, mi tinin mahni grep huia mi leh mi tinin mahni theipui kunga mi ei theuh ula, i tinin mahni tuikhur tui in theuh rawh u.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> LALPA'n min chhanhim ang, tia Hezekian a thlem tak dah che uin fimkhur rawh u. Hnam tin pathian zinga mi reng rengin an ram chu Assuria lal lakah an chhanhim ta em ni?",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Hamath leh Arpad-ho pathiante kha khawiah nge an awm tak? Sepharvaim-ho pathiante kha khawiahnge an awm tak? Samari khua kha ka lakah an chhanhim ta em ni?",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Chung ram pathian zawng zawng zinga mi chuan tute nge an ram ka lakah chhanhim ni? LALPA chuan Jerusalem khua hi ka lakah a chhanhim tehchai ang maw?' tiin,\" a ti a.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Anni erawh chu an ngawi reng a, thu pakhat mahin an chhang lo: lal thupek chu, \"Ani chu chhang suh u,\" tih a ni si a.Chutichuan lal chhungte chunga hotua awm Hilkia fapa Eliakima te, lehkha ziaktu Sebnaa te, chanchin ziaktu Asaphaa fapa Joa-te chu silhfen pawhthler inbelin Hezekia hnenah chuan an lo thleng a, Rabsakeha thu sawite chu an hrilh ta a.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Chutichuan lal chhungte chunga hotua awm Hilkia fapa Eliakima te, lehkha ziaktu Sebnaa te, chanchin ziaktu Asaphaa fapa Joa-te chu silhfen pawhthler inbelin Hezekia hnenah chuan an lo thleng a, Rabsakeha thu sawite chu an hrilh ta a."
		},
		"37": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Tin, heti hi a ni a, lal Hezekia chuan chu chu a hriat veleh a silhfente chu a pawt thler a, saiip puan a inbel a, LALPA inah chuan a lut ta a,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Tin, a chhungte chunga hotua awm Eliakima leh, lehkha ziaktu Sebnaa leh, puithiamho upate chu saiip puan inbelin Amozaa fapa zawlnei Isaia hnenah a tir a.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Tin, anni chuan a hnenah, \"Hezekian heti hian a ti, 'Vawiin ni hi manganna leh hmusitna ni a ni: naute chu an pian a hun tawh si a, anmahni hring turin chakna a awm tawh si lo.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Rabsakeha, a pu Assirua lalin Pathian nung sawichhe tura a tirha thu sawite chu, LALPA i Pathian chuan a bengin a la hria a ni thei e, tichuan a thu sawi, LALPA i Pathianin a benga a hriatahte chuan, a la zilhhau ang: chu mi avang chuan a la awm chhunte tan chuan i tawngtaina chu hlan chho rawh,' a ti e,\" an ti a.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> chutichuan lal Jezekia chhiahhlawhte chu Isaia hnenah an lo kal a.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Tin, Isaian an hnenah, \"In pu hnenah heti hian in sawi tur a ni, 'LALPA chuan heti hian a ti, I thu hriat, Assuria lal chhiahhlawhten mi sawichhiatnate kha, hlau suh.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ngai teh, a kawchhungah chuan thlarau engema ka awmtir ang a, tichuan thuthang a hria ang a, ama ramah a haw leh ang; tichuan ama ram ngeiah chuan khandaiha tihtlukin ka awmtir ang, a ti e,' tiin,\" a ti a.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Chutichuan Rabsakeha chu a kir leh a, Assuria lal chuan Libnah khua a bei lai chu a va hmu a; Lakis khua ata chu a kal chhuak tawh tih a hre tawh reng si a.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Tin, Assuria lal Senakeriba chuan Tirhaka, Ethiopia ram lal chungchang thu, \"Nangmah bei turin a chhuak ta,\" tiin mi sawi a hria. Tichuan chu chu a hriat veleh Jezekia hnenah palaite a tir a,",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> \"Heti hian Juda-ho lal Jezekia hnenah in sawi tur a ni, 'I rin Pathian chuan, Jerusalem khua Assuria lal kutah pek a ni lo ang, tiin bum che suh se.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ngai teh, Asuria lalten ram zawng zawng tichhe vekin an chunga an thiltihte kha i bengin i hria e: tichuan nang tehlul hi chhanhimin i awm dawn bik em ni?",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> hnam tin pathiante chuan, Gozan-ho te, Haran-ho te, Razep-ho te, Eden fa Telasar khuaa awm te, min thlahtuten an tihboralte kha, an chhanhim em ni?",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Hamath lal te, Arpad lal te, Sepharvaim khawpui lal te, Hena lal te, Ivah lal te kha khawiah nge an awm tak?' tiin,\" a ti a.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Tin, Hezekia chuan palaite kut ata lehkha chu a hmu a, a han chhiar a: tichuan Jezekia chu LALPA inah chuan a han lut a, LALPA hmaah chuan a phah ta a.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Tin, Jezekia chuan LALPA hnenah a tawngtai a,",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> \"Aw sipaihote LALPA, Israel-ho Pathian, chrub chunga thua, nang hi, nang chauh hi, leilung luah ram zawng zawng Pathian chu i ni; nang chuan lei leh van hi i siam a ni.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Aw LALPA, i beng rawn dawh la, ngaithla teh; aw LALPA, i mit meng la, en teh: Pathian nung sawichhe tura mite tirtu Senakeriba thu zawng zawng hi ngaithla teh.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> LALPA, Assuria lalten ram zawng zawng leh an lei chu an tichhe ngei tak a,",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> an pathiante chu meiah an paih bawk a: chungte chu pathian an ni lo reng a ni, mihing kuta siam, thing leh lung an ni zawk; chuvangin an tiboral a ni.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Chuvangin aw LALPA kan Pathian, nang hi, nang chauh hi, LALPA i ni tih leilung luah ram zawng zawng hian an hriat theihna'n a lakah min chhandam ang che,\" tiin.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Chumi lai chuan Amozaa fapa Isaia chuan Jezekia hnenah mi a tir a, heti hian a ti a, \"LALPA Israel-ho Pathian chuan heti hian a ti a ni, 'Assuria lal Senakeriba chhiatna tur lama ka hnenah i tawngtai avangin,",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> hei hi a chungchang thu LALPA'n a sawi chu a ni: Zion fanu nula chuan a hmusit chia, a nuihsan che, Jerusalem fanu chuan a lu a thin khum che.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Tunge i tihhmingchhiata i sawichhiat ni? Tu chungah nge i aw i tihpawra i mit i tihsan? Israel ho Mi Thianghlim chung ngeiah.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> I chhiahhlawhte hmangin LALPA chu i tihmingchhia a, Ka tawlailir tam ak nen tlang hmun zo, Lebanon ram rilahte hian ka lo thelng chho ta a; a sidar thing sang takte leh a far thing tha mite hi ka kit ang a: a hmun zo hla ber, a lei tha hmun ram ngawh chuan ka lut ang.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Tuichhunchhuah ka lai a, tui ka in thin a, ka kephah hnuai hian Aigupta lui zawng zawng chu ka tikang vek ang, i ti a.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> keima'n hman lai ata chung chu ka tih a ni a, hmasang ata chung chu ka siam a ni tih i hre lo em ni? Kulhpui nei khuate tichim turin ka ti che a ni.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Chuvangin a chhunga awmte chu an chak mang lo a, an hlau a, an lo mualpho tak kha; phul hlobet ang leh, hnim hring ang leh, in chunga hlobet ang leh, lo buh that hma ang lek an nih kha.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Kei erawh chuan i thut te, i chhuah te, i luh te, ka chunga i thinurziate hi ka hria a sin.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> ka chunga i thinur avang leh, i tawng chaltlaizia chu ka bengah a lo luh chhoh tak avang hian ka hnar vuah chu i hnarha ka vuah ang a, ka thirbarh chu i hmuiah ka vuah bawk ang a, i lo kalna kawng ngeiah khan ka kirtir leh ang che, tih hi,' tiin.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Tin, hei hi i tan chhinchhiahna tur chu a ni ang: kuminah hian buh hli in ring ang a; nakkumah pawh chu mi hlibawk chu in ring ang; tin, a kum thumnaah chuan buh tuh u la, at u la, grep huante siam u la, a rah ei rawh u.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Tin, Juda chhungte zinga la dam chhunte chu a chhukzawnga zung kaia, a chho zawnga rahin a awm leh ang.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Jerusalem atangin a la awm chhunte chu an chhuak ang a, Zion tlang atangin a la dam turte chu an chhuak bawk ang: sipaihote LALPA thahnemngaihna chuan chung chu a ti ang.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> chuvangin LALPA chuan Assuria lal chungchang thu-ah heti hian a ti, 'Ani chuan he khawpui hi a lo thleng lo ang a, hetah hian thal a kap hek lo ang, phaw nen a kiangah a lo kal hek lo ang a, a beina turin lei kulh a siam hek lo ang.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> A lo kalna kawngah, chumiah ngei chuan a kir leh ang a, he khawpui hi a lo thleng lo ang, LALPA'n a ti.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Keimah avang leh ka chhiahhlawh Davida avangin he khawpui hi chhanhim turin ka hum dawn a ni,' tiin,\" a ti a.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Tichuan LALPA vantirhkoh chu a va chhuak a, Assuria-ho riah hmunah chuan mi nuaikhat leh singriat leh sangnga a tihlum a: tin, zing taka mi an han thawh chuan, ngai teh, mitthi ruang hlir a lo ni a.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Chutichuan Assuria lal Senakeriba chu a chhuak a, a kal a, a kir leh ta zel a, Ninevi khuaah chuan a awm ta reng a.Tin, heti hi a ni a, a pathian Nisroka inah chuan pathian a biak laiin a fapa Adrammeleka leh Sarezera-te chuan khandaihin an sat hlum a: tichuan an tlan bo a, Ararat ramah chuan an lut ta a. Tin, a fapa Esar-haddona chuan a aiawhin ro a rel ta a.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Tin, heti hi a ni a, a pathian Nisroka inah chuan pathian a biak laiin a fapa Adrammeleka leh Sarezera-te chuan khandaihin an sat hlum a: tichuan an tlan bo a, Ararat ramah chuan an lut ta a. Tin, a fapa Esar-haddona chuan a aiawhin ro a rel ta a."
		},
		"38": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Chung lai chuan Jezekia chu thih ngamin a na a.Tichuan Amozaa fapa zawlnei Isaia ch a hnenah a lo kal a, a hnenah,\"LALPA chuan heti hian a ti,'I chhungte khawsak dan tur relsak rawh; dam chhuak loin i thi ngei dawn si a,' tiin,\" a ti a.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Chutichuan Hezekia chu bang lam hawiin a let a, LALPA hnenah a tawngtai a,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> \"Aw LALPA, i hmaah thutak leh thinlung tha famkim pua ka awm thinzia leh, i mithmuha thil tha ka tih thinzia kha, khawngaih takin hre reng ang che,\"a ti a. Tin, Jezekia chu a tap ta zawih zawih a.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Chutichuan LALPA thu chu Isaia hnenah a lo thleng",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> \"Kal la, Hezekia hnenah sawi rawh, 'LALPA, i pu Davida Pathian chuan heti hian a ti, I tawngtaina kha ka hria a, i mittuite pawh ka hmu a: ngai teh, i dam chhung nite hi kum sawm leh kum ngain ka tisei ang.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Tin, nang leh he khawpui hi Assuria lal lakah ka chhanhim ang a: he khawpui hi ka hum ang.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Tin, LALPA'n a thil sawi hi a ti ngei dawn tih, hei hi i tan LALPA laka chhinchhiahna tur chu a ni ang:",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> \"En teh Lal Ahaza dar chin tehnaa ni hlim saw, rahka sawmin ka tikir ang,\"a ti a. Chutichuan ni hlim chu rahka sawm a kir leh ta a.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Juda lal Hezekia dam lo, a dam leh hnua a lehkha ziak chu :",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> \"Ka dam chhung nite chhun lai takah hian thlan kawngkaahte chan ka lut dawn a: Ka dam chhung kum la bak turte chu chhuhin ka awm ta,\" ka ti a.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> \"LALPA, LALPA ngei chu, mi nung ramah hian ka hmu dawn tawh lo va: Khawvela awmte zingah hian mihring ka hmu leh dawn tawh lo a nih hi.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ka awmna hi sawnin a awm a, beram vengtu puan in angin ka hnen ata lak boin a awm ta; Puan tahtun a puan a zial angin ka nunna hi ka zial a ani chuan thembu atangin mi chep chhum hmawk dawn a: Nangin ni khat leh zan khat thil thu-ah mi titawp mai dawn a nih hi\" ka ti a.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Zing thlengin a ngawi hram hramg a; sakeibaknei angin ka ruh zawng zawng a titliak vek a: Nangin ni khat leh zan khat thil thu-ah mi titawp mai dan a nih hi.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Vamur emaw, kanghlai emaw angin ka hram ka hram a, Thuro angin ka rum ka rum a, chung lam thlirna'n ka mit a vai zo ta; Aw LALPA, hnehchhiaha ka awm hi, nang chuan a bul mi tumsak ang che.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Eng nge ka sawi ang aw! Ani chuan mi bia a, ani vek chuan a ti ta nghal a: Ka nunna thawpikna avang khan ka dam chhung kum zawng zawngah chuan zawi tein ka kal dem dem tawh ang.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Aw Lalpa, hetiang thil avang hian mihringte hi an nung thin a, chungah chauh chuan ka thlarau nunna chu a awm thin: Chumi avang chuan mi tidam lehin mi tinung leh ang che.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ngai teh, ka thlamuanna turin a ni, thawpikna nasa tak ka neih kha ni: Nimahsela nang chuan, ka nunna i hmangaih avangin, chhiatna khuarkhurum ata chu i chhanhim ta; Ka sual zawng zawng kha i hnung lamah chuan i paih vek si a.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Thlan hian a fak thei si lo che a, thihna hian a chawimawi thei hek lo che: Kuarkhuruma chhukte chuan i thu tak chu an beisei t hei lo a ni.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Mi nungin, mi nungin, anni ngei chuan, vawiina ka tih ang hian an fak ang che: Pa chuan fate hnenah i thutak chu a hriattir ang.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> LALPA chu mi chhandam turin a peih reng a ni. Chuvangin ka dam chhung zawng zawngin, LALPA inah chuan, a hlate hi tintangte nen ka sa ang.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Isaia chuan, \"Theipui rah hlawm khat la se la, damdawi abela bel mi atan a khawihliah bel rawh se, tichuan a dam ang,\" a lo ti tawh a ni.Hezekia pawh chuan, \"LALPA inah ka chho leh ang tih hriatna eng chhinchhiahna nge lo awm ang?\" a lo ti tawh a ni.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Hezekia pawh chuan, \"LALPA inah ka chho leh ang tih hriatna eng chhinchhiahna nge lo awm ang?\" a lo ti tawh a ni."
		},
		"39": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Chumi lai chuan Baladana fapa Babulon lal Merodak-baladana chuan lehkhate leh lawmman Hezekia hnenah a thawn a: a na tih leh a dam leh ta tih a lo hriat avangin.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Tichuan Hezekia chu an chungah a lawm a, an hnenah a thil hlu dahna in te, tangka te, rangkachak te, englo rimtui te, hriak hlu tak te, a ralthuam dahna in chhung zawng zawng chu a entir a; a ina mi leh a rma chhunga mi Hezekian an hnena a entir loh thil eng reng a awm lo.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Chumilai chuan zawlnei Isaia chu lal Hezekia hnenah a lo kal a, a hnenah, \"Nichina mie khan eng nge an sawi?\" Khawi atangin nge i hnenah an lo kal?\" a ti a. Tin, Hezekia chuan, \"Ram hla tak ata, Babulon atang chuan ka hnenah an lo kal a ni,\" a ti a.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Tichuan ani chuan, \"I inah hian eng nge an en kha?\" a ti a. Tin, Hezekia chuan, \"Ka in chhung awm zawng zawng chu an en vek: ka ro tha zinga mi ka entir loh engmah a awm lo,\" tiin a chhang a.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Tichuan Isaian Hezekia hnenah chuan, \"Sipaihote LALPA thu hi hre rawh.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ngai teh, i in chhunga awm zawng zawng leh vawiin thlenga i puten an khawl khawmte chu Babulon khuaa kalpuiin a awm vek ang; engmah reng reng hnutchhiahin a awm lo ang; chutiang nite chu a la thleng dawn,' LALPA'n a ti.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Tin, i fapa, i rila la rah tur, i hrin turte ngei zinga mi chu, an kal bopui ang; anni ch Babulon lal inah chuan mi tilrehah an la awm ang,' a ti,\" a ti a.Tichuan Hezekian Isaia hnenah chuan, \"LALPA thu i sawi hi a tha e,\" a ti a. Amah vek chuan, \"Ka dam chhung hian remna leh thutak a awm dawn si a,\" a ti bawk a.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Tichuan Hezekian Isaia hnenah chuan, \"LALPA thu i sawi hi a tha e,\" a ti a. Amah vek chuan, \"Ka dam chhung hian remna leh thutak a awm dawn si a,\" a ti bawk a."
		},
		"40": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Thlamuan rawh u, ka mite hi thlamuan rawh u, in Pathianin a ti.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Jerusalem-ho hnenah thlamuan lamzawngin thu sawi u la, an indona chu a kin a, an sualna chu ngaihdam a ni a,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Chu! Autu rawl chuan, \"Thlalerah LALPA kawng buatsaih u la, ram rovah kan Pathian tan lamlian tirual rawh u.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Kawr tin, tihsan a ni vek ang a, tlang tin, mual tin, tihhniam a ni bawk ang: kawng kawite tihngil a ni ang a, a bum boh laite tihrual a ni bawk ang:",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> tin, LALPA ropuina chu tihlan a ni ang a, mi zawng zawngin chu chu an hmu tlang dial ang: LALPA ka chuan a sawi tawh si a,\" a ti.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Chu! Aw chuan, \"Eng thu sawiin nge ka au vang?\" a ti a. \"'Mi zawng zawng hlobet ang an ni a, an ropuina zawng zawng pawh phul pangpar ang a ni:",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> LALPA thaw chuan a chhem avangin hlobet chu a vuai a, a par chu a chuai thin: mite chu hlobet ang an ni ngei mai a.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Hlobet chu a vuai a, a par chu a chuai thin: kan Pathian thu erawh chu chatuanin a awm reng ang,' tiin,\" a ti a.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Aw Zion hnena chanchin tha hriltu, tlang sang takah khian han chho rawh; aw Jerusalem hnena chanchin tha hriltu, ring takin i aw chhuah rawh; chhuah rawh, hlau suh; Juda khuate hnenah chuan, \"en teh u, in Pathian hi1",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> En teh u, Lalpa PATHIAN chu mi chak tak angin a lo kal dawn hi; a ban chuan a aiah ro a rel ang; en teh u, a lawmman chu a hnenah a awm hi, a rulhna chu a hmaah a awm bawk a.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ani chuan beram vengtu angin a pawl chu a chawm ang a, beram note chu a banin a pawm khawm ang a, a angchhunga dahin a kalpui ang a, no hruai laite chu zawi tein a hruai dial dial ang,\" ti rawh.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Tuin nge tuite chu a kutphah khuar leka teha, van khi khap leka teh a, leia vaivut hi tehkhawng pakhat leka thun vek a, tlangte chu khin leka buka, mual pawngte chu bukna leka buk kha le?",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Tuin nge LALPA thlarau chu thil tih dan tur kawhhmuh le? A nih loh leh tu nge a remruatsaktu nia amah zirtir le?",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Ani chuan tu nge a rawn a, tuin nge amah chu hriattir a, rorelna kawng entira, hriatna zirtir a, hriatthiamna kawng entir ngai le?",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ngai teh, hnam tin chu baltina tui far khat ang lek an ni a, buknaa thil dip bang kai ang leka ruat an ni: ngai teh, ani chuan thliarkarte chu thil te tak te angin a la nelh nelh mai thin.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Lebanon meuh pawh tuah tham a ni lo a, a rama rante pawh halrala inthawina tham an ni hek lo.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Hnam tinrengte chu a hmaah chuan engmah lo ang an ni a ani ngaih chuan engmah lo aia tlem zawk, boruak mai an ni a.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Pathian chu tu nen nge in tehkhin dawn le? A nih loh leh, eng lem nge amah nen in tehkhin dawn le?",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Milem siam chawp hi, hna thawk mi chuan a chhung a, rangkachak chher mi chuan rangkachakin a luan a, chu mi tan chuan tangka khaidiatte a chhunsak thin.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Chutiang thilpek pe zo lo e rethei lutuk chuan thing mawih lo tur a thlang thin; milem siam chawp, nghing lo tur, atana dinsaktu tur themthiam mi a zawngt thin.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> In rilruin in hre ngai lo em ni? In bengin in hre ngai lo em ni? Atir atang khan an hrilh lo che u em ni? Leilung pian tirh atang khan in hre thiam lo em ni?",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ani chu leilung kualkhungna chunga thua chu a ni, a mithmuh chuan lei chunga awmho chu khaute ang lek an ni a; ani chu van khi puan in chung anga kai pharh a, puan in awmna turah zar a,",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> mi liante engmah loa siam thina chu a ni; ani chuan leia roreltute chu boruakah a siam thin.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> A ni, a phun an ni lo; a ni, a tuh an ni lo; a ni, an kung chuan leiah zung a kai lo: chu lo pawh chu ani chuan anniho chu a chhem a, an vuai a, thawngaleivirin buh si a lak bo angin a la bo thin.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Tu nen nge mi tehkhin a, tu tluk lekah nge mi ruat dan? Mi Thianghlim chuan a ti.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Chung lamah khian in mitte len chho u la, khingte khi tu siam nge ni en rawh u; ani chuan sipaihote khi indawt zelin a hruai chhuak thin a, an hmingin a ko theuh thin a; a chakna nasatna avang leh, thiltihtheihna lama a chak avangin pakhat mah kim lo an awm ngai lo.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Engati nge, aw Jakob-ho, hetianga in tih ni, engati nge, aw Israel-ho, hetianga in sawi ni, \"Ka kawng hi LALPA laka thup a ni a, ro mi relna hi ka Pathian laka lak bo a ni ta,\" tih hi?",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> In rilruin in hre ngai lo em ni? In bengin in hre ngai lo em ni? Kumkhaw Pathian, LALPA, Kawlkil Siamtu chu, a chau ngai lo a, a hah ngai hek lohzia hi; a hriat thiamzia chu zawn chhuah rual a ni lo.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Chau hnenahte chuan thiltihtheihna a pe thin a; chakna reng nei lote chu a tichak thin.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Tleirawlte meuh pawh an chauin an hah ang a, tlangvalte pawh an tlu der ang:LALPA nghaktute erawh chuan an chakna chu an siam tha leh ang a; mupuite angin thlain an thlawk chho ang a; hah loin an tlan ang a; chau loin kein an kal ang.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> LALPA nghaktute erawh chuan an chakna chu an siam tha leh ang a; mupuite angin thlain an thlawk chho ang a; hah loin an tlan ang a; chau loin kein an kal ang."
		},
		"41": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Aw thliarkarte u, ka hmaah chuan ngawi thiap rawh u; mi tin chuan an chakna tithar leh se la: lo hnai hlawm se la; chumi hnuah chuan sawi rawh se: rorel turin i inhnaih tlang teh ang u.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Khawchhak ata mi pakhat, felna avanga a ke bula a koha chu, tuin nge kai harh? Ani chuan hnam tin a hmaah a pe a, lalho chungah ro a reltir a; anni chu vaivut angin a khandaih hennah a pe a, buh si thli chhem len angin a thalngul hnenah a pe bawk a.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ani chuan anniho chu a um a, him takin a kal zel a;a kea a la kalna ngai loh kawngah chuan.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Atir ata chhuan zawng zawng koin, tuin nge thawk a, ti zo? Kei LALPA, a hmasa ber leh a hnuhnung bera hnena awm hi, a titu chu ka ni.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Thliarkarte chuan an hmu a, an hlau a; kawl kilte chu an khur a: an rawn hnaih a, an lo kal a.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Mi tinin mahni thiante an tanpui a; mi tinin an unaute hnenah, \"Thlamuang takin rawm rawh,\" an ti theuh a.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Chutiachuan a charna lam thu-ah chuan, \"A tha e,\" tiin, themthiam mi chuan rangkachak chher mi a fuih a, tuboha deng mam mi chuan dolung deng mi a fuih bawk a: tin, a nghin lohna turin kilhnatein a kilh tlat a.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Nimahsela, nangni Israel-ho ka chhaihhlawh, Jakob-ho ka mi thlan, ka thian Abrahama thlahte u,",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> nangni leilung tawpna ata ka mi hruai, a kil ata ka mi koh, \"Ka chhiahhlawhte in ni, paih thla loin ka thlang zawk che u,\" ka tihate u,",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> hlau suh u, kei in h nenah ka awm si a; mangang suh u, kei in Pathian ka ni si a: ka tichak ang che u a; a ni, ka tanpui ang che u; a ni, ka felna kut ding lamin ka chelh reng ang che u.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ngai teh, in chunga lungni lo zawng zawng chu mualpho tak leh zak takin an awm ang: nangmahni hnialtute chu engmah lo ang an ni ang a, an b oral ang.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> nangmahni hnailtute chu in zawng ang a, in hmu si lo ang: nangmahni dotute chu engmah lo ang an ni ang a, thil awm lo ang mai an ni ang.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Kei LALPA in Pathian hian \"Hlau suh u, ka tanpui dawn a che u,\" tiin, in kut ding lam chu ka chelh dawn si a.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Nang Jakob changpat leh Israel mite u, hlau suh u, ka tanpui ang che u, LALPA'n a ti, nangmahni tlantu che u chu Israel-ho Mi Thianghlim chu a ni.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ngai teh, buh chilna khawl thar tak, hria tak, ha nei mi-ah ka siam ang che u: tlangte chu chilin in vaw sawm ang a, mual pawngte chu buh si angin in siam ang.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> In zap ang a, thliin a chhem leng ang a, thawngaleivirin a tidarh ang: tin, nangni chu LALPAah chuan in lawm ang a, Israel-ho Mi Thianghlim chu in la chhuang ang.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Mi rethei leh pachhiate chuan tui an zawng thin a, a awm si lo a, an lei chu tuihalin a ro vek thin; kei LALPA hian anni chu ka chhang ang a, kei Israel-ho Pathian hian anni chu ka kalsan lo ang.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Tlang sang kawlh vel vulah chuan luite ka luan chhuahtir ang a, ruam laiahte chuan tuihnate ka chhuahtir bawk ang: thlaler chu dilah ka siam ang a, ram ro chu tuihnaah ka siam bawk ang.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Thlalerah chuan sidar thing te, thingri te, lenhmui te, hriak thing te ka phun ang a; ram rovah chuan far te, phan te, tuifar te ka phun za vek ang:",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> LALPA kut chuan chung chu a ti a ni tih leh Israel-ho Mi Thianghlim chuan a siam ani tih an hmuh a, an hriat a, an ngaihtuah a, an hriat thiam tlanna turin.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> In thu chu rawn sawi rawh u, LALPA'n a ti; pathian in intihna chhan berte chu lantir rawh u, Jakob-ho Lalin a ti.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Chung chu lantir se la, thil lo la thleng tur chu kan hnenah saiw rawh se: kan ngaihtuah theihna tur leh a tawpna tur kan hriat theihna turin, tun hma thilte chu eng nge a nih sawi rawh u; a nih loh leh, thil lo la thleng turte chu hriattir rawh u.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Pathian in ni tih kan hriat theihna turin tun hnua thil lo la thleng turte chu sawi rawh u le: a ni, kan manganna tur leh kan en tlanna turin, thil tha emaw thil tha lo emaw ti rawh u le.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Ngai teh u, engmah in lo nih loh hi, in thiltih pawh engmah a ni hek lo: nangmahni thlangtute chu mi tenawm tak an ni.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> hmar lam ata mi pakhat ka kai harh a, ani chu a lo thleng ta: ni chhuahna ata ka hming lamtu chu: ani chu lung charna sawisak angin roreltute a sawisa ang a, bawlvawtuin hlum a rap ban angin a rap bawk ang.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Kan hriat theihna turin tuin nge atir atang khan saiw ngai? A ni, \"Ani hi a dik e,\" kan tih theihna turin tuin nge sawi lawk ngai? A ni, sawi reng reng an awm lo, a ni, hriattir reng reng an awm lo, a ni, in thu sawite hi hria reng reng an awm o.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Keiin Zion hnenah chuan, \"En teh, anni saw en teh,\" ka ti hmasa ang a; Jerusalem hnenah chuan chanchin tha rawn thelntu pakhat a pe ang.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Tin, ka han en pawhin mi reng reng an awm lo a; anmahni ka han zawh pawhin, an zinga remruattu, thu pakhat pawh chhang thei tumah reng reng an awm lo.En teh u, an za hian, an hnathawhte chu engmah lo a ni a, thil awm lo reng reng a ni: an milem chhunte chu thli leh boruak chauh a ni.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> En teh u, an za hian, an hnathawhte chu engmah lo a ni a, thil awm lo reng reng a ni: an milem chhunte chu thli leh boruak chauh a ni."
		},
		"42": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ka chhiahhlawh, ka chelh reng, ka thlan, ka rilruin a lawm em ema hi en teh u: a chungah ka thlaru ka dah ta; Jentailte hnena pek turin rorelna thu a la chhuak ang.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> A au lo ang a, aw a chhuah hek lo ang a, kawtthlerah a awm a chhuah hek lo vang a, kawtthlerah a aw chu ahriattir hek lo ang.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Luang sawp a titliak fithla lo ang a, la khu pawh a timit lo ang: rorelna chu thutakin a la chhuak ang.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Leiah hian rorelna a awmtir hma loh chuan ani chu a chau lo ang a, a beidawng hek lo ang; tin, thliarkarte chuan a dan thu chu an nghak reng dawn.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Pathian, LALPA, van siamtu leh kai pharhtu, lei leh a chhung ata chhuak zawng zawng tizautu, a chunga mite hnena thawkna petu leh a chung kalte hnena thlarau petu chuan heti hian a ti:",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> ,7 \"Kei LALPA hian felnain ka ko a che, i kut ka chelh ang a, ka humhim ang chia, mitdelte mit tivar tur leh, mi tangte rip chhung ata hruai chhuak tur leh, thim zinga thute tan in ata hruai chhuak turin, mite thuthlung atan leh Jentailte tiengtu atan ka ruat ang che.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> ,6 \"Kei LALPA hian felnain ka ko a che, i kut ka chelh ang a, ka humhim ang chia, mitdelte mit tivar tur leh, mi tangte rip chhung ata hruai chhuak tur leh, thim zinga thute tan in ata hruai chhuak turin, mite thuthlung atan leh Jentailte tiengtu atan ka ruat ang che.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> LALPA chu ka ni; chu chu ka hming a ni: ka rpuina hi mi dang hnenah ka pe lo vang a, fak ka hlawhna hi milem siam chawpte hnenah ka pe hek lo ang.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ngai teh u, tun hma thilte chu a lo thleng ta, thil tharte ka sawi a nih hi: a tiah hmain a chanchin ka hrilh che u a nih hi.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Tuifinriata zuk kalte leh, a chhunga awm zawng zawngte leh, thliarkarte leh, a chunga awm zawng zawngte u, LALPA chawimawiin hla thar sa u la, kawlkil atang pawhin amah fakna hla sa rawh u.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Thlaler leh a khawpuite chuan an aw chhuah rawh se, Kedar-ho awmna khuate chuan; Sela khuaa awmte chu hlim takin zai se la, tlang chhip atangte chuan au rawh se.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> LALPA chu tiropui se la, thliarkarahte chuan a fakna thu hirl rawh se.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> LALPA chu mi chak tak angin a chhuak ang a, indo mi angin thinurna a chawk tho vang: a au vang a, a ni, ring takin a au vang; amah dotute chungah chuan chak takin a che ang.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Rei tak ka ngawi reng tawh a; ka awm hle hlein ka insum hram hram thin: tunah erawh chuan hmeichhe nau vei angin ka au tuar tuar ang a; ka thaw huam huamin ka thaw hlawp hlawp bawk ang.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Tlangte leh mual pawngte chu ka tichhia ang a, a hnim zawng zawngte chu ka tiro vek ang; luite chu thliarkarh te ka siam ang a, dilte chu ka tikang ang.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Mitdelte chu an hriat ngai loh kawngah ka rawn hruai ang a; an hriat ngai loh kalkawngahte chuan ka hruai ang: an hmaah chuan thim chu engah ka siam ang a, kawng kawi laite chu ka tingil bawk ang. Chung thil chu ka ti ang a, anni pawh ka thlahthlam lo ang.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Milem siam chawpte ring a, milem chhunte hnena, \"Kan pathian in ni,\" titute chu hawi kirtirin an awm ang a, nasa takin an mualpho ang.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bengngawngte u, bengin hre rawh u; mitdelte u, in hmuh theihna'n en rawh u.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ka chhiahhlawh lo chu tu mit nge del:? A nih loh leh, ka tirhkoh tirh angin tu beng nge ngawng? Mi remtu angin tu mit nge dela, LALPA chhiahhlawh angin tu mit nge del?",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Thil tam tak i hmu a, nimahsela i rilruah i vawng reng thin lo; a bengte chu a awng a, nimahsela a hre thin lo.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Dan chu a felna avanga tihlena tihzahawm chu LALPA chuan a tha a ti a.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Nimahsela he'ng mite hian rawk leh suam an tawk a, humah an tla a, tan inah an tang bo a; sal atan man an ni a, chhantu tumah an awm lo.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> In zingah hian chungah chuan tu nge beng chhi tur awm che u? Hun lo la thleng tur atan ngaithlaa hre tur tu nge awm che u?",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Tuin nge Jakob-ho rallaka lak tura pea, Israel-ho rukrute hnenah pe ni? LALPA, a chunga thil kan tihsualna chuan a pek a ni lo'm ni? A kawngahte an kal duh si lo a, a dan thu lah an awih hek lo.Chuvangin a thinur nasa tak chu an chungah a leih a, indo ralthlak an chungah a thlentir a, chu chuan anmahni chu a kang a.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Chuvangin a thinur nasa tak chu an chungah a leih a, indo ralthlak an chungah a thlentir a, chu chuan anmahni chu a kang a."
		},
		"43": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Tunah erawh chuan, aw Jakob-hote u, LALPA nangmahni siamtu leh aw Israel-hote u, nangmahni dintu chuan heti hian a ti: \"Hlau suh u, ka tlan tawh che u hi; in hmingah ka ko che u a, ka ta in ni si a sin.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Tuite in dai kai lai pawhin kei in hnenah ka awm ang a; luite in dai kai lai pawhin a chim pil lo ang che u: meia in kal tlang lai pawhin in kang lo ang a; meialhin a tialh hek lo ang che u.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Kei hi LALPA in Pathian, Israel-ho Mi Thianghlim nangmahni chhandamtu ka ni si a; nangmahni tlanna atan Aigupta ram ka pe a, Ethiopia leh Seba ramte chu nangmahni aiah ka pe.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> ka ngaiha hlu tak in nih a, mi zahawm tak in nih bawk a, ka hmangaih bawk che u avangin, nangmahni aiah mite ka pe ang a, in nunna aiah mi tin ka ep ang.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Hlau suh u, in hnenah ka awm si a: in thlahte chu kahwchhak lam atangin ka rawn hruai ang a, khawthlang lam atangin ka hruai khawm ang che u,",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> hmar lam hnenah chuan, 'Thlah rawh u,' ka ti ang a; chhim lam hnenah chuan, 'Hreng reng suh u,' ka ti ang; ka fapate chu hla tak atangin rawn hruai u la, ka fanute chu kawlkil atangin rawn hruai rawh u;",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> ka hming pu apiangte leh ka ropuina tura ka siam apiangte chu; anmahni chu ka din a, a ni, anmahni chu ka siam a ni.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> \"Mit nei si mitdelte leh, beng nei si bengngawngte chu hruai chhuak rawh u.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Hnam tinreng inkhawm se la, mi tin awm khawm rawh se: an zingah tuin nge hei hi sawi thei a, tun hma thilte min hriattir thei? Thiam chantira an awm theihna turin an thuhretute chu rawn hruai rawh se: a nih loh leh, bengin hria se la, 'Thutak a ni,' ti rawh se.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Mi hriata, mi rina, amah chu ka ni tih in hriat theihna turin, nangni hi mi hriatpuitute in ni, ka chhiahhlawh ka thlana pawh chu, LALPA'n a ti: ka awm hma chuan Pathian reng reng din an awm lo a, ka awm hnuah pawh an awm hek lo ang.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Kei, keimah ngei hi, LALPA chu ka ni; keimah lo chu chhandamtu reng reng an awm lo.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Keimahin ka sawi a, ka chhandam a, ka hriattir a, in zingah khan ram dang pathian reng reng an awm loh kha; chuvangin nangni hi ka thu mi hriatpuitute in ni, LALPA'n a ti, tin, kei chu Pathian ka ni.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> A ni, ni awm achinah khan kei chu amah chu ka ni; tichuan ka kut ata chhan chhuakt hei tumah reng reng an awm lo: hna ka thawk ang a, tuin nge chu chu sut ang?\" tiin.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> LALPA, nangmahni tlantu, Israel-ho Mi Thianghlim chuan heti hian a ti: \"Nangmahni avangin Babulon khuaah chuan sipaiho ka tir a, tichuan an zain, Kaldai-hote chu, an lawmna lawngpuiah-te chuan tlan bo mi hruaiin ka hruai chhuk ang.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Kei hi, LALPA, in Mi Thianghlim, Israel-ho Siamtu, in Lal chu ka ni,\" tiin.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Tuipuia kawng siam a, tui tam tak zinga lamlian sialtu,",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> sipai rual ropui tak, tawlailirte leh sakawrte hruai a, tho leh hauh lo tura titlu rem rumtu, khawnvar phita tihmih anga tichimittu LALPA chuan heti hian a ti:",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> \"Tun hma thilte chu hre reng suh u la, hmasang thilte chu ngaihtuah hek suh u.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ngai teh u, thil thar ka ti dawn e; tun apang hian a tiak ang; chu chu in hre dawn lo'm ni? Thlalerah meuh pawhkawng ka siam ang a, ram rovah chuan luite ka siam bawk ang.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> ,21 Ka mi, ka thlante, mi fakna tilangtu tura ka tana ka mi siamte chu, in tur ka pek theihna'n, thlalerah chuan tuite ka awmtir avang leh, ram rovah chuan luite ka awmtir avangin ram sate pawhin mi chawimawi ang, sihalte, sava nghawngseite lamin.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> ,20 Ka mi, ka thlante, mi fakna tilangtu tura ka tana ka mi siamte chu, in tur ka pek theihna'n, thlalerah chuan tuite ka awmtir avang leh, ram rovah chuan luite ka awmtir avangin ram sate pawhin mi chawimawi ang, sihalte, sava nghawngseite lamin.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Nimahsela aw Jakob-ho, nangni zawngin mi ko si lo a, aw Israel-ho, nangni zawngin mi ning zawk a nih hi.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> halrala in thil hlan ran tete chu mi rawn lak ngai lo a; in inthawina lamte chuan mi chawimawi ngai hek lo. Thil hlanin rawng ka bawltir ngai lo che u a, berawin ka tihah ngai hek lo che u.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Fu reng reng tangkain mi leisak ngai lo a, in inthawinate thauin mi titlai ngai hek lo: in sualna phurh hnate mi thawhtir zawk a, in khawlohnatein nangnin mi tihah ta a ni.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Kei, keimah ngei hi, keimah leh keimah avang ngawta in bawhchhiatnate thai bo thintu chu ka ni; in sualnate pawh ka hre reng lo ang.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Mi hriatpui rawh u; i ngaihtuah tlang ang u: thiam chantira in awm theihna'n in thu chu sawi rawh u.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> In pu hmasa ber khan thil a tisual a, in palaite pawhin ka lakah an bawhchhia a.chuvangin hmun thianghlima mi liante chu ka tibawrhbang ang a, tichuan Jakob-ho chu anchhedawngah ka siam ang a; Israel-ho chu hauburah ka siam bawk ang.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> chuvangin hmun thianghlima mi liante chu ka tibawrhbang ang a, tichuan Jakob-ho chu anchhedawngah ka siam ang a; Israel-ho chu hauburah ka siam bawk ang."
		},
		"44": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> \"Tunah erawh chuan, aw Jakob-ho ka chhiahhlawhte u, aw Israel-ho ka thlante u, ngaithla rawh u:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> LALPA, nangmahni siamtu, chhul atanga nangmahni dintu, nangmahni tanpuitu tur chuan heti hian a ti: 'Aw Jakobho ka chhiahhlawhte u, nangni Jesurun-ho ka thlante u, hlau suh u.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Tuihal chungah chuan tui ka leih dawn si a, lei rovah chuan tuiluangte chu ka leih bawk dawn a ni: in thlahte chungah ka thlarau ka leih ang a, in fate chungah ka malsawmna ka leih bawk ang:",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> tichuan anni chu, tuipuisuthlahte tui luanna kianga to ang hian, hlobet zingah chuan an to ang.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Mi pakhatin, LALPA ta ka ni, a ti ang a; mi dangin Jakoba hming a invuah ang a;midangin a kutah, LALPA ta, tia ziakin, Israel hming chu chi hmingah an hmang ang,' tiin,\" a ti a.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> LALPA, Israel-ho Lal, an tlantu sipaihote LALPA chuan heti hian a ti: \"Kei hi hmasa bera chu ka ni a, hnuhnung bera pawh ka ni; keimah lo chu Pathian reng reng an awm lo.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Hmasanga mite ka din achinah khan keima tih angin tuin nge ko ang a, tuin nge chung chu sawi ang a, tuin nge ka aiah indawt zelin tilang ang le? Thil lo thleng turte leh lo la awm turte chu sawi rawh se.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Hlau suh u la, tih hek suh u: hmasang khan in hnenah ka sawi tawhin ka hriattir tawh che u a ni lo'm ni? Tichuan nangni hi mi hriatpuitute in ni. Keimah lo hi Pathian reng reng an awm em? A ni, Lungpui reng reng a awm lo; pakhat mah a awm ka hre lo.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> \"Milem siam chawp siamtute chu an zain boruak mai an ni a; an thil duhzawngte chu a tangkai lo ang; an mualphona tur reng rengin anmahni hriatpuitute pawhin an hmu thei lo a, an hre thei hek lo.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Tuin nge pathian din tehlul le? A nih loh leh, tuin nge engmaha tangkai hlei lo milem siam chawp chhung tehlul le?",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ngai teh, a pawlpui zawng zawngte chu an mualpho ang a; hnathawk mite pawh mihring zinga mi an ni: an zain inkhawm vek se la, ding rawh se; an hlau vang a, an mualpho tlang ang.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Thirdengin hreipui a chher thin a, meihawlah chuan a thawlh a, tubohtein a deng a, a ban chak tak chuan a chher thin: a ni, a ril a lo tam a, a tha chu a lo zawi thin: tui reng reng a in lo a, a chau thin.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Thingrem siamtuin hrui a pawt mar a, pensilin a riruat a, nawhmamnatein a riruang a din a, bial siamnain a riruat a, mihring ruangam angin a din a, ina awm tan mihring mawina angin a din thin.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Sidar thingte a tan a kit a, thil leh sasua a la a, ngaw thing zinga mi pakhat chu a puala awm turin a tinghet a: far kung a phun a, ruahin a chawm thin.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Chumi hnuah chuan mi tan meia tuahah a ni tawh ang; chumia mi chu a la a, a intilum thin; a ni, meiah a chhem a, chhang a hem thin: a ni, pathian a siam a, a be thin; chu thing chu milem siam chawpah a siam a, chu chu bawkkhupin chibai a buk thin.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Chu thing chu a then meiah a tuah a; a then chu sa eina'n a hmang a; sa a rawh a, a tlai thin: a ni, mei lum a ai a, 'Chhei, ka lum ta, mei hmel ka hmu ta le,' a ti a:",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> a bang chu pathianah a siam a, a siam chawp milem ngeiah chuan: chu chu bawkkhupa chibai bukin a bia a, a hnenah a tawngtai a, 'Mi chhanhim rawh, ka pathian i ni si,' a ti thin.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> An hre lo a, an ngaihtuah hek lo: ani chuan an hmuh theih lohna turin a maimitchhintir ta si a; an hriat thiam lohna turin an thinlung pawh a kharsak ta a ni.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Tichuan tumah an hre chhuak leh lo a, 'THenkhat chu meiah ka tuah si a; a ni, a vamah pawh chhang ka hem nghe nghe a; sa pawh ka rawh a, ka ei si a: a bang chu thil tenawmah ka siam dawn em ni? Thinga mi bawkkhupin chibai ka buk dawn em ni?' Ti turin anmahniah chuan hriatna leh hriatthiamna a awm hek lo.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Vut chauh a ei thin a: a thinlung buma awm chuan, a nunna a inchhanhim theih lohna tur leh, 'Ka kut ding lamah hian dawt a awm lo em ni?' A tih theih lohna turin, amah chu a pentir ta.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> \"Aw Jakob-hote u, chung thilte chu hre reng rawh u, Israel-hote u, hre reng bawk rawh u, chhiahhlawh in ni si a: keiin ka din che u a; ka chhiahhlawh in ni: aw Israel-hote u, ka theihnghilin in awm lo ang.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> In bawchhiatnate chu chhum chhah mup tihbo angin ka tibo ta a, in sualnate chu chhum tihbo angin ka tibo ta bawk a: ka hnenah lo kir leh rawh u, ka tlan tawh si che u a,\" tiin.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Aw vante u; hlim takin zai rawh u, LALPA'n chu chu a ti ta si a: lei hnuai lamte u, au rawh u, tlangte u, aw ram hnuai leh a chhunga thing awm tinrengte u, hla sa chhuak phut rawh u: LALPA chuan Jakob-ho a tlan tawh a, Israel-hovah chuan a inchawimawi dawn si a.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> LALPA, nangmahni tlantu, chhul atanga nangmahni dintu chuan heti hian a ti: \"Kei hi LALPA, thil zawng zawng siamtu, mahni chauha van kai pharhtu, lei tizautu chu ka ni; tu nge ka hnenah awm?:",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Kei hi dawtheiho chhinchhiahna engmah loa siam a, aienthiamte mi aa siamtu, mi finte hawi kirtira, an hriatna atthlaka siamtu,",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> mahni chiahhlawh thu tingheta, mahni palaite remruat hlensaktu, Jerusalem chungchang thua, 'Chutah chuan mi an awm leh ang,' titu elh Juda ram khaw chungchang thua, 'Siamin a awm leh hlawm ang a, a chhe laite chu ka siam tha leh ang,' titu,",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> tui thuk tak hnena, 'Kang chat rawh, i luite pawh ka tikang bawk dawn,' titu,Kura chungchang thua, 'Ani chu ka beram vengtu a ni a, Jerusalem chungchang thua Siamin a awm leh ang, tih leh, Pathian biak in hnena, I lungphum chu remin a awm leh ang, ti hial khawpin ka duhzawng zawng zawng chu a ti ang,' titu ka ni,\" tiin.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Kura chungchang thua, 'Ani chu ka beram vengtu a ni a, Jerusalem chungchang thua Siamin a awm leh ang, tih leh, Pathian biak in hnena, I lungphum chu remin a awm leh ang, ti hial khawpin ka duhzawng zawng zawng chu a ti ang,' titu ka ni,\" tiin."
		},
		"45": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> LALPA chuan a hriak thih, Kura, hnamte chu a hmaah tudawl tur leh, lalho kawnghrente phelhsak tur leh, a hmaa kawngkharte hawnsak tur leh, kulh kawngkharte khar loa awmtir tura, a kut din lam ka chelha hnenah chuan, heti hian a ti:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> \"Kei i hmaah ka kal ang a, a bumboh laite chu ka tirual ang: dar kawngkharte chu ka tichhe rem rum ang a, a kalhna thir tlawnte chu ka tibung ang:",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> tin, LALPA, i hminga kotu che, Israel-ho Pathian ngei chu ka ni tih i hriat theihna'n thim zinga rote chu ka pe ang chia, hmun fianrialte sum thuhrukte pawh ka pe ang che.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Jakob-ho ka chhiahhlawhte leh Israel-ho ka thlante avang chuan i hmingin ka ko che a ni: mi hre ngai lo mah la, hming ka sak sak ang che.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> ,6 Kei hi LALPA chu ka ni, a dang reng reng an awm lo; keimah lo chu Pathian reng reng an awm lo: keimah lo chu a dang reng reng an awm lo tih ni chhuahna lam atang leh thlang lam atanga an hriat theihna turin, mi hre ngai lo mah la, i tai ka hrensak ang che: kei hi lalpa chu ka ni, a dang reng reng an awm lo.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> ,5 Kei hi LALPA chu ka ni, a dang reng reng an awm lo; keimah lo chu Pathian reng reng an awm lo: keimah lo chu a dang reng reng an awm lo tih ni chhuahna lam atang leh thlang lam atanga an hriat theihna turin, mi hre ngai lo mah la, i tai ka hrensak ang che: kei hi lalpa chu ka ni, a dang reng reng an awm lo.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Eng ka siam thin a, thim pawh ka siam thin a ni; remna ka siam thin a, sualna pawh ka siam thin a ni; kei hi LALPA, chung thil zawng zawng ti thintu chu ka ni,\" tiin.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Vante u, chung lam atang khan far thlaktir rawh u, van dumte khan felna rawn leih thla rawh se: chhandamna an chhawr chhuahtir theihna'n lei inhawng se la, felna nen to duntir rawh se; kei LALPA hian chu chu ka siam a ni.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Mahni Siamtu hnailatu chu a chung a pik e! leia lampei zinga lampei mai mai chu! Hlum chuan a vawtu hnenah, \"Eng nge i siam ni?\" a ti dawn em ni? A nih loh leh, i hnathawh chuan, \"A kutin thia reng a nei lo,\" a ti dawn em ni?",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> A pa hnenah, \"Eng nge i hrin ni?\" titu chung emaw, a nu hnenah, \"Eng nge i hrin dawn ni?\" titu chung emaw a pik e!",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> LALPA, Israel-ho Mi Thianghlim, anmahni Siamtu chuan heti hian a ti: \"Thil lo la thleng tur thu chu mi zawt u la; ka fapate thu-ah leh, ka kut hnathawh thuah hian thu mi pe rawh u.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Lei hi ka siam a, a chunga mihring awm hi ka siam bawk a: keimah ka kut ngei hian, van ka kai pharh a, a sipaihote chu thu ka pe bawk a ni.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Kura chu felna nein ka kai harh a, a kawng zawng zawng chu ka tingil ang: ani chuan a khawpui chu a siam leh ang a, ant lanna man duh vang ni loin, lawmman duh vang ni hek loin,ka salte chu a chhuahtir ang, sipaihote LALPA'n a ti,\"tiin.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> LALPA chuan heti hian a ti, \"Aigupta thawkrimho leh Thiopia sumdawng mi leh Seba-ho mi sang takte chu in hnen lamah an lo kal ang a, in taah an awm tawh ang; namgmahni an zui ang che u; khaidiat bunin a ni an lo kal dawn ni: tichuan bawkkhupin chibai an buk ang che u a, 'Pathian chu nangmahniah a awm ngei mai; a dang reng reng an awm lo, Pathian dang reng reng an awm lo,' tiin.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Aw Israel-ho Pathian, Chhandamtu, Pathian inthu thina chu i ni ngei mai.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Mualpho takin an awm ang, a ni, an zain zak takin an awm ang: milem siamtute chu zahnaah chuan an lut tlang ang.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Israel-ho erawh chu kumkhaw chhandamnaa LALPA Chhandamin an awm ang: chatuan thleng pawhin in mualphoin in zak hek lo ang.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> LALPA, van siamtu chuan, (ani chu Pathian, leilung hi dina siamtu chu a ni; ani chuan leilung hi a tinghet a, engmah loah a siam lo a, mihring awmna'n a din zawk a ni) heti hian a ti si a: \"Kei hi LALPA chu ka ni; a dang reng reng an awm lo.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> A rukin, ram thim hmunah thu ka sawi ngai lo a; Jakoba thlante hnenah, 'Engmah lovah mi zawng rawh u,' ka ti ngai lo: kei LALPA hian felna thu ka sawi thin a, thu dik takte chu ka hril thin.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> \"Inkhawm u la, lo kal rawh u; hnam tin zinga hremna pumpelhote u, lo hnai tlang rawh u: an thing mile siam chawp keng thina, mi chhanhim thei hlei lo pathian hnena tawngtai thintute chuan hriatna reng reng an nei lo.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Sawi u la, rawn tichhuak rawh u; a ni, inberawn hlawm rawh se: hmasang ata tuin nge hriattir? Hman lai ata tuin nge sawi? Kei LALPA hian ka tih a ni law ni? Keimah lo chu Pathian dang reng reng an awm lo; Pathian fel leh chhandamtu ka ni; keimah lo chu a dang reng reng an awm lo.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Kawlkila mi zawng zawngte u, ka lam lo hawi u la, chhandamin awm rawh u: kei hi Pathian ka ni si a, a dang reng reng an awm lo.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Khup tinreng chu ka hmaah a thingthi tawh ang a, lei tinreng pawhin ka hnenah chhechham in thu a tiam tawh ang,' tiin mahni leh mahni inchhalin chhia ka chham ta, thu chu felna hlirin ka ka atangin a chhuak tawh a, a lo let leh tawh lo ang.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Miin 'LALPA-ah chauh felna leh chakna a awm,' tiin, ka hnenah an la sawi ang: ama hnen ngeiah mi an lo kal ang a, a chunga lungni lo zawng zawngte chu mualpho takin an awm tawh ang.Israela thlahte zawng zawng chu LALPA-ah chuan a ni, thiam chantira an awm a, LALPA chu an chhuan dawn ni,\" tiin.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Israela thlahte zawng zawng chu LALPA-ah chuan a ni, thiam chantira an awm a, LALPA chu an chhuan dawn ni,\" tiin."
		},
		"46": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bela chu a lo kun reng a, Neboa chu a lo intihniam reng a; an milemte chu sachungah leh ran chungah an hlang tawh a: in thil vah velpui thinte chu phurah lek siam ani a, sa chau tana phur ritah lek siam ani bawk a.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> An lo intihniam rengin, an lo kun tlang ta reng hlawm a, phur rit chu an chhan him thei si lo a, anmahni ngei pawh chu sala hruaiin an awm ta zawk a.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Aw Jakoba chhungte leh, Israela chhungte zinga la awm chhun zawng zawng, pum a anga ka puak a, chul a anga ka kawm tawhte u, ka thu ngaithla rawh u:",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> in tarkun thleng pawhin amaha chu ka ni ang a, in lua kelsam a to vek thleng pawhin ka pawm ang che u: keima'n ka siam a, keimah vekin ka pua ang; a ni, kei chuan ka pawm ang a, ka chhanhim ang.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Thuhmuna ngaih ka nihna turin tur nen nge mi tehkhina, tu tlukah nge mi siama, tu nen nge mi tehkhin dawn?",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Iptea mi rangkachak bun chhuak thina, tangka buknaa buk hinate chuan, rangkachak chhertu an ruai a, ani chuan pathianah a siam hin a; tichuan an bawkkhup a, a ni, chibai an buk thn.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> An kokiah an pu a, an kalpui a, a hmun turah chuan an dah hin a, a ding ta reng a; a awm na ata chu a sawn tawh lo ang: a ni, miin ani chu an an vang a, nimahsela a chhang thei si lo ang a, an manganna ata a chhan chhuak thei hek lo ang.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Aw bawhchhetute u, chu chuhre reng u la, intimipa u la, hre chhuak leh rawh u,",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Tun hma ahmasang thilte chu hre reng rawh u: kei hi Pathian ka ni a, a dang reng reng an awm si lo: kei hi Pathian ka ni, keimah ang reng reng an awm lo;",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> keiin a tawp turte chu atir a ang rengin ka sawi hin a, thil la tih lohte chu hmasang a ang rengin ka sawi hin; \"Ka remruat chu a ding chhuak ang a, ka duhzawng zawng zawng chu ka ti vek ang,\" ka ti a:",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> khawchhak lam ata sava koham tak, ram hla tak ata ka mi ruat chu ka ko a; a ni, ka sawi tawh a, ka hlen bawk ang; ka tum tawh a, ka ti bawk ang.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Rilru uangthuang, felna hlata awmte u, ka thu ngaithla rawh u;ka felna chu ka rawn la hnai a, hla takah a awm lo ang, ka chhandamna pawhin rei a rial lo ang; tichuan ka ropuina Israel-ho tan chhandamna chu Zion-ah chuan ka dah ang.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> ka felna chu ka rawn la hnai a, hla takah a awm lo ang, ka chhandamna pawhin rei a rial lo ang; tichuan ka ropuina Israel-ho tan chhandamna chu Zion-ah chuan ka dah ang."
		},
		"47": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Aw Babulon fanu nula, chhuk la, vaivutah thu rawh; aw Kaldai fanu, lalthutphah lovah leiah thu rawh : awm no leh nuamsa an ti danw tawh lo che a ni.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Buh rawt sawmna lungte la la, chhang phut siam rawh: i inkhuhna puan kha dah la, i fen fual kha hlip la, i ke kha hawng la, luite dai kai rawh.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> I saruak chu khuh lohin a awm ang a, a ni, i zahmawh chu a lang ang: phuba ka la ang a, mi tumah ka ren lo ang.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Min tlantu chu, a hming sipaihote LALPA a ni, Israel-hote Mi Thianghlim chui.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Aw Kaldai fanu, ngawi rengin thu la thim hnuaiah lut rawh, \"Ram ti lalnu,\" anti dawn tawh lo che a ni.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ka mite chungah ka thinur a, ka rochan chu ka tibawrhbang a, i kutah ka pe chia: nang chuan an chungah khawngaihna reng reng i lantir lo a; tarho chungah lam pawh i nghawngkawl rit tak chu i nghat ta chawrh a.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Tin, \"Kei hi kumkhuain lalnuah ka awm ang,\" i ti a: chutichuan chung thilte chu i rilruin i ngaihtuah lo a, a tawpna tur lah chu i hre reng hek lo.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Chutichuan nang nunkhawnawm bawla, ngaihsam taka awma, mahni rilrua, \"Keimah ka ni, keimah lo chu mi dang reng reng an awm lo, hmeithaiah ka thu lo ang a, fate chan thu ka hre hek lo ang,\" titu, hei hi hre rawh:",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> he'ng thil pahnih, fate channa leh hmeithaina hian, ni khat thil thu-ah mitkhapkar loah a tlakbuiak zawk dawn che a ni: i dawi hmanna chu tam hlein, i invenna chu tam rei rui mah se la, chung chu nasa tak maiin i chungah a lo thleng dawn a ni.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> I suahsualna chu i ring a; \"Tuma'n mi hmu lawi lo e,\" i ti vei si a; i finna leh i hriatna chuan a tikhawlo chia: \"Keimah ka ni, keimah lo chu mi dang reng reng an awm lo,\" i rilruin i ti bawk a.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Chuvangin thil th alo i chungah a lo thleng ang a; a ven dan i thiam lo ang: vanduaina pawhin a tlakbuak ang chia; chu chu i tibo thei lo ang: tiauna pawh vawilehkhatah i chungah alo thleng thut ang a, chu chu i hre lawk lo ang.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> I invenna leh i dawi hmanna, i naupan tet ata i intihhah thinnate chu, dinpui ta che; i sawtpui theih dan phawta, i hnehpui theih dawn phawt chuan.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> I remruat a tam em avangin i hah ta a nih hi: tunah chuan van semtute, arsi thlirtute, thlakipa thu hrilhlawktute chu ding se la, i chunga thil lo la thelng turte lakah chuan chhanhim che rawh se.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Ngai teh, buhpawl ang mai ani ang; meiin a kang ang; meialh thiltihtheihna lakah chuan an inchhanhim lo ang: intihhlumna tur meihawl ang a ni lo ang a; ai tur mei ang pawh a ni hek lo ang.Chutiang chuan i intihhah thinna thilte chu i tan a awm dawn a ni: i naupan tet ata i laka sumdawngtute chu mahni kawng theuhvah an vak bo ang a; chhanhimtu tur che tumah reng reng an awm lo ang.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Chutiang chuan i intihhah thinna thilte chu i tan a awm dawn a ni: i naupan tet ata i laka sumdawngtute chu mahni kawng theuhvah an vak bo ang a; chhanhimtu tur che tumah reng reng an awm lo ang."
		},
		"48": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Aw Jakba chhung, Israela hming tawma, Juda tuite laka chhuaka, thutakah ni si lo a, felnaah ni si hek lo a, LALPA hming chhala chhechham, Israel-ho Pathian hmin glam thintute u, hei hi ngaithla rawh u.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> (khawpui thianghlima mi an inti si thin a, Israel-ho Pathian chungah rinna an nghat abwk a ni; a hming chu sipaihote LALPA a ni).",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Tun hma thilte chu hmasang atangin ka sawi a; a ni, ka ka atangin a chhuak a, ka hriattir a: vawilehkhatah ka hlen thut a, a lo thleng a.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Mi luhlul in nih a, in nghawng chu thir tha a nih a, in chal chu dar a nih ka hriat avangin,",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> hmasang atangin in hnenah ka sawi a; a lo thlen hma pawhin in hnenah ka hriattir che u kha: chutilo chuan, \"Ka milem chuan a tih a ni, ka milem thu a pek a ni,\" in ti dah ang e.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> In hriat kha; he'ng zawng zawng hi en rawh u; nangmahni'n in sawi dawn tawh lawm ni? Tun achinah thil thar ka hriattir dawn a che u, thil inthup in hriat ngai lohte chu.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Chung chu hmasang atanga siam ni loin, tuna siam a ni a; vawiin ni hma khan in bengin in hre ngai lo; chutilochuan, \"Ngai teh, chung chu kan hre reng alawm,\" in ti dah ang e.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> A ni, in bengin in hre ngai lo a; a ni, in rilruin in hr engai hek lo: a ni, hmasang atang rengin in beng chu hawnin a awm ngai lo: vervek tak takin in ti thin tih leh, chhul atang rengin bawhchhetu an ti thin che u tih ka hre si a.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ka tihboral lohna tur che uin ka hming avangin ka thinur chu ka kher rih ang a, fak ka hlawhna'n in chungah ka insum ang.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ngai teh u, ka tithianghlim che u a ni, nimahsela tangka tithianghlim angin a ni lo; hrehawmna rawhtuina meiah chuan ka fiah che u a ni.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Keimah leh keimah avangin, a ni, keimah leh keimah avang ngawtin a ni, ka tih dan ni; ka hming hi engah nge tihchhiatin a awm ang? Ka ropuina hi mi dang hnenah ka pe lo ang.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Aw Jakob-ho leh ka koh Israel-hote u, ka thu ngaithla rawh u: kei hi amaha chu ka ni; a hmasa ber chu ka ni a, a hnuhnung ber pawh ka ni bawk.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> A ni, ka kut hian leilung nghahchhan chu a phum a, ka kut ding lam hian vante khi a kai pharh a: ka koh veleh an ding ho thin.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Nangniho zawng zawngte u, inkhawm u la, ngaithla rawh u; an zingah chuan tuin nge he'ng thil hi sawi ngai? LALPA chuan amah chu a hmangaih a: ani chuan Babulon chungah a duhzawng a ti ang a, a ban chu Kaldai ho chungah lekin a awm ang.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Kei, keimah ngei hian, thu ka sawi ta; a ni, amah chu ka ko a, ka hruai a, a kawng chu a titluang zel ang.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Nangniho hian mi ranw hnaih u la, hei hi ngaithla rawh u; atir atang khan arukin thu ka sawi ngai lo a; a awm tirh atang khan chutah chuan ka awm: tunah hian LALPA Pathian chuan keimah leh a thlarau chu min tir ta a.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> LALPA, nangmahni tlantu, Israelho Mi Thianghlim chuan heti hian a ti: \"Kei hi LALPA in Pathian, in thatna tura nangmahni zirtirtu, in kalna tur kawnga hruaitu che u chu ka ni.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Aw nangni hian ka thupekte chu lo ngaithla ta u la chu aw! I chunga remna chu lui ang maia awmin, in felna chu tuifinriat fawnte ang maiin a awm tur.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> i thlahte pawh tiau vaivut mal te te zatin an awm tur. An hming chu ka hma ata thai boin a awm lo ang a, tihboralin a awm hek lo ang,\" tiin.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Babulon ata chhuak u la, Kaldai-ho chu tlan bosan rawh u, hei hi hla sa thawmin hriattir u la, hrilh u la, kawlkil thleng pawhin tiri u la, \"LALPA chuan a chhiahhlawh Jakob-ho a tlan ta,\" ti rawh u.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Thlalerahte chua a hruai lai khan an tuihal lo a; lungpui atang chuan an tan tuite a luan chhuahtir a: lungpui chu a tihpel a, tichuan tuite chu a lo chhuak ta dur dur a.LALPA chuan, \"Mi suaksualte tna chuan muanna reng reng a awm lo,\" a ti a.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> LALPA chuan, \"Mi suaksualte tna chuan muanna reng reng a awm lo,\" a ti a."
		},
		"49": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Aw thliarkarte u, ka thu ngaithla u la, hla tak ata mi tinte u, ngaithla bawk rawh u: LALPA chuan chhul atang rengin mi ko a; ka nu pum chhung atang rengin ka hming a lo sawi tawh a:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> ka ka hi khandaih hriam tak angin a siam a, a kutah chuan mi thukru a; thla nawhtlet varah mi siam a, a thal bawmah chuan mi khung tlat a:",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> tin, ka hnenah, \"Nang chu ka chhiahhlawh i ni a; Israela, chawimawia ka awmna tura chu i ni,\" a ti a.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Kei erawh chuan, \"Athlawn maiin ka thawkrim a, engmah loah leh boruak maiah ka tha ka seng a: nimahsela matheiloin ka chunga rorelna tur chu LALPA hnenah a ni a awm ni, mi rulhna tur pawh chu ka Pathian hnenah a ni a awm ni,\" ka ti a.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Tin, tunah chuan LALPA, Jakob-ho hnena hruai lehna'n leh, Israel-ho a hnena hruai khawma an awmna'n, a chhiahhlawh awm tura chhul atanga mi dintu chuan a sawi a: (LALPA mithmuhin mi zahawm ka ni si a, ka Pathian chu ka chakna a lo ni ta bawk a:)",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> a ni, ani chuan, \"Jakob-ho hnamte tundinnan leh Israel-ho zinga humhimate chu awmtir lehna'na, ka chhiahhlawha i awm hi, thil te tak te a la ni; Jentailte tiengtu-ah pawh ka ruat bawk ang che, kawlkil thlenga ka chhandamtua i awm theihna turin,\" a ti a.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> LALPA, Israel-ho tlantu leh an Mi Thianghlim chuan, mite hmusita, hnamhoten riau a, roreltute chhiahhlawh hnenah chuan heti hian a ti: \"LALPA rinawma, Israel-ho Mi Thianghlim nangmah thlangtu avang khan lalten an hmu ang a, an tho vang; mi liante pawhin chiobai an buk ang,\" tiin.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> ,9 LALPA chuan heti hian a ti, \"Hun lawmawmah ka ngaithla chia, chhandamna niah ka tanpui che: mi tangte hnenah, 'Chhuak rawh u,' thima awmte hnenah, 'Lo lang rawh u,' tia, ram tung ding tur leh rochan ram tiau tawh hnute anniho chu luahtir turin ka humhim chein, mite thuthlung atan ka ruat ang che. Kawngahte chuan an ei zel ang a, tlang sang kawlh vel vul zawng zawngahte chuan an tlatna hmun chu a awm ang.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> ,8 LALPA chuan heti hian a ti, \"Hun lawmawmah ka ngaithla chia, chhandamna niah ka tanpui che: mi tangte hnenah, 'Chhuak rawh u,' thima awmte hnenah, 'Lo lang rawh u,' tia, ram tung ding tur leh rochan ram tiau tawh hnute anniho chu luahtir turin ka humhim chein, mite thuthlung atan ka ruat ang che. Kawngahte chuan an ei zel ang a, tlang sang kawlh vel vul zawng zawngahte chuan an tlatna hmun chu a awm ang.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> An riltamin an tuihal lo ang a; lumin a tihreawmin niin a em hek lo ang: anmahni khawngaihtu chuan a hruai dawn si a, tuihna kiang ngeiahte chuan a hruai dawn a ni.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Tichuan ka tlang zawng zawng chu kawngah ka siam ang a, ka lamliante chu tihsanin a awm bawk ang.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> En teh, sawngte saw hla tak atangin an lo kal dawn saw; en teh, sanwgte saw hmar la atang te, thlang lam atang tein an lo kal dawn saw; sawngte saw Sinim ram atangin an lo kal dawn saw.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Aw vante u, hlim takin zai rawh u; aw leilung, hlim takin awm rawh; aw tlangte u, hla sa chhuak phut rawh u: LALPA chuan a mite ch a thlamuan si a, mi hrehawm tuarte pawh chu a khawngaih dawn a ni.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> \"Nimahsela Zion chuan, 'Jehoa'n mi kalsan a, LALPA'n mi theihnghilh ta,'a ti a.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> hmeichhiain a fapa, a rila rah chu, khawngaih lohna turin a nau a hnute hne lai chu a theihnghilh thei em ni? Thei e, chungte chuan an theihnghilh a ni thei e, nimahsela kei chuan ka theihnghilh lo ang che.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> En teh, ka kutphahahte hian ak ziak che hi; i kulh bangte chu ka hmaah a awm reng fo a ni.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> I fate chu an hmanhmawh a; nangmah tiboraltute leh nangmah tichhetute chuan an chhuahsan ang che.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> \"Dak la, i mit len vel la, en rawh: he'ng zawng zawng hi an inkhawm a, i hnenah an lo kal a nih hi. Ka nunna chhalin, 'Nang chuan chawimawina inbel angin hengho hi i ineblin, mo a inhreng angin hengho hian i inhreng ngei ang,' LALPA'n a ti.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> I hmun chhia leh tiau hnute leh i ram tihboral hnu thu-ah zawng tunah chuan a awmate atan i te lutuk ngei ngei dawn tawh si a, nangmah lemtute kha hla takah an awm dawn tawh a ni.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> I fa hloh hnua i fa neih lehte chuan, 'Hmun hi ka tan a te lutuk a: ka awmna turin hmun mi pe rawh,' tiin i bengah an la sawi ang.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Tichuan nangin i rilruin, 'Hengho hi tuin nge mi hrinsak ni le? Ka fate ka hloh a, mahni maia sala vak vak ka ni si a: tichuan hengho hi tuin nge tiseilian ni le? Ngai teh, keimah chauha hnutchhiahin ka awm si a, hengho hi khawiah nge an lo awm ni le?' i ti ang,\" tiin.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Lalpa PATHIAN chuan heti hian a ti, \"Ngai teh, hnam tin tan ka kut ka pharin, mi tin tan ka chhinchhiahna ka tar chhuak ang: tichuan i fapate chu apawma pawmin i hnenah an rawn hruai ang a, i fanute pawh an kokia chhuanga rawn hruaiin an awm ang.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Tin, lalte chu i fate pawmtupa an ni ang a, an lalnute pawh chu i fate pawmtunu an ni ang; anni chuan hmaia lei siin chibai an buk ang chia, i kea vaivut chu an liak ang; tichuan kei hi LALPA ka ni tih i hre mai ang, mi nghaktute chu mualphoin an awm lo ang.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> \"rallakte chu mi chak tak lakah chhuhsaka awmin, mi hlauhawm salte chu chhanchhuahin an awm dawn em mi?",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Daw e a, LALPA chuan heti hian a ti, 'Mi chak tak salte meuh pawh chhuhsain an awm ang a, mi hlauhawm rallakte chu chhanchhuahin an awm ang: nangmah dotu chu ka do dawn si a, i fate pawh ka chhandam dawn a ni.Tin, nangmah hnenchhaihtute chu anmahni sa ka eitir ang a; uain thlum rui ang hian anmahni thisenin an rui ang: tichuan mi zawng zawngin, kei LALPA hi nangmah chhandamtu leh nangma tlantu, Jakob-ho Mi Chaka chu ka ni tih, an hria ang,'\" tiin.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Tin, nangmah hnenchhaihtute chu anmahni sa ka eitir ang a; uain thlum rui ang hian anmahni thisenin an rui ang: tichuan mi zawng zawngin, kei LALPA hi nangmah chhandamtu leh nangma tlantu, Jakob-ho Mi Chaka chu ka ni tih, an hria ang,'\" tiin."
		},
		"50": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> LALPA chuan heti hian a ti, \"In nu makna lehkha, ka makna chu, khawiah nge a awm ni? A nih loh leh, ka leibatnate a tu bera hnenah nge ka hralh che u ni? Ngai teh u, in khawlohnate avangin a ni, hralha in awm a, in bawhchhiatnate avangin a ni, in nu pawh kha maka a awm ni.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Eng vangin nge ka lo kal khan mi reng reng an awm loh le? Eng vangin nge ka koh khan mi chhang tur reng reng an awm loh le? Ka kut hi tlan thei lo turin tihtawiin a awm reng reng em ni? A nih loh leh, chhanhim turin thiltihtheihna reng reng ka nei lo em ni? Ngai teh u, ka zilhhaunain tuifinriat ka tikang thin a,luipuite chu ram rovah ka siam thin: tui reng reng a awm loh avangin a sanghate chu a uih a, tuihalin an thi thin.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> van khi thimin ka tuam thin a, saiip puan a khuhna turin ka siam thin,\" tiin.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Mi hah tak chu thu-a ka tihhahdam thiamna'n Lalpa PATHIAN chuan zirtirte lei mi pe a; ani chuan atuk atuk tin, a kai harh a, zirtirten an hriat anga hre turin ka beng hi ka kai harh thin.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Lalpa PATHIAN chuan ka beng mi tihawngsak a, kei chu ka hel lo a, ka hawi kir hek lo.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ka hnungzang hi vawtute hnenah ka dawh a, ka biangte hi hmul pawttute hnenah ka dawh bawk : mualphonaah leh chilah ka hmai ka hup lo.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Lalpa PATHIAN chuan mi tanpui dawn si a; chuvangin ka zak ngai lo va: chuvangin meilung ang tlatin ka hawi thin a, ka mualpho lo ang tih ka hria.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Thiam mi chantirtu chu a hnai e; tuin nge mi do ang? I ding ve ve ang: mi dotu chu tu nge ni? Mi rawn h naih rawh se.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ngai teh, Lalpa PATHIAN chuan mi tanpui ang; tuin nge thiam loh mi chantir ang? Ngai teh, chung zawng zawngte chu silhfen angin a la hlui ang a, thimin a ei chhe vek ang.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> In zingah LALPA tih a, a chhiah hlawh thu awih chu, tu nge ni? Thima leng a, eng reng reng nei lo va chuan LALPA hming chu ring se la, a Pathian chungah innghat rawh se.Mei chhema, thingthutea inhreng thin zawng anwgte u, ngai teh u; in meialhah leh in thingthu halte zingah chuan leng rawh u. Hei hi ka kut atang in la hmuh tur chu a ni; lungngai taka i la mutna tur chu.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Mei chhema, thingthutea inhreng thin zawng anwgte u, ngai teh u; in meialhah leh in thingthu halte zingah chuan leng rawh u. Hei hi ka kut atang in la hmuh tur chu a ni; lungngai taka i la mutna tur chu."
		},
		"51": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Felna umtute u, LALPA zawngtute u, ka thu ngaithla rawh u: nangmahni chherna lungpui lam leh khuarkhuruma nangmahni laih chhuahna khur lam kha en rawh u.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> I pu Abrahama lam leh nangmahni hringtu Sari lam en rawh u; ani chu pakhat chauh a nih lai khan ka ko a, mal ka sawm a, mi ta takah ka siam tak kha.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> LALPA chuan Zion chu a thlmuan ta si a: a hmun che tawhte zawng zawng chu a thlamuan a, a thlaler chu Eden angin a siam a, a ram ro chu LALPA huan angin a siam bawk a; chutah chuan lawmna leh hlimna te, lawm thu sawina leh hla sa thawm te a awm ang.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Aw ka mite u, ka thu hi ngaithla u la; aw ka hnamte u, ka thu-ah hian beng lo chhi rawh u: keimah atangin dan thu a lo chuak dawn si a, mi tin enna turin ka rorelan chu ka chawlhtir ang.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ka felna chu a hnai e, ka chhandamna chu a chhuak tawh a, ka bante hian mi tin ro a relsak ang, thliarkarte chuan mi nghak ang a, ka ban hi an ring ang.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> van lamahte hian in mit len chho u la, hnuai lama leilung chu en rawh u: van khi meikhu angin a la zam ral ang a, leulung hi silhfen angin a la hlui ang, a chhunga awmte chu chutiang bawkin an la thi ang: ka chhamdamna erawh hi chu kumkhuain a awm ang a, ka felna pawh hi tihboin a awm lo ang.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Felna hretu, ka dan thu thinlunga pai mite u, ka thu ngaithla rawh u; mihringte sawichhiatna hlau suh u la, an hauna che u avangin mangang hek suh u.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Thimin silhfen a ei chhe vek angin, anni chu a ei chhe vek dawn si a, sulrulin sahmul a ei angin anni chu a ei dawn a ni: ka felna erawh chu kumkhuain a awm ang a, ka chhandamna chu chhuan zawng zawng thlengin a awm ang.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Aw LALPA ban , harh la, harh la, chakna inbel rawh ; hman laia, hma sang chhuante awm laia i harh ang khan harh rawh. Nang hi Rahab sat sawmtu, drako chhuntu kha i ni lo'm ni?",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Nang hi tuifinriat, tui thuk zau tak tui tikangtu, tuifinriat mawng thuk chu tlante kal kaina tur kawnga siamsaktu i ni lo'm ni?",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Tin, LALPA tlante chu an kir leh ang a, hla sa chungi Zion chu an thleng ang a; chatuana lawmna an lu chungahte a awm tawh ang: lawmna leh hlmna an hmu ang a, lungngaihna leh an rumna chu a bo tawh ang.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Nangmahni thlamuantu che u ka ni a, mihring thi leh mai tur hlobet ang lek hi engati nge in hlauh le?",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Kei LALPA hi nangmahni siamtu ka ni a, vante khi kai pharh a, leilung nghahchhan siamtu ka nih in theihnnghilh ta elo? Eng tizia nge nangmahni hnehchhiah duhtute thinur hlau reng renga in la awm fo le?",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Salhruai bo chu rang taka chhuahin a awm ang a; thiin khuarkhurumah a chhuk lo vang a, a chaw chu a awm lo hek lo ang.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Kei LALPA i Pathian, a fawnte chu ri hum hum khawpa tifinriat chawk lettu chu ka ni si a: ka hming chu sipaihote LALPA a ni.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Tin, van khi ka kaipharh theih a, leilung nghahchahnte ka um theih a, Zion-ho hnenah, \"Ka mite in ni e,\" ka tih theihna'n ka thute chu i kaah ka dah a, ka kutin ka hum che a ni.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Aw Jerusalem , LALPA kut ata thinrimna nova mi in nu, harh la, harh la, tho rawh; nang chuan pai paina bo berhbua mi i in a, i in fai kelh a.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> A fapa hrin zawng zawng zingah chuan amah hruaitu tur tumah an awm lo a; a fapa chawm len zawng anwg zingah chuan a kuta chelh tumah an awm hek lo.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Heng thil pahnih hian a tlak buak tak che hi; tuin nge tahpui dawn che aw? Tiauna leh chhiatna te, tam leh khandaihte hian; engtin nge ka thlamaun ang che aw?",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> I fapate chu an chau a, sathar lena a awk angin thler lu lam zawng zawngah chuan an mu phung a; LALPA thinrimna leh i Pathian zilhhaunain an khat hlawm a ni.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Chuvangin, nang tihretheih leh uain rui ni si loa mi rui, hei hi hre tawh rawh:",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> i LALPA Jehoa, i Pathian, i mite thu sawipui thintu chuan, heti hian a ti, \"Ngai teh, pai paina no, ka thinrimna no berhbu ngei chu, i kut ata ka la chhuak ta; i in leh tawh lo ang:tichuan nangmah tiretheitute kutah chuan ka dah ang; anni chuan i nunna hnenah, 'Kan zawh tur chein bawkkhup rawh,' an tih kha: tichuan nangin zawhtute hnenah chuan i hnungzang chu lei ang leh kawtthler angin i dah kha,\" tiin.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> tichuan nangmah tiretheitute kutah chuan ka dah ang; anni chuan i nunna hnenah, 'Kan zawh tur chein bawkkhup rawh,' an tih kha: tichuan nangin zawhtute hnenah chuan i hnungzang chu lei ang leh kawtthler angin i dah kha,\" tiin."
		},
		"52": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Aw, Zion, harh la, harh la, i chakna inbel rawh; aw Jerusalem, khawpui thianghlim, i silhfen mawi takte chu inbel rawh: tun achinah chuan serhtan loh leh mi bawlhhlawh chu i chhungah an lut dawn tawh si lo.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Aw Jerusalem, vaivut i kai kha inthing rawh; tho la, thu rawh: aw Zion fanu, sala awm, i nghawng phuarnate kha phelh rawh.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> LALPA chuan heti hian a ti si a, \"Engmah loa hralh in ni a; tichuan tangka loa tlan in ni tawh ang,\" tiin.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Lalpa PATHIAN chuan heti hian a ti si a, \"Ka mite chu atirah chuan Aigupta rama awm turin an chhuk a: tin, Assuria min enga khawlawi loin an hnehchhiah hlawm a.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Chutichuan tunah, hetah hian eng nge ka tih dawn? Ka mite hi engmah loa hruai boin an awm si a, LALPA'n an ti, a chunga roreltute chu an te tuar tuar a, LALPA'n a ti, ka hming hi nilenga sawichhiatin a awm fo.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Chuvangin ka mite chuan ka hming an hria ang; chuvangin chumi niah chuan a sawitu chu ka ni tih an hria ang; ngai teh, keimah hi ka ni,\" tiin.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> tlangahte chanchin tha thlena, remna thu tlangaupuia, thil tha chanchin tha a thlena, chhandamna thu tlangpuia, Zion hnena \"I Pathian chu lalah a thu,\" titu ke chu a va mawi em!",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Chu! I ral vengtute aw chu! Aw an chhuah a, hlim takin an zaiho chu: LALPA chu Zion-a a lo kir leh hunah chuan inhmatawnin an hmu dan si a.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Jerusalem hmun chhe tawhte u, hlim chhuak phut u la, hlim takin zaiho rawh u: LALPA chuan amite chu a thlamuan ta si a, Jerusalem chu a tlan ta a ni.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> LALPA chuan hnam tinrengte mithmuhah a ban thianghlim chu a hlim ta; tichuan kawlkila mi zawng anwgin kan Pathian chhandamna chu an hmu ang.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Chhuak rawh u, chhuak rawh u, chuta tang chuan chhuak rawh u, thil bawlhhlawh reng reng dek suh u; a chhung ata kal chhuak rawh u; LALPA bungbel kengtue u, thianghlim takin awm rawh u.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Hmanhmawh akin in kal chhuak dawn si lo a, tlan chhiain in kal dawn hek lo: LALPA chuan in hma a hruai dawn si a; Israel-ho Pathian chu in hnudaltu a ni ang.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ngai teh, ka chhiahhlawh chuan fing takin a ti ang a, chawimawi leh chawisanin a awm ang, sang tak maiin a awm ang.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> A hmel chu mihring hmel ai maha tihchhiat a ni a; a pianhmang pawh mihring pianhmang aia tihchhiat a ni bawk; mi tam takin mak an tih ang bawkin,hnam tam takin mak an ti a, lalho pawh mak tiin an dang reng ang, an hmuh ngai loh an hmuin an hriat ngai loh an hria ang.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> hnam tam takin mak an ti a, lalho pawh mak tiin an dang reng ang, an hmuh ngai loh an hmuin an hriat ngai loh an hria ang."
		},
		"53": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Kan thu sawi tuin nge ring? LALPA kut chu tu hnenah nge a lan?",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> A hmaah chuan huan thil tiak no tak angin ani chu a chawr chhuak si a, lei ro atanga zung angin a puak chhuak bawk a ni: piahmang thatna leh hmel mawina reng reng a nei lo a; amah ka hmuhin amah kan duhna turin mawina reng reng a awm lo.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ani chu mihringte hmusit leh duh lohin a awm a; lungngaihante nei mi leh natna hre mi a ni a: miten an hmai an huhsan ang chuan ani chu hmusitin a awm a, keini lah chuan ani chu kan ngaisang si lo.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ani chuan kan natnate phurin, kan lungngaihnat epah a phur ngei a: nimahsela keini chuan lungngaihna tlakbuakah, Pathian vuakah, tihretheihah kan ngai si a.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Nimahsela ani chu kan bawhchhiatnate avangin hliamin a awm a, kan khawlohnate avangin vuak thitlinin a awm a:kan thlamuanna tur thununna chu a chungah a tla a; a vuakna vualtea tihdamin kan awm ta.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> kan za hian beram angin kan vak bo a; mahni kawng kawngah kan peng theuh a; Lalpa chuan ani chuungah chuan kan za khawlohna chu a nghat ta a.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ani chu hnechhiahin a awm a, nimahsela a inngaitlawm a, a ka pawh a ang lo: beram no talh tura an hruaia ang leh, beram a hmul mettu hmaa a ngawi renga awm ang maiin; a ni, a ka a ang lo.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Hnehchhiahna leh rorelnaa lak boin a awm a; a dam rualpi lek phei chu tuin nge mi nung ram ata tihborala a awm chu ngaihtuah tehlul ni? Ka mite bawhchhiatna avangin lungngaihna tlak buakin a awm a ni.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Tin, thil rawng taka ti ngai loin, a kaah tihderna reng reng awm ngai lo mah sela, a thlan chu mi sualte hnen lamah an ruatsak a, a thih hnu chuan mi hausa hnen lamah a awm a.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Nimahsela LALPA'n ani chu vuak thitlin a duh reng a ni; a tina ta ngei a: a nunna chu sual tan thil hlana i hman tikah, a chi thlah chu a hmu tawh ang a, a damchhung nite chu a tisei ang a, LALPA duhzawng chu a kutah hlawhtling a awm ang.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> A nunna thawhrim rah chu a hmu ang a, a lungpui tawh ang: ka chhiahhlawh fel tak chuan a hriatnain mi tam tak chu thiam a chantir ang a, an khawlohnate chu a phurhsak ang.chuvangin ani chu mi liante chanvo ang ka sem ve ang a, ani chuan rallak sumte chu mi chakte a sem ve ang; a nunna chu thi khawp hiala a leih buak a, bawhchhetute zinga chhiar tela a wm avangin: nimahsela mi tam tak sualna chu a phur a, bawhchhetute tan chuan a tawngtaisak a.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> chuvangin ani chu mi liante chanvo ang ka sem ve ang a, ani chuan rallak sumte chu mi chakte a sem ve ang; a nunna chu thi khawp hiala a leih buak a, bawhchhetute zinga chhiar tela a wm avangin: nimahsela mi tam tak sualna chu a phur a, bawhchhetute tan chuan a tawngtaisak a."
		},
		"54": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Aw ching, nang, fa hring ngai lo, hlim takin zai rawh; nang, nau vei ngai lo, hla sa chhuak phutin, au chhuak rawh: pasal nei mi fate ai chuan khawharnu fate an tam zawk si, LALPA'n a ti.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> I puan in hmun chu zauh rawh, i awmnate puan in chung chu kai pharh rawh se: ren suh: i hruite chu tisei la, i kaihmarna khente chu tinghet rawh.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ding lam leh vei lamah i darh zau dawn si a; tichuan i chi thlahte chuan hnam tin an rochung ang a, khawpui tiau hnuahte chuan mi an awmtir leh ang.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Hlau suh, i mualpho dawn si lo: zak hek suh, mualphoin i awm dawn si lo: i tleirawl lai mualphona chu i theihnghilh tawhin, i hmeithaina hmingchhiatna chu i hre reng dawn tawh si lo.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Nangmah Siamtu chu i pasal a ni si a; a hming chu sipaihote LALPA a ni: Israel-ho Mi Thianghlim chu nangmah tlantu a ni bawk a ni; ani chu khawvel zawng zawng Pathian an ti ang. Nupui rilrua lungngai tak, tlangval laia nupui tawh, paih hnu koh leh angin LALPA'n a ko che a nih hi, i Pathianin a ti.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Mitkhapkar lek ka ma chia; nimahsela khawngaihna nasa takin ka hruai leh ang che.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ka thinur liamin mitkhapkar i lakah ka hmai ka thup a; nimahsela kumkhawngilneihnain ka khawngaih ang che, LALPA nangmah tlantu chuan a ti. Chu chu ka tan Nova tuite ang kha a ni si a: \"Nova tuite chuan lei a chim pil leh tawh lo ang,\" tia, chhia ka chham ang khan, \"I chungah ka thinur tawh lo ang a,ka zilhhau tawh hek lo ang che,\" tiin, chhia ka chham ta a ni.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Tlang liante chu an kal bo ang a, tlang tete chu sawnin an awm bawk ang; ka ngilneihna erawh hi chu i lak ata a kal bo lo ang a, ka remna thuthlung chu sawnin a awm hek lo ang, LALPA a khawngaihtu che chuan a ti.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Aw nang tihretheih, tuifawn vawrh vawrh, thlamuanna nei lo, ngai teh,i lungrem chu lung tha miin ka rem ang a, i lungphumte chu sapphir lungtein ka rem bawng ang.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> I chhip zumte ch rubi lungin, i kawngkharte chu karbankul lungin, i kulh zawng zawng chu lungmawitein ka siam ang.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Tin, i fate zawng zawng chu LALPA zirtirin an awm ang a, i fate thlamuanan chu nasa tak a ni ang.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Felnaa tihnghehin i awm ang a: hnehchhiahna ata hla takah i awm ang a, i hlau dawn lo a ni; thil rapthlak ata hla takah i awm bawk ang a, a hnaih dan lo che a ni.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ngai teh, bei tur chein an la pung khawm a ni thei a, neimahsela ka thu a ni lo vang: angmah bei tura pung apiangte chu nangmah avangin an tlu ang.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Ngai teh, kei chuan thirdeng pum zapa a hnatahwhna tur hriam chher thintu chu ka siam a; keimah vekin tichhe turin tichhetu ka siam bawk a ni.Nangmah beina tura hriam chher reng reng a sawt lo ang; lei tinreng thupawia nangmah rawn khingtute chu thiam loh i chantir ang. Chu chu LALPA chhiahhlawhte rochan chu ani a, an felna chu ka hnen ata a ni, LALPA'n a ti.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Nangmah beina tura hriam chher reng reng a sawt lo ang; lei tinreng thupawia nangmah rawn khingtute chu thiam loh i chantir ang. Chu chu LALPA chhiahhlawhte rochan chu ani a, an felna chu ka hnen ata a ni, LALPA'n a ti."
		},
		"55": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Hawh u, tuihal apiangte u, tuiahte hian lo kal rawh u, tangka nei lote pawh; lo kal u la, lei u la, ei rawh u; a ni lo kal u la, uain leh hnutetui tangka pe loin, a man pawh pe loin lei rawh u.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> chaw ni si loah eng vangin nge tangka in sen? Puar leh fanna ni si loah eng vangin nge in tha in sen? Ka thu ngun takin ngaithla u la, thil tha chu ei rawh u, in nunna chu thil thauvah chuan hlim rawh se.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> In beng rawn dawh u la, ka hnenah lo kal rawh u; ngaithla u la, tichuan in nunna chu a nung ang: tin, in hnenah kumkhaw thu ka thlung ang, Davida hnena khawngaihna tiam tlatte chu.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ngai teh, ani chu mi tin tan hretuah ka ruat a, mi tin tan hruaitu leh hotuah ka ruat a ni.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ngai teh, i hriat ngai loh hnam chu i ko ang a, nangmah hre ngai lo hnam chu i hnenah an lo tlan ang, LALPA i Pathian avang leh Israel-ho Mi Thianghlim avang chuan; ani chuan a chawimawi si chia.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Hmuh awla a awm loa hian LALPA chu zawng u la, a hnaih lai hian ko rawh u:",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> mi suaksual chuan a awm dan chu bansan se la, mi fel lo chuan a ngaihtuahnate chu bansan bawk rawh se: LALPA hnenah kir leh rawh se, tichuan anin a lo khawngaih ang; kan Pathian hnenah kir leh rawh se, anin a ngaidam nasa khawp dawn si a.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ka ngaihtuahte hi i ngaihtuahte a ni si lo a, i awm dante chu ka awm dan a ni hek lo, LALPA'n a ti.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Van khi lei aia a sang zawk angin, ka awm dante hi in awm dante aiin a sang zawk si a, ka ngaihtuahte pawh hi in ngaihtuahte aiin a sang zawk bawk a ni.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ruah leh vur chu van atangin a sur thin a, khi lamah khian a kir leh ngai lo a, lei hi a chawm zawk a, thil a totirin a chawrtir a, buh chi thehtu hnenah buh chi a pe a, eitu hnenah ei tur a pe thin;",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Chutiang bawkin ka ka atanga ka thu chhuak chu a awm ang: engmah tih nei loin ka hnenah a kir leh lo ang a, ka duh ang chu a tizo zawk ang a, thil ti tura ka tirhnaah chuan a hlawhtling bawk ang.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Hlim taka chhuakin, thlamuang taka hruai chhuahin in awm dawn si a: tlang liante leh tlang tete chuan in hmaah hla an sa chhuak phut ang a, phul thing zawng zawngte chuan an kut an beng bawk ang.Hnimhlingnei ai chuan far a to zawk ang a, buar ai chuan lenhmui a to zawk ang: chu chu LALPA tan hming thatna tur leh kumkhaw chhinchhiahna tihborala awm lo tur a ni ang.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Hnimhlingnei ai chuan far a to zawk ang a, buar ai chuan lenhmui a to zawk ang: chu chu LALPA tan hming thatna tur leh kumkhaw chhinchhiahna tihborala awm lo tur a ni ang."
		},
		"56": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> LALPA chuan heti hian a ti, \"Dik takin ro rel u la, fel takin ti rawh u: ka chhandamna chu a lo thleng dawn dawnin ka felna chu a lo lang dawn ta si a.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Chutiang ti mi leh, chumi pawm tlattu mihring fapa chu, a eng a thawl e; chawlhni bawhchhe loa serh thintu leh, thil tha lo reng reng ti lo tura a kut veng tha thintu chu.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Tin, ram dang mi, LALPA zamwtu chuan, 'LALPA'n a mite lakah mi tihrang ngei ang,' ti suh se: mi tilreh chuan, 'En teh, thing ro ka nih hi,' ti hek suh se.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ka chawlhnite serha, ka lawmzawng thilte thlanga, ka thuthlung pawm tlattu mi tilrehte chungchang thu-ah chuan LALPA'n heti hian a ti si a:",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> An hnenah ka in chhungah leh ka kulh chhungahte chuan fanu leh fapa neite ai mah chuan hriat rengna tha zawk leh hming tha zawk ka pe ang; an hnenah kumkhaw hming, tihboral tawh loh tur ka pe ang,' tiin.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ram dang mite pawh, chawlhni bawhchhe loa serh thin leh, ka thuthlung pawm tlat apiang, LALPA rawng bawl tur leh, LALPA hming ngaina tur leh, a chhiahhlawhahte awm tura LALPA zawm apiangte chu;",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> anni ngei chu ka tlang thianghlimah chuan ka hruai ang a, ka tawngtaina inah ka tihlim ang; halrala an thil hlante leh an inthawinate chu ka maichamah chuan lawmin a awm ang: ka in chu mi tinreng tan tawngtaina in an ti dawn si a,\" tiin.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Lalpa PATHIAN, Israel hnawh chhuahhote hruai khawmtu chuan, \"Hruai khawm sate bakah mi dang pawh ka la hruai khawm ang,\" a ti a.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ram sa zawng zawngte u, a ni, ramhnuaia sa awm zawng zawngte u, ei turin lo kal rawh u.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> A ralvengtute chu an mit a del a, hriatna nei lo hlir an ni a; ui aw nei lo hlir an ni a, an bauh thei lo; mumang neia, mu renga, mut duh mi an ni a.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> A ni, uite chu duham tak an ni a, tawk tih lem an nei ngai lo; chung chu beram vengtu thil hre thei lote an ni: mahni kawng kawng, mahni hlawkna lam theuh, an hawi vek hlawm, an zavai maiin.\"Lo kal rawh u, uain ka la ang a, tichuan zuin kan inthun khat dan nia; naktuk chu vawiin ang hi a ni leh ang a, ni ropui nasa deuh mai ani ang,\" an ti theuh a.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> \"Lo kal rawh u, uain ka la ang a, tichuan zuin kan inthun khat dan nia; naktuk chu vawiin ang hi a ni leh ang a, ni ropui nasa deuh mai ani ang,\" an ti theuh a."
		},
		"57": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Mi tha an thi a, tuma'n pawi an ti lo; Pathian ngaihsak mite pawh an thi a, tuma'n chhiatna thleng tur laka lak bo an ni tih an ngaihtuah lo.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Mi fel chu a thi a, thil tha loin a khawih phak lo a, dik tak a ti thinte chu thlamuang takin an khumah an mu siai siai thin.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Nimahsela nangni dawithiamnu fapa, uire leh nawhchizuar thlahte u, hetah lo hnai rawh u.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Tunge nuihza siamna'n in hman thin le? Tunge in thensana, lei in chhuah khum thin le?",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Nangni sasaw zinga, thing buk hnuai tina intizauthau a, ruam chhungte lung khi belahte naupang that thinte u, bawhchhiatna fa, dawttheihan thlahte in ni lo'm ni?",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Luikawr ruam lung mam zingah chuan i chanvo a awm a; chung, chungte ngei chu, i chanpual chu a ni: chungte tan ngei chuan thilhlan in mi i leih a, thil pek i hlan kha. Chung thilah chuan tihlungawiin ka awm dawn em ni?",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Tlang sang zo tak chungah chuan i khum chu i dah a: Moleka hnenah i kal a.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Tin, kawngkharte leh kawngka biang phenahte chuan i hriat rengna chu i tung a: ka lakah ni loin mi dang lakah i inhlip a, i han chho si a, i khum i zauh a, an hnenah thu i thlung a; an khum chu i hmuhnaah chuan i hmangaih a.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Tin, hriak nen lal hnenah i kal a, i rimtuite chu i ti nasa zual a, i palaite chu hla takah i tir a, Seol thleng rawkin i intihhniam kha.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> I kalna kawng sei avang khan i hah a: nimahsela, \"Beiseina reng reng a awm lo,\" i ti si lo va: i chakna tihharhna i hmu a; chuvangin i chauh tak loh kha.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Tunge i hlauha i tih a, dawt i sawi thina, kei mi hriat tak loh a, i rilrua i ngaihtuah tak loh le? Rei tak ka ngawi reng lo em ni?Hlau pawh mi hlauh loh hi.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> I felna thu hi ka sawi ang a; i thitihte zawng i tan engmah a hnemhnang lo ang.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> I au hunah chuan milim lak khawmte chuan chhanhim che rawh se; nimahsela anniho chu thliin a la ang a, thawin a len bo vek ang: kei mi ringtu erawh chuan ram hi a nei ang a, ka tlang thianghlim hi a luah ang.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Tin, ani chuan, \"Chhung pawng rawh u, chhung pawng rawh u, kawng buatsaih rawh u, ka mite kawng ata tlukna tur chu paih rawh u,\" a ti ang.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Mi chungnung, chawisan, chatuana awm, a hming Thianghlima chuan heti hian a ti si a: \"Kei hmun chungnung leh thianghlimah ka awm a, mi thuhnuairawlhte rilru tiharh tur leh inchhir ngawih ngawihte thinlung tiharh turin mi rilrua inchhir ngawih ngawiha thuhnuairawlh tak hnenah pawh ka awm a ni.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Kumkhuain ka do dawn si lo a, ka thinur fo dawn hek lo: chutichuan mi rilru ka hmaah a chau vang a, nunna ka siamte pawh chu an chau bawk ang.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> A duhama a khawlohna avangin ka thin a ur a, ka vua a, ka hmai ka hup a, ka thin a ur a ni: ani lah chu a thinlung awm dan pangngaiha luhlul takin a awm zel a.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> A awm dante chu ka hmu a, amah chu ka tidam ang: ka hruai bawk ang a, amah leh a sunpuitute hnenah thlamuannate ka pe leh ang.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Kei chuan hmui rah ka siam thin a: 'Remna, remna, hla taka awm hnenah leh hnai taka awm hnenah chuan awm rawh se,' LALPA'n a ti, ani chu ka tidam ang.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Mi suaksualte erawh chu tuifinriat fawn fawn thin ang chu an ni: an awm hle hle thei si lo a, a tuite chuan bawlhhlawh leh chirhdiak a vawrh chhuak thin,\"tiin.Ka Pathian chuan, \"Mi suaksualte tan chuan muanna reng reng a awm lo,\" a ti a.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Ka Pathian chuan, \"Mi suaksualte tan chuan muanna reng reng a awm lo,\" a ti a."
		},
		"58": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ring takin au rawh, inren suh, tawtawrawt angin i aw chhuah tuar tuar la, ka mite hnenah an bawhchhiatna chu hril la, Jakoba chhungte hnenah an sualnate hril bawk rawh.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Anni chuan zanw zawng ni tin, mi zawng thin a, ka kawng thute hriat zawng an chak thin: fel taka ti leh an Pathian rorelna bansan ngai lo hnam angin ka hnenah rorelan fel tak mi dil thin a, Pathian rawn hnaih pawh an chak thin a ni.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> \" Eng vangin nge chaw ka nghei a, i hmuh si loh? Eng vangin nge ka intihretheih a,i hriat si loh?\" an ti thin. Ngai teh u, in chaw nghei ni chuan nangmahni nawmsak in bawl a, in hnathawktute zawng zawng in hnehchiah thin.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ngai teh u, innghirnghona leh inhnialna tur leh, suahsualna kuttuma inchum turin a ni, chaw in nghei thin ni: in aw hi chung lama hriattir tlak zawngin chumi ni chuan chaw in nghei ngai lo.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Chutiang chu chaw ngheina ka duhzanga chu em ni? Mi a intihretheihna tur ni a ni em ni? Phungladin anga a lu kun tur leh, a hnuaia saiip puan phaha vut phul tur em ni? Chung chu chaw ngheina leh LALPA tan ni lawmtlak i ti dawn em ni.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Hei hi chaw ngheina ka duhzawnga chu a ni lo'm ni? Nghawngkawl hruite hlihsak leh, hnehchhiahho chhuahtir leh, nghawngkawl hruite hlihsak leh, hnehchhiahho chhuahtir leh, nghawngkawl tinreng tihtliahsak hi.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Mahni chaw mi riltamte hnena sem leh, rethei hnawhchauhho mahni ina hruai hi a ni lo'm ni? Mi saruak hmuha puan vawm leh, mahni tisa ang pu laka bihruk loh hi a ni lo'm ni?",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Chumi hunah chuan i eng chu zing ni chhuak angin a lo chhuak ang a, i damna tur chu a lo chawr chhuak thuai ang: i felna chuan i hma a hruai ang a: LALPA ropuina chu i hnudaltu a ni ang.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Chumi hunah chuan i ko ang a, tichuan LALPA'n a chhang ang; i au vang a, tichuan anin, \"Heta hi ka awm,\" a ti ang. In zinga ta nghawngkawl te, zungtanga mi kawh te, sual taka tawng te hi i tihbo a,",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Riltamte tan i inphal a, tihretheihte i tihtlai bawk chuan, i eng chu thim zingah a eng chhuak ang a, i thim mupna chu chhun ang a ni tawh ang:",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> tin, LALPA chuan a hruai fo ang chia, hmun rovah pawh a titlai ang chia, i ruhte pawh a tichak bawk ang; tin, huan tuia chawm ang leh, tuihna kang ngai lo ang i ni tawh ang.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Tichuan i laka lo la chhuak turte chuan hmun hlui chhe tawhte chu an rem leh ang a: chhuan tam tak lungphumahte chuan i rem chho leh ang; tichuan nang chu, \"A chhe lai siamthatu,\" \"Mi awmna tura kawngte siamthatu,\" an ti ang che.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Chawlhni bawhchhe lo tura, ka ni thianghlima i duhzawng ti lo tura i kephah chu i hawi kirtir a, chawlhni lawmawm i tih a, LALPA ni thianghlim chu zahawm i tih a, mahni kawng zawh lo a, mahni nawmsang bawl lo a, mahni thu sai loa i chawimaw chuan,LALPA chungah chuan i lawm ang a, leilung hmun sangahte chuan ka chuantir ang chia; i pu Jakoba rochun thilin ka chawm ang che: LALPA ka chuan chu chu a sawi tawh a ni.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> LALPA chungah chuan i lawm ang a, leilung hmun sangahte chuan ka chuantir ang chia; i pu Jakoba rochun thilin ka chawm ang che: LALPA ka chuan chu chu a sawi tawh a ni."
		},
		"59": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ngai teh u, LALPA kut chu chhandam thei lo turin tihtawiin a awm lo a; a beng chu hre thei lo turin a ngawng hek lo:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> in khawlohnate chu nangni leh in Pathian kara tlain a tithen zawk che u a ni a, benga a hriat duh lohna turin in sualnate chu a hmai chu a hliahsak bawk che u a ni.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> In kutte chu thisena tihbawlhhlawhin a awm a, in kut zungtangte lah khawlohnaa tihbawlhhlawhin a awm si a; in hmuite chuan dawt a sawi a, in lei chu suahsualna thu saiwin a phun nuah nuah thin.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Tuma'n dik takin thupawi an sawi lo a, tumah thutak takin thu an sawipui ngai lo:boruak mai mai hi an ring a, dat an sawi thin a; thiltihsualna an pai a, khawlohna an hring thin.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Rulmuk tuite an awp keu a, maimawm ril puan an tah thin: an tui eitute chu an thi thin a, tihkeha awmah chuan rul a lo chhuak thin.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> An maimawm ril puan chu silhfenahte a chang lo ang a, an thiltihte chu an inbel hek lo ang: an thiltihte chu khawlohna thiltihte a ni a, thil rawng taka tihna chu an kutah a awm bawk a.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> An kete chu thil tha lo lamah a tlan thin a, thisen sawiselbo chhuah turin an hmanhmawh thin: an ngaihtuahte chu khawlohna ngaihtuahnate a ni thin a; tiauna leh chhiatna chu an kawngahte a awm thin.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Thlamuanna kawng an hre lo a; an kalhnaahte chuan dikna reng reng a am ngai lo: an tan kawng kawite an siam a; chuta kal apiang chuan thlamuanna an hre ngai lo.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Chuvangin rorelna chu keimahni atanga hla takah a awm thin a, felna chuan min um phak ngai hek lo: eng kan nghak thin a, nimahsela, ngai teh, thim a lo ni thin; enna kan nghak thin a, nimahsela thim mupah bawk kan kal thin.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Mitdel angin bang kan dap dun dun thin a, a ni, mit nei lote angin kan dap dun dun thin: thimhlim ang maiin chhunah kan inchhuih thin a; mi chakte zingah chuan mitthi ang mai kan ni.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Savawmte angin kan zain kan huk dur dur thin a, thurote angin nasa takin kan rum nghuat nghuat thin: rorelna kan nghak thin a, nimahsela a awm hauh si lo a; chhandamna kan nghak thin a, nimahsela keimahni atangin hla takah a awm thin.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Kan bawhchhiatnate hi i hmaah a pung ta si a, kan sualnate hian min hek thin a ni: kan bawhchhiatnate hi kan hnenah a awm reng si a, kan khawlohnate zawng kan hria a ni:",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> kan bawhchiat te, LALPA kan phatsan te, kan Pathian zui zel loa kan hawisan te, hnehchhiah thu leh hel thu kan sawi te, dawt thu kan pai a, thinlung ata kan sawi chhuah thinte hi.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Tichuan rorelna chuan hnung lam min hawisan a, felna chuan hla takah min dinsan ta: thutak chu kawtthlerah a tlu reng si a, dikna chu a lut thei lo a ni.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> A ni, thutak a awm ta lo a; thil tha lo bansantu chu rallakah a insiam thin: tichuan LALPA'n chu chu a hmu a, rorelna reng reng awm ta lo chuan a tilungni ta lo a.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Tin, mi reng reng an awm lo tih a hria a, dilsaktu reng reng an awm lo chu mak a ti a: chuangin ama ban ngei chuan chhandamna a insiam a; ama felna ngei chuan a inchelh ding ta a.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Tin, felna chu awmphawah a ha a, chhandamna lukhum akhum a; tin, inthuamnaah chuan phuba lakna silhfente chu a inbel a, kawrfualah chuan thahnemngaihna a ha a.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> An thiltihte angin, an thiltihte ang ngeiin ani chuan a thungrul ani chuan a thungrula ng, amah dotute chu thinrimnain, a hmelmate chu thungrulhnain a thungrul ang; thliarkarte chu thungrulhnain a thungrul ang.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Chutichuan LALPA hming chu tlang lam atangin LALPA hming chu tlang lam atangin an tih ang a, a ropuina ni chhuahna atangin an tih bawk ang; ani chu tui lian thut, LALPA thawa chhem luan vut vut angin a lo kal dawn si a.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Tin, Zion-ah chuan tlantu a lo kal ang a, Jakob-ho zinga bawhchhiatna hawisantute hnenah pawh a lo kal ang, LALPA'n a ti:Kei zawng hei hi a ni, an hnena ka thuthlun chu ni LAPAN a ti: ka thlarau i chunga awm leh, ka thu i kaa ka dahte chuan, tun achinah chatuan thleng pawhin i ka chu an chhuahsan lo ang a, i thlahte ka chu an chhuahsan hek lo ang a, i thlahte thlah leh chhawng ka pawh tun atanga kumkhuain an chhuahsan hek lo ang, LALPA'n a ti.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Kei zawng hei hi a ni, an hnena ka thuthlun chu ni LAPAN a ti: ka thlarau i chunga awm leh, ka thu i kaa ka dahte chuan, tun achinah chatuan thleng pawhin i ka chu an chhuahsan lo ang a, i thlahte ka chu an chhuahsan hek lo ang a, i thlahte thlah leh chhawng ka pawh tun atanga kumkhuain an chhuahsan hek lo ang, LALPA'n a ti."
		},
		"60": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Tho la, eng rawh; i eng chu a lo thleng a, LALPA ni ropuina chu i chunga lo chhuah tak hi.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Ngai teh, thimin leilung hi a khuh dawn si a, thim chhah mupin mite a khuh bawk dawn a ni: nimahsela LALPA chu i chungah a lo chhuak ang a, a ropuina chu i chungah a la lang ang.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Tichuan hnam tin i eng lamah an lo kal ang a, lalte pawh i lo chhuah enna lamah an lo kal bawk ang.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Dak la, i mit len vel la, en rawh: an zain an inkhawm a, i hnenah an lo kal a nih hi: i fapate chu hla tak atangin an lo kal ang a, i fanute chu an rawn pawm ang.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Chumi hunah chuan i hmu ang a, i eng tawh ang a, i thinlung chu a khur a, tihzauin a awm ang; tuifinriata sumdawnna tam tak mai chuan i hnen lam a pan dawn avang leh, hnam tin sum chuan i hnen a lo thlen dawn avangin.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Sanghawngsei tam tak mai chuan an tuam dul dul ang che, Midian leh Epha rama Sanghawngsei tuaite chuan; chung zawng zawng chu Seba ram atangin an lo kal ang: rangkachak leh beraw an rawn phur ang a, LALPA fakna thu an hriattir ang.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Kedar-ho ran rual zawng i hnenah an lo kal khawm ang a, Nebai-otha-ho berampate chuan i rawng an bawl ang: ka maichamah chuan lawmin an chho ang a, ka ropuinain chu ka chawimawi ang.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Chhum anga thlawkte leh, thuro anmahni tukverh pana thlawk noh noh anga thlawkte saw tute nge ni?",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ani chuan a chawimawi che avangin LALPA i Pathian hming atan leh Israel-ho Mi Thianghlim atan chuan i fapate an tangka leh rangkachak nen hla tak atanga hruai turin matheiloin thliarkarte chuan mi nghak ang a, Tarsis lawng liante chuan hmasak ber an chuh ang.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Tin, ram dang mite chuan i kulh bangte chu an rem chho leh ang a, an lalte pawhin i rawng an bawl tawh ang; ka thinrim chuan ka vua chian, nimahsela ka duhsaknain ka khawngaih si che a nih hi.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> I kawngkharte pawh hawnin a awm areng ang a; a chhun azanin an khar lo ang; miten hnam tin sum chu i hnenah an rawn laka, an lalte pawh an rawn hruai ve theihna'n.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> I rawng bawl duh lo hnam leh ram chu a boral dawn si a; a ni, chung hnamte chu tihchhiat hlauhin an awm ang.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ka hmun thianghlim cheimawi turin Lebanon ropuina chu i hnenah a lo kal ang, far te, phan te, tuifar te chu an lo kal tlang ang; tichuan ka ke rahna hmun chu ka tiropui ang.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Tin, nangmah tiretheituteho fapate chu kunin i hnenah an lo kal ang a; nangmah hmusittute zawng zawng chu chibai bukin i kehphah hnuaiah an kun ang; nang chu \"LALPA khawpui,\" \"Israel-ho Mi Thianghlim Zion,\" an ti ang che.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Tuma tlawh ngai loh khawpa kalsan leh huata i awm aiah kumkhaw chhuan ber, chhuan tam tak lawmnaah ka siam ang che.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Tin, hnam tin hnutetui i fawp ang a, lalho hnute pawh i hne ang: kei LALPA hi nangmah chhandamtu leh nangmah tlantu, Jakob-ho Mi Chaka chu ka ni tih i la hre bawk ang.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Dar aiah rangkachak ka rawn la ang a, thir aiah pawh tangkarua ka rawn la ang, thing aiah pawh dar, lung aiah pawh thir: thlamuanna chu i hotuah ka ruat bawk ang a, felna chu nangmah phuttuah ka ruat ang.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Rang taka thiltih thawm chu i ramah hriat a ni tawh lo ang a, tiauna leh chhiatna thawm pawh chu i ramah hriat a ni tawh lo ang a, tiauna leh chhiatna thawm pawh i ramri chhungah rhiat a ni tawh lo ang; i kulh chu \"Chhandamna,\" i ti zawk ang a, i kawngkharte pawh \"Fakna,\" i ti bawk ang.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ni khi chhunah nangmah entu a ni tawh lo ang ;a thla pawh khian enna turin a tieng hek lo ang che: LALPA erawh chu i tan kumkhaw entuah a awm ang a, i Pathian chu i ropuina atan a awm bawk ang.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> I ni chu a tla tawh lo ang a, i thla pawh chu a rla thaw hek lo ang: LALPA chu i kumkhaw entu a ni dawn tawh si a, i lusun nite chu a tawp dawn tawh a ni.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> I mite pawh an zain mi fel an i ang a, i ram hi an luah kumkhua ang; chawimawi ka awm theihna turin anni chu a zung puak chhuak ka phun, ka kut chhuak chu, an ni ang.In zinga hnam te ber pawh hnam ropui tak an ni ang a, hnam tlemte pawh hnam chak tak an ni ang: kei LALPA hian a hun hunah chuan ka thlentir thuai ang.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> In zinga hnam te ber pawh hnam ropui tak an ni ang a, hnam tlemte pawh hnam chak tak an ni ang: kei LALPA hian a hun hunah chuan ka thlentir thuai ang."
		},
		"61": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Thuhnuairawlhte hnenah chanchin tha hril tura LALPA'n hriak mi thih avangin Lalpa PATHIAN thlarau chu ka chungah a awm; ani chuan thinlung lungchhiate tuam tur te, salte hnena chhuahna thu leh mi tangte hnena tan in hawnna thu sawi tur te,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> LALPA lungawi kum thu leh kan Pathian phuba lak ni thu sawi tur te, lungngai zawng zawng thlamuan tur te,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> vut aiah pangpar thihrui te, lungnaih aiah hlimna hriak te, nguina thlarau aiah fakna silhfente an hnenah pekah Zion-a lungngaia awmte tan ruat tur tein mi tir a ni: ani chu chawimawia a awmna turin, felna thing, LALPA phunte, tih an nih theihna'n.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Tin, hmun hlui chhe tawhte chu an rem leh ang a, tun hmaa khaw lo tiau tawhte chu an din tha leh ang a, khawpui chhe tawh, chhuan tam tak tiaunate chu an siam tha leh ang.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Tin, ram dang mite chuan in ran rualte chu dingin an tlattir ang a, hriat ngai loh mite chu in leilettu-ahte leh in grep hrui enkawltuahte an awm ang.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> nangni erawh chu, \"LALPA puithiamte, \" tia vuaih in awm ang a: miten, \"Kan Pathian rawngbawltute,\" an ti ang che u: hnam tin sum in ei ang a, an ropuina chu in inchhuan phah ang.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> In mualpho aiah a leh hnih in hmu ang a; in zah aiah in chanvovah hlimin in zai ang: chuvangin in ramah chuan a leh hnih in luah ang a: kumkhaw hlimna in hnenah a awm ang.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Kei LALPA hian rorelan fel ka ngaina si thin a, khawlo taka ram hi ka haw thin a ni; tichuan anmahni ka rulhna chu tihtak meuhin an hnenah ka pe ang a, an hnenah kumkhaw thu ka thlung bawk ang.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Tichuan an thlahte chu hnam tin zingah hriat an ni ang a, an fate chu mi tin zingah hriat an ni bawk ang: anmahni hmu apiangin LALPA malsawm chi an ni tih an hria ang.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> LALPA-ah chuan nasa takin ka hlim ang a, ka nunna hi ka Pathianah chuan lawm takin a awm ang; mo neitu tur chu pangpar thihruia a inchei thin ang leh, mo tur chu a incheinatea a inchei thin ang hian, ani chuan chhandamna silhfente mi bel a, felna kawrfualin mi tuam ta si a.Leilung hian a thil chawr chu a chhuahtir ang leh, huan hian a chhunga thil chinte chu a chawrtir ang hian, Lalpa Pathian chuan felna leh rfakna hnam tinreng hmaah chuan a chawrtir dawn si a.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Leilung hian a thil chawr chu a chhuahtir ang leh, huan hian a chhunga thil chinte chu a chawrtir ang hian, Lalpa Pathian chuan felna leh rfakna hnam tinreng hmaah chuan a chawrtir dawn si a."
		},
		"62": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> A felna chu enna anga a chhuah a, amah chhandamna chu khawnvar alh anga a chhuah hma loh chuan, Zion avangin ka ngawi reng lo ang a, Jerusalem avangin ka awm hle hle lo ang.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Tichuan hnam tinin i felna chu an hmu ang a, lal zawng zawngin i ropuina chu an hmu bawk ang: tin, hming thar, LALPA kain a vuah tur chuan an ko ang che.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> LALPA kuta mawina lallukhum leh i Pathian kuta ropuina lukhum i ni bawk ang.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> \"Mak,\" an ti leh tawh lo ang che; i ram pawh chu \"Tihtiau,\" an ti leh tawh hek lo ang: \"Duhlai,\" an ti tawh zawk ang chia, i ram pawhin pasal a nei dawn a ni.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> tlangvalin nula nupuia an nei thin ang hian ifapaten nupuiah an nei ang che: mo neitu chu mo chungah a lawm angin, i Pathian chu i chungah a lawm ang.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> ,7 Aw Jerusalem, i kulh chungah ralvengtute ka ventir a; a chhun azanin engtikah mah an ngawi lo ang: Jerusalem hi a tihngheha,m leiah hian fakawma a siam hma loh chuan, nangni LALPA hriatpuitua awmte u, awm hle hle hlek suh u la, amah pawh chu awm hle hletir hlek suh u.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> ,6 Aw Jerusalem, i kulh chungah ralvengtute ka ventir a; a chhun azanin engtikah mah an ngawi lo ang: Jerusalem hi a tihngheha,m leiah hian fakawma a siam hma loh chuan, nangni LALPA hriatpuitua awmte u, awm hle hle hlek suh u la, amah pawh chu awm hle hletir hlek suh u.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> ,9 LALPA'n, \"I buh chu nangmah dotute chawah ka pe leh tawh hauh lo ang a: ram dang miten i thawh chhuah uain chu an in tawh lo ang: a sengtute chuan an ei tawh zawk ang a, LALPA chu an fak ang; a lotute chuan ka hmun thianghlim hung chhung kawtlaiah chuan an in tawh ang,\" tiin a kut ding lam leh a ban chak tak chhalin chhia a chham ta.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> ,8 LALPA'n, \"I buh chu nangmah dotute chawah ka pe leh tawh hauh lo ang a: ram dang miten i thawh chhuah uain chu an in tawh lo ang: a sengtute chuan an ei tawh zawk ang a, LALPA chu an fak ang; a lotute chuan ka hmun thianghlim hung chhung kawtlaiah chuan an in tawh ang,\" tiin a kut ding lam leh a ban chak tak chhalin chhia a chham ta.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Chhuak u la, kulh kawngkaahte chhuak rawh u; mite tan kawng buatsaih u la; chhung pawng u la, lamlian chu chhung pawng rawh u; lungte chu chhar fai u la; mite tan chhinchhiahna tar chhuak rawh u.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ngai teh u, LALPA'n kawlkil thlengin heti hian a hriattir a ni, \"Zion fanu hnenah heti hian sawi rawh u, 'En teh, nangmah chhandamna a lo thlen dawn hi; en teh, a lawmman chu a hnenah a awm hi, a rulhna chu ahmaah a awm bawk a.Tichuan anni chu, Mi thianghlimho, LALPA tlante an ti ang a: nang chu, Zawn chhuah, Kalsan loh khawpui, an ti ang che,' tiin, \" a ti a.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Tichuan anni chu, Mi thianghlimho, LALPA tlante an ti ang a: nang chu, Zawn chhuah, Kalsan loh khawpui, an ti ang che,' tiin, \" a ti a."
		},
		"63": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Edom ram atanga lo kal, Bozrah khua atanga silhfen thihsen sin saw tu nge ni? A puan sina ropui tak, nasa taka chaka lo kal saw? Keimah, fel taka thu sawia, chhandam kawnga mi chak taka kha ka ni.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Eng vangin nge i puan sin kha a sen a, i silhfente pawh kha grep sawrna khura rap sawrtu silhfen anga a awm ni?",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Keimah chauhin grep sawrna khurah ka rap sawr a; mi tin zinga mi pakhat mah ka hnenah an awm ve lo va: a ni, anni chu ka thinurin ka rap a, ka thinrimin ka chil a; tichuan an nunna thisen chu ka silhfenahte hian thehin a awm a, ka puan zawng zawng hi ka tibawlhhlawh ta a.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Phuba lak ni chu ka thinlungah a awm si a, ka mi tlante kum chu a lo thleng ta bawk a ni.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Tichuan ka han en a, tanpuitu tur reng reng an awm lo a; chelh dingtu reng reng an awm lo chu mak ka ti a: chuvangin keima ban ngei hian chhandamna mi thlen a; ka thinrimna chuan mi chelh ding ta a.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Tichan mi tin chu ka rap bet a, ka thinrimin ka tirui a, an nunna thisen chu leiah ka baw ta.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> LALPA thil engkima min vur avangin LALPA ngilneihzia thute leh LALPA fakna thute ka sawi ang a; a khawngaihnate leh a ngilneihna a nasat avangin Israela chhungte laka a thatna nasa taka an chunga a vur thu pawh kha ka sawi bawk ang.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ani chuan, \"Ka mite, fa adera ti lo turte, an ni ngei mai,\" a ti si a: chutichuan anmahni chhandamtuah a lo awm ta a.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> An manganna zawng zawngah chuan ani chu amangang ve thin a, vantirhkoih, a hmaa awm mi chuan, anni chu a chhanhim bawk thin a: a hmangaihna leh a khawngiahnain a tlan ta hlawm a; hmasang ni zawng zawngah chuan anmahni a puain anmahni a pawm thin.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Nimahsela an hel a, a thlarau thianghlim chu an tilungngai ta a: chuvangin anmahni dotua awm tura tihlamletin a awm a, amah ngei chuan anni chu a bei ta a.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Chumi lai chuan amite chuan Mosia hmasang nite chu an hre reng a, heti hian an ti, \"Tuifinriat atanga a beram rual vengtue nena anmahni hruai chhotu kha khawiah nge? A thlarau thianghlim an zinga dahtu kha khawiah nge?",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> A ban ropui tak Mosia ding lama kaltirtu kha khawiah nge? Kumkhaw hming insiam nana an hmaa tui tithentu kha khawiah nge?",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> An inchhuih lohna tura tui thuk taka, thlalera sakawr hruai anga anmahniho hruaia kaitu kha khawiah nge?",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Ruama ran chhukte angin LALPA thlarau chuan anniho chu a chawlhtir a: chutiang chuan, hming ropui tak i insiamna'n i mite chu i hruai kha,\" tiin.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Van atang khan rawn thlir thla la, i thianghlimna leh i ropuina awmna atang khan rawn en teh: i thahnemngaihna leh i thiltih ropui takte khakhawiah nge? i thinlunga i ngaihna leh i lainatnate kha kalak ah tihrehin a awm ta .",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Abrahama'n min hre loin, Israela pawhin min ngaihsak lo mah se la, nang chu kan pa i ni si a ; nang chu , aw LALPA,kanpa i ni a; i hming chu chatuan ata keimahni min tlantu a ni .",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Aw LALPA, nangin eng vangin nge i kawng atangtea min vah botir thina, nangmah tih lo tura kan thinlung min tihkhauhsak thin le? i chhiahhlawh, i roluah hnamte avang hian, lokir leh rawh .",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> I mi thianghlimte chuan rei lo te chauh an nei a; min dotute chuan i hmun thianghlim chu an rap che ta a.An chunga ro i rel ngai lohte ang a,i hming pu ngai lote ang chu kan lo ni ta.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> An chunga ro i rel ngai lohte ang a,i hming pu ngai lote ang chu kan lo ni ta."
		},
		"64": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> ,2 Aw, hnam tin i hmaa an khurhna turin nangmah dotute hnenah i hming hriattir nan, meiin thingnawi a tialh a,mei chuan tuite a ti so ang hian tlangte chu i hmaa an luan thlak dul dulna'n, van kha tithlerin lo chhuk teh hram la aw!",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> ,1 Aw, hnam tin i hmaa an khurhna turin nangmah dotute hnenah i hming hriattir nan, meiin thingnawi a tialh a,mei chuan tuite a ti so ang hian tlangte chu i hmaa an luan thlak dul dulna'n, van kha tithlerin lo chhuk teh hram la aw!",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Kan beisei loh thil rapthlak i tih lai khan i lo chhuk a, tlangte chu i hmaah an luan thlak dul dul kha.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Hmasang ata tawh miten, nangmah chauh lo chu, anmahni nghaktu atan thawksak thintu Pathian an hre ngai si lo a, bengin an hrengai hek lo a, mitin an hmu ngai hek lo.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Nang chuan, hlim taka awma fel taka titu, i kawngte nangmah hre reng thintute chu, i hmuak thin a: ngai teh, nang i thinur a, keinin thil kan tisual a: chungah te chuan rei tak kan lo awm tawh a, tichuan chhandamin kan la awm thei ang em?",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Mi bawlhhlawh angin kan lo awm ta vek si a, kan felna zawng zawngte pawh silhfen bawlhhlawh ang a ni a: kan zain hnah angin kan vuai thin a; kan khawlohnate hian thli angin min leh bo thin.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Tichuan i hming lama, nangmah chelh tura mahni intiharh tumah reng reng an awm lo: kan lakah hian i hmai i thup ta si a, kan lakah hian i hmai i thup ta si a, kan khawlohna te hmangin min toboral ta ni.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Tunah erawh chuan, aw LALPA nang chu kan pa i ni a; keini hi bellei kan ni a, nang min vawtu i ni; tichuan kan za hian i kut chhuak kan ni.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Aw LALPA, thinur nasa lutuk suh la,khawlohnate pawh kumkhua chuan hre reng heksuh ang che: ngai teh, khawngaih takin min en la, kan za hian i mite kan nih hi.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> I khawpui thianghlimte chu thlalerah a lo chan a, Zion chu thlalerah a lo chan a, Jerusalem chu hmun tihtiauvah a lo chan tak hi.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Kan in thianghlim leh kan in mawi tak, kan puten an lo fak thinna che chu,meia hal a ni a; kan thil duhawmte zawng anwg lah chu tihchhiatin a awm ta vek si a.Aw LALPA, chung thilahte chuan i insum thei dawn em ni? I ngawi rengin min tirethei nasa reng dawn em ni?",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Aw LALPA, chung thilahte chuan i insum thei dawn em ni? I ngawi rengin min tirethei nasa reng dawn em ni?"
		},
		"65": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Mi lam ngai lote zawnin ka awm a, mi zawng ngai lote hmuhin ka awm a: ka hming pu lo hnam hnenah chuan, \"Mi en rawh u, mi en rawh u,\" ka ti a.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Mi helhmangte tan nilengin ka bante ka phar thin, chungho chu anmahni ngaihtuahteang zela kawng tha loa kal thinte ,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> huanahte inthawia, leirawh chan chungahte englo rimtui hala, ka hmaichhan ngeia mi tithinur thinte,",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> thlan zingahte thu a, hmun fianrialtea riak thinte, vawk sa eia, an beltea thil tenawm tuihang awm thinte,",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> \"Nangmah chauhin ding rawh, mi rawn hnaih suh, nang ai chuan ka thianghlim zawk hi,\" ti thinte chu an ni: chungho chu ka hnara mei khu awm, nilenga mei nung reng thin chu a ni.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> ,7 Ngai teh u, ka hmaah ziakin a awm : ka ngawi reng lo ang a, ka thungrul zawk ang, a ni, an angchhungah nangmahni khawlohna leh in pute khawlohnate chu ka thungrul ve ve ang, LALPA'n a ti, chungho chuan tlang lian chungahte englo rimtui halin tlangte chungahte kan hming an sawiche thin: chuvangin an hming an sawichhe thin: chuvangi an hnathawh chu a hmasa berin an angchhungah ka tehsang a.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> ,6 Ngai teh u, ka hmaah ziakin a awm : ka ngawi reng lo ang a, ka thungrul zawk ang, a ni, an angchhungah nangmahni khawlohna leh in pute khawlohnate chu ka thungrul ve ve ang, LALPA'n a ti, chungho chuan tlang lian chungahte englo rimtui halin tlangte chungahte kan hming an sawiche thin: chuvangin an hming an sawichhe thin: chuvangi an hnathawh chu a hmasa berin an angchhungah ka tehsang a.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> LALPA chuan heti hian a ti, \"Grep bawrah uain thar an hmu a, miin, 'Tichhe suh, khatah khan malsawmna a awm si,' an ti ang khan, ka chhaihhlawh avangin ka ti ve ang, an zaa ka tihchhiat vek lohna'n.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Tin, Jakoba atangin chi pakhat ka tichhuak ang a, Juda atangin ka tlangte luahtu tur ka tichhuak ang: tichuan ka mi thlante chuan chu chu an luah ang ang a, ka chhiahhlawhte chu chutah chuan an awm ang.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Tin, ka mi, mi zawngtute tan chuan, Saron chu beram rualho huang a ni ang a, Akor ruam chu bawng rualho bawhna hmun tur a ni ang.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Nimahsela nangni LALPA kalsana, ka tlang thianghlim theihnghilh a, vanneihna Siamtua tan dawhkan buatsaih a, Chantawka Khawrelsaktui tak uain chawhpawlh sa chhung khat thinte uain chawhpawlh sa chhung khat thinte uain chawlhpawlh sa chhung khat thinte u;",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> ka koh lai che u khan mi in chhan duh loh a, thu ka sawi lai khan benga in hriat duh loh a, ka mithmuha thil sual chu in tih zawka, ka thil lawm loh zawng chu in thlan avangin khandaihin in chantawka khua chu ka relsak ang che u a, in zain thahnaah chuan in kun vek ang.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Chuvangin Lalpa PATHIAN chuan heti hian a ti, \"Ngai teh u, ka chhiahhlawhte chuan an ei ang a, nangni erawh chu rilramin in awm ang: ngai teh u, ka chhiahhlawhte chuan an in ang a, nangni erawh chu tuihalin in awm ang: ngai teh u, ka chhiahhlawhte chu an hlim ang a, nangni erawh chu in zak ang:",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> ngai teh u, ka chhiahhlawhte chu thinlunga an lawm avangin hlim takin an zai ang a, nangni erawh chu thinlunga in lungngaih avangin in tap ang a, thlarauva in vui avangin in chiau vak vak ang.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Tin, in hming chu chhechhamna'n ka mi thlante hnenah in hnutchhiah ang a, Lalpa PATHIAN chuan a tihlum ang che u; tin, a chiahhlawhte chu hming dangin a ko tawh a:",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> chutichuan leiah hian mahni mal insawm chawptu chu thutak Pathianah chuan mal a insawm ang a; Pathian chhalin chhia a chham ang; tun hma mangannate chu theihnghilha a awm ak avang leh ka mit laka thupha a awm tak avangin.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ngai teh u, van tharte leh lei thar ka siam anih hi; tun hma thilte chu hriat rengin a awm tawh lo ang a, rilruah pawh a lut tawh hek lo ang.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Nimahsela ka thil siamah chuan kumkhuain lawmin hlim rawh u: ngai teh u, Jerusalem chu hlimnaah ka siam a, amite chu lawmnaah ka siam anih hi.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Jerusalem chungah chuan ka hlim ang a, ka mite chungah pawh ka lawm ang: a chhungah chuan tap thawm chu hriat a ni tawh lo ang a, chiau thawm pawh hriat a ni tawh hek lo ang.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> chuta tanga chhuak chu nausen ni rei lo te dam an awm lo ang a, putar a dam chhung nite tlingtla lo an awm hek lo ang: naupang chu kum za mi niin a thi dawn si a, mi sual kum za chauh dam chu anchhe dawng an ni sawn a ni.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Tin, inte an sa ang a, chungah chuan an awm reng bawk ang; grep huante an siam ang a, a rah an ei bawk ang.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Midang awmna turin in an sa tawh lo ang a, mi dang eiah grep huan an siam tawh lo ang: thing dam chung nite ang hian ka mite dam chhung nite chu a awm dawn si a, ka mi thlante chu rei tak an thawh chhuah chungah chuan an lawm dawn a ni.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> A thlawnin an thawk rim lo ang a, vanduaina mai turin fa an hring hek lo ang; LALPA malsawm mi thlahte an ni si a, an fate chu an hnenah an awm reng ang.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Tin, heti hi a ni ang a, annin mi koh hma pawhin ka chhang ang a; thu an la sawi lai mek pawhin ka bengin ka hria ang.Chinghnia leh beram no chu an tla dun tawh ang a, sakeibaknei chuan bawngpa angin buhpawl a ei tawh ang: vaivut chu rul chaw a ni ang. Ka tlang thianghlim reng rengah chuan an tina tawh lo ang a, an tichhe tawh hek lo ang, LALPA'n a ti.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Chinghnia leh beram no chu an tla dun tawh ang a, sakeibaknei chuan bawngpa angin buhpawl a ei tawh ang: vaivut chu rul chaw a ni ang. Ka tlang thianghlim reng rengah chuan an tina tawh lo ang a, an tichhe tawh hek lo ang, LALPA'n a ti."
		},
		"66": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> LALPA chuan heti hian a ti, \"Van ka thutphah a ni a, lei ka ke nghahchhan a ni: in eng ang nge mi saksak ang: Khawii hmun nge ka chawlhna tur chu?",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Heng thil engkim hi ka kutin ka siam ani si a, chutichuan he'ng thil engkim hi a lo awm ta a ni, LALPA'n a ti: amaherawhchu mi, rethei taka awm, rilrua inchhir ngawih ngawih, ka thua khur thina lam hi ka en zawk ang.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bawngpa talhtu chu mihring thattu ang a ni a; beram nova inthawitu chu ui nghawng titliaktu ang a ni a; thilpek hlantu chu vawk thisen hlantu ang a ni a, beraw haltu chu milem malsawmtu ang a ni: a ni, anmahni kawng chu a thlang ta a, an thil tenawmahte chuan an rilru a lawm thi;",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> ka koh lai khan tuma'n mi chhan lo a, thu ka sawi lai kha, benga an hriat loh a, ka mit hmuha thil sual chu an tih zawk a, ka thil lawm loh zawng chu an thlan avangin kei pawhin anmahni bumna turte chu ka thlansak ang a, an hlauhzawngte chu an chungah ka thlentir ang,\" tiin.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> A thua khur thitne u, LALPA thu hi hre rawh u: \"In unau, nangmahni hawtu leh ka hming avanga nangmahni hnawt chhuaktute chuan, 'In lawmna kan hmuh theihna'n LALPA chu tihropuiin aawm rawh se,' an ti a; nimahsela an zak tawh zawk ang.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Chu! Khawpuia sa mur mur thawm chu! Biak ina thawm a nih chu! A hmelmate thungrultu, LALPA thawm anih chu!",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ani chuan vei hman loin nau a nei a; na hre hman loinmipa naupang ahring a.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Chutiang chu tuin nge hre thei ngai? Chutiangte chu tuin nge hmu ngai? Ni khatah ram a piang thut dawn em ni? Vfawilhekhatah hnam hrinin a awm thut dawn em ni? Zion chuan nau a vei veleh a fate chu a hring ta pang si a.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Pian hun thlentir siin ka hrintir dawn lo em ni? LALPA'n a ti: kei hrintir thintu hian fa ka neihtir phal dan lo em ni? i Pathianin a ti.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> \"Jerusalem hmangaihtu zawng zawngte u, Jerusalem chu hlimup u la, lawmpui rawh u: amah suntu zawng zawngte u, lawm avangin hlimpui rawh u:",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> in hneka, thlamuanna hnuteahte chuan in tlai theihna'n leh, in hnek daka, a ropuina tam takah chuan in lawm theihna'n,\" tih hi.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> LALPA chuan heti hian a ti si, \"Ngai teh u, remna chu luipui ang maiin a hnen thlengin ka luantir ang a, hnam tin ropuina chu luite a kuang liam dul dul ang maiin, a hnen thlengin ka luantir bawk ang, tichuan chu chu in hne ang; a hmathlak ang che u a, a mal chungah chuan a tumtir ang che u.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Mi, a nuin a thlamuan angin ka thlamuan ang che u; tichuan Jerusalem-ah chuan thlamuanin in awm dawn nia.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Tin, chu chu in hmu ang a, in thinlung chu ahlim ang a, in ruhte pawh hlobet hring dup angin a duah hluah hluah ang: tichuan LALPA kut chu a chhiahhlawhte lamah a awm tih an hria ang a, a hmelmate chungah alungni lo ang.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ngai teh u, a thinur chu thinrimnaa hrithla tur leh, a zilhhauna chu meialhtea hritla turin, LALPA chu mei nen a lo kal dawn si a, a tawlailirte chu thawngaleivir ang mai a ni ang.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Meiin a ni, LALPA'n a ngaihtuah dawn ni, a khandaihin a ni, mi zawng zawng a ngaihtuah dawn ni: tichuan LALPA tihhlumte chu tam tak an ni ang.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Huanahte inthawi tuma inzui dum dum tura intithianghlim leh inthianfai thinte, vawk sa leh thil tenawm leh chaichim sa eite chu an boral tlang ang, LALPA'n a ti.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Am thiltihte leh an ngaihtuahte chu ka hre si a: hnam tinreng leh tawng tinreng ka hruai khawm hun a lo thleng dawn; tichuan an lo kal ang a, ka ropuina an hmu ang.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Tin, an zingah chuan chhinchhiahna ka awmtu ang a, tichuan an zinga hremna pumpelh apiangte chu hnam tin hnenah - Tarsis te, Pul te, thal ngul kuaiho Lud hnenah te, Tubal leh Javan-ho hnenah te, thliarkar hla ta, ka hmingthan la hre ngai lo a, ka ropuina la hmu ngai loho hnenahte chuan - ka tir ang; tichuan hnam tin zingah ka ropuina thu an sawi ang.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Tichuan Israela thlahten an thilhlan chu bungbel thianghlim taka LALPA ina an rawn la lut thin ang hian, LALPA hnena thilhlan atan hnam tinreng zing ata in naute zawng zawng chu saker chungah te, tawlailirah te, zawnnaah te, sabengtung chungah te, sanghawngsei chungah te, Jerusalem ka tlang thianghlimah chuan an rawn hruai ang, LALPA'n a ti.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Tin, chung zinga mi pawh chu puithiam atante leh Levia mi atante ka la ang, LALPA'n a ti.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Van tharte leh lei thar ka la siam tur chu ka hmaah a awm reng dawn angin, in thlahte leh in hming chu a awm reng bawk dawn a ni, LALPA'n a ti.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Tin, heti hi a ni ang a, thla thar atanga thla thar dang thlengin, chawlhni atanga chawlhni dang thlengin mi zawng zawng ka hmaah chibai mi buk turin an lo kal zut zut ang, LALPA'n a ti.Tin, an kal chhuak thin ang a, ka laka bawhchhetute ruang chu an en ang: an lungte chu an thiin, an mei chu tihmihin a awm dawn si lo; mi zawng zawng tan thil tenawm tak an ni ang.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Tin, an kal chhuak thin ang a, ka laka bawhchhetute ruang chu an en ang: an lungte chu an thiin, an mei chu tihmihin a awm dawn si lo; mi zawng zawng tan thil tenawm tak an ni ang."
		}
	}
};
